"Dilithium\\">Dilithium</a> to the U.S.S. <i>Valor</i>\n</li>\n<li> Warp to Lackey III\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li> Refined Behavior\n<ul>\n<li> Attempt to Beam Up <a href=\\"/index.php?title=Decalithium&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\\" class=\\"new\\" title=\\"Decalithium (page does not exist)\\">Decalithium</a> From the <a href=\\"/Gorn\\" title=\\"Gorn\\">Gorn</a> Refinery\n</li>\n<li> Beam Charges Into Gorn Jamming Station\n</li>\n<li> Beam Up Decalithium from the Gorn Refinery\n</li>\n<li> Warp to Paulson Nebula\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li> Hide and Seek\n<ul>\n<li> Scan Suspicious Objects (0/3)\n</li>\n<li> Beam to Station\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li> Lost and Found\n<ul>\n<li> Go To Lackey Klingon Listening Post\n</li>\n<li> Transmit Data from the Computer Core\n</li>\n<li> Defend the Data Core During Transmission 1:00\n</li>\n<li> Depart System\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li> Hail Starfleet to Report\n</li>\n</ul>\n"}]}}}}"""))
