ight\\"><div class=\\"thumbinner\\" style=\\"width:252px;\\"><a href=\\"/File:Qaris.png\\" class=\\"image\\"><img alt=\\"\\" src=\\"http://hydra-media.cursecdn.com/sto.gamepedia.com/thumb/4/43/Qaris.png/250px-Qaris.png?version=475b32e8111c611c034305084c41e1bf\\" width=\\"250\\" height=\\"253\\" class=\\"thumbimage\\" srcset=\\"http://hydra-media.cursecdn.com/sto.gamepedia.com/4/43/Qaris.png 1.5x, http://hydra-media.cursecdn.com/sto.gamepedia.com/4/43/Qaris.png 2x\\" /></a>  <div class=\\"thumbcaption\\"><div class=\\"magnify\\"><a href=\\"/File:Qaris.png\\" class=\\"internal\\" title=\\"Enlarge\\"><img src=\\"/skins/common/images/magnify-clip.png\\" width=\\"15\\" height=\\"11\\" alt=\\"\\" /></a></div>Administrator <a href=\\"/Qaris\\" title=\\"Qaris\\">Qaris</a></div></div></div>\n</li>\n<li> Speak to Qaris\n</li>\n<li> Inspect Safety Hazards (0/4)\n</li>\n<li> Talk to Bar Patrons\n</li>\n<li> Quell the Bar Fight\n<ul>\n<li> [Tactical] Beam down Security Escorts<sup id=\\"cite_ref-1\\" class=\\"reference\\"><a href=\\"#cite_note-1\\">[1]</a></sup>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li> Inspect the Bar (0/1)\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li> Roadblocks\n<ul>\n<li> Make your way to Cargo Bay 6\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li> In the Brig\n<ul>\n<li> Locate <a href=\\"/Marta\\" title=\\"Marta\\">Marta</a> in Cargo Bay\n</li>\n<li> Defeat Captain <a href=\\"/index.php?title=Urthog&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\\" class=\\"new\\" title=\\"Urthog (page does not exist)\\">Urthog</a>\n</li>\n<li> Rescue Marta <div class=\\"thumb tright\\"><div class=\\"thumbinner\\" style=\\"width:252px;\\"><a href=\\"/File:Marta.png\\" class=\\"image\\"><img alt=\\"\\" src=\\"http://hydra-media.cursecdn.com/sto.gamepedia.com/thumb/0/02/Marta.png/250px-Marta.png?version=524a855fb7a4941f761b9a847e530e76\\" width=\\"250\\" height=\\"293\\" class=\\"thumbimage\\" srcset=\\"http://hydra-media.cursecdn.com/sto.gamepedia.com/0/02/Marta.png 1.5x, http://hydra-media.cursecdn.com/sto.gamepedia.com/0/02/Marta.png 2x\\" /><