{"query":{"pages":{"24010":{"pageid":24010,"ns":0,"title":"Mission: Second Wave","revisions":[{"*":"<div id=\\"toc\\" class=\\"toc\\"><div id=\\"toctitle\\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\\"><a href=\\"#Outline\\"><span class=\\"tocnumber\\">1</span> <span class=\\"toctext\\">Outline</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\\"><a href=\\"#Mission_Text\\"><span class=\\"tocnumber\\">1.1</span> <span class=\\"toctext\\">Mission Text</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\\"toclevel-3 tocsection-3\\"><a href=\\"#Federation\\"><span class=\\"tocnumber\\">1.1.1</span> <span class=\\"toctext\\">Federation</span></a></li>\n<li class=\\"toclevel-3 tocsection-4\\"><a href=\\"#Klingon\\"><span class=\\"tocnumber\\">1.1.2</span> <span class=\\"toctext\\">Klingon</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\\"toclevel-2 tocsection-5\\"><a href=\\"#Goal\\"><span class=\\"tocnumber\\">1.2</span> <span class=\\"toctext\\">Goal</span></a></li>\n<li class=\\"toclevel-2 tocsection-6\\"><a href=\\"#Objectives\\"><span class=\\"tocnumber\\">1.3</span> <span class=\\"toctext\\">Objectives</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\\"toclevel-3 tocsection-7\\"><a href=\\"#Federation_2\\"><span class=\\"tocnumber\\">1.3.1</span> <span class=\\"toctext\\">Federation</span></a></li>\n<li class=\\"toclevel-3 tocsection-8\\"><a href=\\"#Klingon_2\\"><span class=\\"tocnumber\\">1.3.2</span> <span class=\\"toctext\\">Klingon</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Outline\\">Outline</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Second_Wave&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\\" title=\\"Edit section: Outline\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Mission_Text\\">Mission Text</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Second_Wave&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\\" title=\\"Edit section: Mission Text\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h3>\n<h4><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Federation\\">Federation</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Second_Wave&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\\" title=\\"Edit section: Federation\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h4>\n<div class=\\"missiontext\\">\n<p>By now, you've faced the Borg.\n</p><p>The Collective is appearing with more frequency in the Alpha Quadrant, and Defera is facing repeated attacks.\n</p><p>We've been able to push them back so far, but we can't do it forever. Not without help.\n</p><p>Starfleet has convinced representatives from the Klingon Empire, the Cardassians, and the Deferi to meet on Deep Space 9. We want you to be there as well.\n</p>\n</div>\n<h4><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Klingon\\">Klingon</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Second_Wave&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\\" title=\\"Edit section: Klingon\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h4>\n<div class=\\"missiontext\\">\n<p>My name is Commander Mesi Achebe, and I was authorized by your High Council to contact you.\n</p><p>By now, you've faced the Borg.\n</p><p>The Collective is appearing with more frequency in the Alpha Quadrant, and Defera is facing increasing attacks.\n</p><p>We've been able to push them back so far, but we can't do it forever. Not without help.\n</p><p>Starfleet is organizing a meeting on DS9 to discuss the Borg situation. Representatives from Starfleet, the Cardassians, and the Deferi will be present. Your chancellor is sending a representative as well.  We want you to be there to represent the Klingon forces fighting the Collective.\n</p><p>We have our differences, but some problems are simply too big to ignore.\n</p>\n</div>\n<h3><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Goal\\">Goal</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Second_Wave&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\\" title=\\"Edit section: Goal\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h3>\n<div class=\\"missiongoal\\">\n<p>Report to Deep Space Nine to take part in negotiations for a combined force to combat the Borg.\n</p><p>Deep Space Nine is located in the Bajor Sector of the Beta Ursae Sector Block.\n</p>\n</div>\n<h3><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Objectives\\">Objectives</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Second_Wave&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\\" title=\\"Edit section: Objectives\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h3>\n<div class=\\"leftcolumn\\">\n<h4><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Federation_2\\">Federation</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Second_Wave&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7\\" title=\\"Edit section: Federation\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h4>\n<ul>\n<li> Disarming Diplomats\n<ul>\n<li> Go to <a href=\\"/Deep_Space_9\\" title=\\"Deep Space 9\\">Deep Space 9</a>\n</li>\n<li> Attend the Borg Conference\n<ul>\n<li> Talk to Commander Andrews in Operations\n</li>\n<li> Speak with Conference Attendees\n<ul>\n<li> Talk to <a href=\\"/S%27taass\\" title=\\"S'taass\\">S'taass</a> in the Multipurpose Room\n</li>\n<li> Talk to Captain <a href=\\"/Shon\\" title=\\"Shon\\" class=\\"mw-redirect\\">Shon</a> in the Shipyard\n<ul>\n<li> (Optional) U.S.S. Belfast Duty Officer Assignments (0/3)\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li> Talk to <a href=\\"/Rugan_Skyl\\" title=\\"Rugan Skyl\\">Rugan Skyl</a> in the Replimat\n<ul>\n<li> (Optional) Home Away From Homesick\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li> Talk to Ambassador <a href=\\"/Surah\\" title=\\"Surah\\">Surah</a> in Quark's Bar\n<ul>\n<li> (Optional) Diplomatic Distractions\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li> Find the Conference Speaker\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li> Take Turoblift to the Conference\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li> Conference Conflicts\n<ul>\n<li> Discuss the Borg Problem\n<ul>\n<li> Take a Seat at the Conference Table\n</li>\n<li> Discuss the Borg Threat\n<ul>\n<li> Convince Cardassia to Join the Fight <sup id=\\"cite_ref-1\\" class=\\"reference\\"><a href=\\"#cite_note-1\\">[1]</a></sup>\n</li>\n<li> Convince Defera to Join the Fight <sup id=\\"cite_ref-2\\" class=\\"reference\\"><a href=\\"#cite_note-2\\">[2]</a></sup>\n</li>\n<li> Convince Starfleet to Join the Fight <sup id=\\"cite_ref-3\\" class=\\"reference\\"><a href=\\"#cite_note-3\\">[3]</a></sup>\n</li>\n<li> Convince the Klingon Empire to Join the Fight <sup id=\\"cite_ref-4\\" class=\\"reference\\"><a href=\\"#cite_note-4\\">[4]</a></sup>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n<li> Escaping Envoys\n<ul>\n<li> Escape Deep Space 9\n<ul>\n<li> Leave Conference Room\n</li>\n<li> Escort VIPs to the Shipyard\n<ul>\n<li> (Engineering) Free the Trapped Security Officer\n</li>\n<li> (Science) Heal Injured Security Officer\n</li>\n<li> (Tactical) Arm Diplomats\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li> Escort VIPs to Your Ship\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li> Defend Deep Space 9\n<ul>\n<li> Defeat Jem'Hadar Attack Ships\n</li>\n<li> Clear a Path for Ships Retreating From Deep Space 9\n<ul>\n<li> Assist the USS Belfast\n</li>\n<li> Assist the USS Opaka\n</li>\n<li> Assist the USS Fletcher\n</li>\n<li> Assist the USS Phinda\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li> Contact Deep Space 9\n</li>\n<li> Flee Circus\n<ul>\n<li> Warp to Bajor\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<div class=\\"rightcolumn\\">\n<h4><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Klingon_2\\">Klingon</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Second_Wave&amp;action=edit&amp;section=8\\" title=\\"Edit section: Klingon\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h4>\n<ul>\n<li> Disarming Diplomats\n<ul>\n<li> Go to <a href=\\"/Deep_Space_9\\" title=\\"Deep Space 9\\">Deep Space 9</a>\n</li>\n<li> Attend the Borg conference\n<ul>\n<li> Talk to Commander Andrews in Operations\n</li>\n<li> Speak with Conference attendees\n<ul>\n<li> Talk to S'taass in the Multipurpose Room\n<ul>\n<li> (Optional) S'taass Duty Officer Assignments\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li> Talk to Ambassador Surah in Quark's Bar\n<ul>\n<li> (Optional) Diplomatic Distractions\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li> Talk to Rugan Skyl at the Replimat\n<ul>\n<li> (Optional) Home away from Homesick\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li> Talk to Captain Shon at the Shipyard\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li> Find the Conference Speaker\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li> Conference Conflicts\n<ul>\n<li> Take a seat at the Conference Table\n</li>\n<li> Discuss the Borg Threat\n<ul>\n<li> Convince the Klingon Empire to Join the Fight\n<ul>\n<li> This requires completion of S'taass's side mission.\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li> Convince Cardassia to Join the Fight\n<ul>\n<li> This requires completion of Rugan Skyl's side mission.\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li> Convince Defera to Join the Fight\n<ul>\n<li> This requires completion of Surah's side mission.\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li> Convince Starfleet to Join the Fight\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li> Escaping Envoys\n<ul>\n<li> Escape Deep Space 9\n<ul>\n<li> Leave Conference Room\n</li>\n<li> Escort VIPs to the Shipyard\n<ul>\n<li> (Engineering) Free the Trapped Security Officer\n</li>\n<li> (Science) Heal Injured Security Officer\n</li>\n<li> (Tactical) Arm Diplomats\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li> Escort VIPs to Your Ship\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li> Defend Deep Space 9\n<ul>\n<li> Defeat Jem'Hadar Attack Ships\n</li>\n<li> Clear a Path for Ships Retreating From Deep Space 9\n<ul>\n<li> Assist the USS Belfast\n</li>\n<li> Assist the USS Opaka\n</li>\n<li> Assist the USS Fletcher\n</li>\n<li> Assist the USS Phinda\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li> Contact Deep Space 9\n</li>\n<li> Flee Circus\n<ul>\n<li> Warp to Bajor\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<p><br style=\\"clear: both; height: 0px;\\" />\n</p>\n<ol class=\\"references\\">\n<li id=\\"cite_note-1\\"><span class=\\"mw-cite-backlink\\"><a href=\\"#cite_ref-1\\">\u2191</a></span> <span class=\\"reference-text\\">This requires either a Diplomacy rank of 2 or completing Rugan Skyl's side mission.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\\"cite_note-2\\"><span class=\\"mw-cite-backlink\\"><a href=\\"#cite_ref-2\\">\u2191</a></span> <span class=\\"reference-text\\">This requires either a Diplomacy rank of 3 or completing Surah's side mission.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\\"cite_note-3\\"><span class=\\"mw-cite-backlink\\"><a href=\\"#cite_ref-3\\">\u2191</a></span> <span class=\\"reference-text\\">This requires either a Diplomacy rank of 4 or completing Captain Shon's side mission.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\\"cite_note-4\\"><span class=\\"mw-cite-backlink\\"><a href=\\"#cite_ref-4\\">\u2191</a></span> <span class=\\"reference-text\\">This requires a Diplomacy rank of 1.</span>\n</li>\n</ol>\n"}]}}}}"""))
