		missions.add(new Mission(text: """
{"query":{"pages":{"42341":{"pageid":42341,"ns":0,"title":"Mission: First City","revisions":[{"*":"<h3><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Mission_Text\\">Mission Text</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_First_City&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\\" title=\\"Edit section: Mission Text\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h3>\n<div class=\\"missiontext\\">As the newest Captain of a KDF starship, you find that the citizens of First City treat you differently. Some have more respect, and some wish you to prove your worthiness of command.</div>\n"}]}}}}"""))
		missions.add(new Mission(text: """
{"query":{"pages":{"38115":{"pageid":38115,"ns":0,"title":"Mission: Duties of Command","revisions":[{"*":"<h3><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Mission_Text\\">Mission Text</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Duties_of_Command&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\\" title=\\"Edit section: Mission Text\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h3>\n<div class=\\"missiontext\\">Perform the duties that a Captain in the KDF must.</div>\n"}]}}}}"""))
		missions.add(new Mission(text: """
{"query":{"pages":{"38124":{"pageid":38124,"ns":0,"title":"Mission: The Hunt is On","revisions":[{"*":"<h3><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Mission_Text\\">Mission Text</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_The_Hunt_is_On&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\\" title=\\"Edit section: Mission Text\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h3>\n<div class=\\"missiontext\\">A security breach brings your special talents into play.</div>\n"}]}}}}"""))
		missions.add(new Mission(text: """
{"query":{"pages":{"39421":{"pageid":39421,"ns":0,"title":"Mission: Space Chase","revisions":[{"*":"<h3><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Mission_Text\\">Mission Text</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Space_Chase&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\\" title=\\"Edit section: Mission Text\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h3>\n<div class=\\"missiontext\\"><a href=\\"/Franklin_Drake\\" title=\\"Franklin Drake\\">That Federation scum</a> has escaped Qo'noS. Your job is to hunt him down.</div>\n"}]}}}}"""))
		missions.add(new Mission(text: """
{"query":{"pages":{"39422":{"pageid":39422,"ns":0,"title":"Mission: Manhunt","revisions":[{"*":"<h3><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Mission_Text\\">Mission Text</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Manhunt&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\\" title=\\"Edit section: Mission Text\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h3>\n<div class=\\"missiontext\\">\n<p>We have identified the Federation prisoner you've been chasing. His name is Franklin Drake. Some of our sources say he's a Starfleet Intelligence agent, but there are hints that he's much more. From what I can tell, he's not part of the normal chain of command.\n</p><p>Previously we didn't have any images or genetic samples from him, which is why he was so hard to identify. Now we'll be on him the second he shows his face again. We already have a lead for you to follow.\n</p><p>Records indicate a Klingon shuttle entered space above Rura Penthe Penal Colony. That system is restricted, and there was no traffic scheduled for today. You are authorized by the High Council to approach the system and determine if Drake is there.\n</p><p>Bring him back alive if you can.\n</p>\n</div>\n"}]}}}}"""))
		missions.add(new Mission(text: """
{"query":{"pages":{"39545":{"pageid":39545,"ns":0,"title":"Mission: Friend or Foe","revisions":[{"*":"<h3><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Mission_Text\\">Mission Text</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Friend_or_Foe&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\\" title=\\"Edit section: Mission Text\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h3>\n<div class=\\"missiontext\\">\n<p>During my time as ambassador, I uncovered evidence that one of the Great Houses has been corrupted by a foreign influcence and plotting against the Empire. I was thrown into Rura Penthe as punishment for digging too close to the truth.\n</p><p>The fugitive, Drake, suggested that we travel to the <a href=\\"/Vorn_System\\" title=\\"Vorn System\\">Vorn System</a>. We hope to find evidence that will prove there is an internal threat to the Empire.\n</p>\n</div>\n"}]}}}}"""))
		missions.add(new Mission(text: """
{"query":{"pages":{"8401":{"pageid":8401,"ns":0,"title":"Mission: Bringing Down the House","revisions":[{"*":"<h3><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Mission_Text\\">Mission Text</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Bringing_Down_the_House&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\\" title=\\"Edit section: Mission Text\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h3>\n<div class=\\"missiontext\\">\n<p><a href=\\"/Sirella\\" title=\\"Sirella\\">Sirella</a>, lady of the <a href=\\"/House_of_Martok\\" title=\\"House of Martok\\">House of Martok</a>, has requested that you meet her in the <a href=\\"/Ketha_Lowlands\\" title=\\"Ketha Lowlands\\">Ketha Lowlands</a>.\n</p><p>She did not explain why she wanted to see you, but I expect that she has some task she would like completed. The House of Martok has lost much prestige since I took the Chancelor's seat, but they still have many allies among the <a href=\\"/Klingon_Defense_Force\\" title=\\"Klingon Defense Force\\">KDF</a> and I am loathe to reject Sirella's request without a good reason.\n</p><p>Gaining the favor of the House of Martok could serve you well, but remember that they have many enemies. I Harbor no ill toward Sirella, but do not get caught up in her vengeance against me. It would not be in your best interest.\n</p>\n</div>\n"}]}}}}"""))
		missions.add(new Mission(text: """
{"query":{"pages":{"9190":{"pageid":9190,"ns":0,"title":"Mission: The House Always Wins","revisions":[{"*":"<h3><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Mission_Text\\">Mission Text</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_The_House_Always_Wins&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\\" title=\\"Edit section: Mission Text\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h3>\n<div class=\\"missiontext\\">\n<p>The idea that one of the Great Houses is conspiring with Romulans to attack the House of Martok is troublesome, <i>&lt;Rank&gt;</i>.\n</p><p>Come to the Ketha lowlands. Worf and I would be honored if you would participate in M'Ven's <i>Heghtay.</i>\n</p><p>Once we have put our family matters to rest, you may work with Worf and K'mtar to determine our plan of attack.\n</p>\n</div>\n"}]}}}}"""))
		missions.add(new Mission(text: """
{"query":{"pages":{"41891":{"pageid":41891,"ns":0,"title":"Mission: Test of Mettle","revisions":[{"*":"<h3><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Mission_Text\\">Mission Text</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Test_of_Mettle&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\\" title=\\"Edit section: Mission Text\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h3>\n<div class=\\"missiontext\\">\n<p>Congratulations, <b>&lt;Name&gt;</b>! You've proven yourself and are due the accolades of a true Klingon Warrior.\n</p><p>Return to <a href=\\"/First_City\\" title=\\"First City\\">First City</a> on <a href=\\"/Qo%27noS\\" title=\\"Qo'noS\\">Qo'noS</a>.\n</p>\n<div class=\\"missionnote\\">This mission will provide access to a free ship.</div>\n</div>\n"}]}}}}"""))
		missions.add(new Mission(text: """
{"query":{"pages":{"8203":{"pageid":8203,"ns":0,"title":"Mission: Second Star to the Right, Straight on 'til Morning","revisions":[{"*":"<h3><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Mission_Text\\">Mission Text</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Second_Star_to_the_Right,_Straight_on_%27til_Morning&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\\" title=\\"Edit section: Mission Text\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h3>\n<div class=\\"missiontext\\">\n<p>A <a href=\\"/Federation\\" title=\\"Federation\\" class=\\"mw-redirect\\">Federation</a> task force is attacking a starbase we have claimed in the Alhena system.\n</p><p>I need more ships to defend the base, and the I.K.S. &lt;shipname&gt; is right for the job.\n</p><p>Fight for the Empire!\n</p>\n</div>\n"}]}}}}"""))
		missions.add(new Mission(text: """
{"query":{"pages":{"7942":{"pageid":7942,"ns":0,"title":"Mission: Keep Your Enemies Closer","revisions":[{"*":"<h3><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Mission_Text\\">Mission Text</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Keep_Your_Enemies_Closer&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\\" title=\\"Edit section: Mission Text\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h3>\n<div class=\\"missiontext\\">\n<p>Valiant warriors are being held by the <a href=\\"/United_Federation_of_Planets\\" title=\\"United Federation of Planets\\">Federation</a>. The Federation's idea of \\"mercy\\" is to allow our soldiers to rot in a cell instead of seeking an honorable death.\n</p><p>I spit upon their mercy. We are <a href=\\"/Klingon\\" title=\\"Klingon\\">Klingon</a>!\n</p><p>I will allow you to attempt to rescue your fellow warriors from their terrible fate. But you will need cunning to do so.\n</p><p>The Federation penal colony is highly guarded. Only Starfleet vessels may approach. But I know where you can acquire a Starfleet <a href=\\"/Danube_Class_Runabout\\" title=\\"Danube Class Runabout\\">runabout</a> ... if you are up to the challenge.\n</p>\n</div>\n"}]}}}}"""))
		missions.add(new Mission(text: """
{"query":{"pages":{"7629":{"pageid":7629,"ns":0,"title":"Mission: Blood of the Empire","revisions":[{"*":"<h3><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Mission_Text\\">Mission Text</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Blood_of_the_Empire&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\\" title=\\"Edit section: Mission Text\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h3>\n<div class=\\"missiontext\\">\n<p>There is a report of a battle in the <a href=\\"/Norgh_System\\" title=\\"Norgh System\\">Norgh system</a>.\n</p><p>If there is an enemy bold enough to attack that close to the <a href=\\"/Klingon_Empire\\" title=\\"Klingon Empire\\">Empire</a>, it must be dealt with ... harshly.\n</p><p>I'm calling all available ships to the Norgh system to assist. Fight with honor.\n</p>\n</div>\n"}]}}}}"""))
		missions.add(new Mission(text: """
{"query":{"pages":{"7632":{"pageid":7632,"ns":0,"title":"Mission: Destiny","revisions":[{"*":"<h3><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Mission_Text\\">Mission Text</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Destiny&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\\" title=\\"Edit section: Mission Text\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h3>\n<div class=\\"missiontext\\">\n<p><i>&lt;rank&gt;</i>, it is my duty as Chancellor to do something about the threat of the Fek'Ihri. I think you are the best officer for this taks.\n</p><p>Report to me in the <a href=\\"/Klingon_High_Council\\" title=\\"Klingon High Council\\">High Council</a> chamber on <a href=\\"/Qo%27noS\\" title=\\"Qo'noS\\">Qo'noS</a>. We will discuss what you can do for your <a href=\\"/Klingon_Empire\\" title=\\"Klingon Empire\\">Empire</a>.\n</p>\n</div>\n"}]}}}}"""))
		missions.add(new Mission(text: """
{"query":{"pages":{"7683":{"pageid":7683,"ns":0,"title":"Mission: Afterlife","revisions":[{"*":"<h3><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Mission_Text\\">Mission Text</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Afterlife&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\\" title=\\"Edit section: Mission Text\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h3>\n<div class=\\"missiontext\\">\n<p>I have received a message from the emperor.\n</p><p><a href=\\"/Kahless\\" title=\\"Kahless\\">Kahless</a> commands that you travel to the monastery at <a href=\\"/Boreth_System\\" title=\\"Boreth System\\">Boreth</a>. He says that he will meet you there and instruct you on what you must do to stop the advance of <a href=\\"/Molor\\" title=\\"Molor\\">Molor</a> and his <a href=\\"/Fek%27Ihri\\" title=\\"Fek'Ihri\\">Fek'Ihri</a> horde.\n</p><p>The Fek'Ihri are formidable. May you be victorious!\n</p>\n</div>\n"}]}}}}"""))
		missions.add(new Mission(text: """
{"query":{"pages":{"7689":{"pageid":7689,"ns":0,"title":"Mission: The Gates of Gre'thor","revisions":[{"*":"<h3><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Mission_Text\\">Mission Text</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_The_Gates_of_Gre%27thor&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\\" title=\\"Edit section: Mission Text\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h3>\n<div class=\\"missiontext\\">\n<p>Gre'thor itself is yours to conquer. Face the spectres of Cowardice, Treachery, Dishonor and Death, and stop Molor from returning to the land of the living.\n</p>\n</div>\n"}]}}}}"""))
		missions.add(new Mission(text: """
{"query":{"pages":{"43065":{"pageid":43065,"ns":0,"title":"Mission: A House Pursued","revisions":[{"*":"<h3><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Mission_Text\\">Mission Text</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_A_House_Pursued&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\\" title=\\"Edit section: Mission Text\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h3>\n<div class=\\"missiontext\\">\n<p>&lt;Rank&gt; &lt;Name&gt;, just the person I wanted to see.\n</p><p>The council is concerned that rogue elements are operating out of the Servin System. Reports of Orions continue to come from our intelligence on the front, and every time we send KDF ships to investigate, they never return.\n</p><p>This wouldn't be the first time the Orions have acted without consulting me. Some defiance is to be expected. When they target our warships, though, they have gone too far.\n</p><p>You don't need me to tell you this, but be prepared to encounter hostile Orions when you arrive. If they are acting against the interests of the Empire, they won't be friendly to outsiders.\n</p>\n</div>\n"}]}}}}"""))
		missions.add(new Mission(text: """
{"query":{"pages":{"43067":{"pageid":43067,"ns":0,"title":"Mission: House on Fire","revisions":[{"*":"<h3><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Mission_Text\\">Mission Text</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_House_on_Fire&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\\" title=\\"Edit section: Mission Text\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h3>\n<div class=\\"missiontext\\">\n<p>The once mighty House of Torg, reduced to scavenging and piracy. Uncovering the fact that they are selling <a href=\\"/Borg\\" title=\\"Borg\\">Borg</a> weaponry puts you in a position to stop them.\n</p><p>The logs you downloaded showed they were heading for the <a href=\\"/Veela_System\\" title=\\"Veela System\\">Veela System</a>. There are several <a href=\\"/Orion_Syndicate\\" title=\\"Orion Syndicate\\">Orion Syndicate</a> facilities located there. It's likely that they are storing the weapons in one of them until the buyer can take delivery.\n</p><p>The weapons should be simple to scan for, but the local Orions might not take too kindly having their warehouse scrutinized.\n</p>\n</div>\n"}]}}}}"""))
		missions.add(new Mission(text: """
{"query":{"pages":{"27375":{"pageid":27375,"ns":0,"title":"Mission: Alpha","revisions":[{"*":"<h3><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Mission_Text\\">Mission Text</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Alpha&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\\" title=\\"Edit section: Mission Text\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h3>\n<div class=\\"missiontext\\">\n<p>&lt;Rank&gt;, a bird-of-prey on a very important mission has gone missing in Romulan space.\n</p><p>We received a brief burst from its emergency transponder, but then it went silent. We don't know what happened, bit it is vital that we recover the ship's data recorder and all of its sensor data.\n</p><p>I want you to report to the Orith system. It is the last know location of the ship. Find the vessel. If there are survivors, your are authorized to assist them. However, the recovery of the data is your primary concern.\n</p>\n</div>\n"}]}}}}"""))
		missions.add(new Mission(text: """
{"query":{"pages":{"31898":{"pageid":31898,"ns":0,"title":"Mission: Temporal Ambassador","revisions":[{"*":"<h3><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Mission_Text\\">Mission Text</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Temporal_Ambassador&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\\" title=\\"Edit section: Mission Text\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h3>\n<h4><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Federation_.2F_Klingon\\">Federation / Klingon</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Temporal_Ambassador&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\\" title=\\"Edit section: Federation / Klingon\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h4>\n<div class=\\"missiontext\\">\n<p><b>&lt;Rank&gt;</b>, we've detected an anomaly in the Azure Nebula.   \n</p><p>Because of the Tholian activity in that area, we're concerned that they may be attempting to open a rift to the Mirror Universe. I need a ship to go out there and check it out.  \n</p>\n<div class=\\"missionnote\\">This mission can only be completed as a single player.</div>\n</div>\n<h4><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Romulan\\">Romulan</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Temporal_Ambassador&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\\" title=\\"Edit section: Romulan\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h4>\n<div class=\\"missiontext\\">\n<p>&lt;rank&gt;, Franklin Drake suggested I contact you to assist with a critical mission.\n</p><p>We've detected an anomaly in the Azure Nebula.   \n</p><p>Because of the Tholian activity in that area, we're concerned that they may be attempting to open a rift to the Mirror Universe. I need a ship to go out there and check it out.  \n</p>\n<div class=\\"missionnote\\">This mission can only be completed as a single player.</div>\n</div>\n"}]}}}}"""))
		missions.add(new Mission(text: """
{"query":{"pages":{"33718":{"pageid":33718,"ns":0,"title":"Mission: Secrets of Nimbus","revisions":[{"*":"<div id=\\"toc\\" class=\\"toc\\"><div id=\\"toctitle\\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\\"><a href=\\"#Outline\\"><span class=\\"tocnumber\\">1</span> <span class=\\"toctext\\">Outline</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\\"><a href=\\"#Mission_Text\\"><span class=\\"tocnumber\\">1.1</span> <span class=\\"toctext\\">Mission Text</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\\"toclevel-3 tocsection-3\\"><a href=\\"#Federation\\"><span class=\\"tocnumber\\">1.1.1</span> <span class=\\"toctext\\">Federation</span></a></li>\n<li class=\\"toclevel-3 tocsection-4\\"><a href=\\"#Klingon\\"><span class=\\"tocnumber\\">1.1.2</span> <span class=\\"toctext\\">Klingon</span></a></li>\n<li class=\\"toclevel-3 tocsection-5\\"><a href=\\"#Romulan\\"><span class=\\"tocnumber\\">1.1.3</span> <span class=\\"toctext\\">Romulan</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\\"toclevel-2 tocsection-6\\"><a href=\\"#Goal\\"><span class=\\"tocnumber\\">1.2</span> <span class=\\"toctext\\">Goal</span></a></li>\n<li class=\\"toclevel-2 tocsection-7\\"><a href=\\"#Objectives\\"><span class=\\"tocnumber\\">1.3</span> <span class=\\"toctext\\">Objectives</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Outline\\">Outline</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Secrets_of_Nimbus&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\\" title=\\"Edit section: Outline\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Mission_Text\\">Mission Text</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Secrets_of_Nimbus&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\\" title=\\"Edit section: Mission Text\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h3>\n<h4><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Federation\\">Federation</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Secrets_of_Nimbus&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\\" title=\\"Edit section: Federation\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h4>\n<div class=\\"missiontext\\">\n<p>We have a situation in the Nimbus system, <b>&lt;Rank&gt;</b>. <a href=\\"/Romulan_Republic\\" title=\\"Romulan Republic\\">Romulan Republic</a> intelligence suggests that there are triggers for thalaron weapons somewhere on the planet Nimbus III. There are also increasing reports of <a href=\\"/Tal_Shiar\\" title=\\"Tal Shiar\\">Tal Shiar</a> activity on the planet.\n</p><p>Most people steer clear of Nimbus III these days \u2013 the Orion Syndicate basically runs the planet. Obviously, though, it would be a disaster if the Tal Shiar managed to get their hands on the thalaron triggers or take control of the planet. Stopping them not only helps a planet that needs Starfleet assistance, it provides a diplomatic connection with the Romulan Republic.\n</p><p>I know that I can count on you to do the right thing.\n</p>\n</div>\n<h4><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Klingon\\">Klingon</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Secrets_of_Nimbus&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\\" title=\\"Edit section: Klingon\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h4>\n<div class=\\"missiontext\\">\n<p>We have a situation in the Nimbus system, <b>&lt;Rank&gt;</b>. <a href=\\"/Romulan_Republic\\" title=\\"Romulan Republic\\">Romulan Republic</a> intelligence suggests that there are triggers for thalaron weapons somewhere on the planet Nimbus III. There are also increasing reports of <a href=\\"/Tal_Shiar\\" title=\\"Tal Shiar\\">Tal Shiar</a> activity on the planet.\n</p><p>Those Tal Shiar dogs cannot be allowed to have those triggers! We have sent a team to Nimbus III already, but they have failed to report in. Something must have happened.\n</p><p>I'm leaving this task in your hands. May you find glory in the sands of Nimbus.\n</p>\n</div>\n<h4><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Romulan\\">Romulan</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Secrets_of_Nimbus&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\\" title=\\"Edit section: Romulan\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h4>\n<div class=\\"missiontext\\">\n<p>&lt;rank&gt;, after what you've been through, I wouldn't blame you if you decided to take a leave of absence. But you seem to be recovering from the vestiges of indoctrination as well as can be expected.\n</p><p>I hope you're feeling better. The psychologists assure us that the nightmares and flashbacks will pass.\n</p><p>At the moment, we're trying to follow up on scattered intel regarding a missing chache of thalaron triggers. Our best information places them on <a href=\\"/Nimbus_III\\" title=\\"Nimbus III\\">Nimbus III</a>. We're also getting increasing reports of <a href=\\"/Tal_Shiar\\" title=\\"Tal Shiar\\">Tal Shiar</a> activity on the planet.\n</p><p>Naturally, we want to keep the triggers out of the hands of <a href=\\"/Hakeev\\" title=\\"Hakeev\\">Hakeev</a> and the Tal Shiar. But I'd also like to know exactly what they're doing on \\"the planet of galactic peace.\\"\n</p><p>Nimbus III has been a derelict planet for many years now, and it has only gotten worse under the influence of the <a href=\\"/Orion_Syndicate\\" title=\\"Orion Syndicate\\">Orion Syndicate</a>. Hassan the Undying has turned the planet into his personal fiefdom. Both Starfleet and the Klingon Defense Force have sent people to investigate, but they haven't found much.\n</p><p>Our operatives have been following leads provided by an itinerant trader there named <a href=\\"/Horace_Jones\\" title=\\"Horace Jones\\">Horace Jones</a>. So far nothing's turned up. If you're feeling up to it, perhaps you'll have better luck.\n</p>\n</div>\n<h3><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Goal\\">Goal</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Secrets_of_Nimbus&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\\" title=\\"Edit section: Goal\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h3>\n<div class=\\"missiongoal\\">Go to Nimbus III, which is located in the Tau Dewa Sector Block, and follow up on leads regarding banned weapons.</div>\n<h3><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Objectives\\">Objectives</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Secrets_of_Nimbus&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7\\" title=\\"Edit section: Objectives\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h3>\n<ul>\n<li> Go to Nimbus III\n</li>\n<li> Contact Horace Jones\n</li>\n</ul>\n"}]}}}}"""))
		missions.add(new Mission(text: """
{"query":{"pages":{"35908":{"pageid":35908,"ns":0,"title":"Mission: The Lost City of Paradise","revisions":[{"*":"<div id=\\"toc\\" class=\\"toc\\"><div id=\\"toctitle\\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\\"><a href=\\"#Outline\\"><span class=\\"tocnumber\\">1</span> <span class=\\"toctext\\">Outline</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\\"><a href=\\"#Mission_Text\\"><span class=\\"tocnumber\\">1.1</span> <span class=\\"toctext\\">Mission Text</span></a></li>\n<li class=\\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\\"><a href=\\"#Goal\\"><span class=\\"tocnumber\\">1.2</span> <span class=\\"toctext\\">Goal</span></a></li>\n<li class=\\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\\"><a href=\\"#Objectives\\"><span class=\\"tocnumber\\">1.3</span> <span class=\\"toctext\\">Objectives</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Outline\\">Outline</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_The_Lost_City_of_Paradise&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\\" title=\\"Edit section: Outline\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Mission_Text\\">Mission Text</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_The_Lost_City_of_Paradise&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\\" title=\\"Edit section: Mission Text\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h3>\n<div class=\\"missiontext\\">\n<p>Funny seeing you folks here. No one seems to bat an eye about our little planet until the Orions get their hands on something nasty. Now between that and the Romulans, this joint is jumpin'!\n</p><p>You want info? Sure, I'll give you info. The owner of the local bar, a reformed Borg by the name of <a href=\\"/Two_of_Eight\\" title=\\"Two of Eight\\">Two of Eight</a>, has his ear close to the ground.\n</p><p>He can tell you more about the <a href=\\"/Tal_Shiar\\" title=\\"Tal Shiar\\">Tal Shiar</a>. Just don't tell too many people I told you, alright?\n</p>\n</div>\n<h3><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Goal\\">Goal</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_The_Lost_City_of_Paradise&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\\" title=\\"Edit section: Goal\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h3>\n<div class=\\"missiongoal\\">Speak with Two of Eight in the bar on Nimbus III and uncover information about missing thalaron triggers.</div>\n<h3><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Objectives\\">Objectives</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_The_Lost_City_of_Paradise&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\\" title=\\"Edit section: Objectives\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h3>\n<ul>\n<li> Find Leads on Thalaron Weapons\n<ul>\n<li> Talk to the Bar Owner, Two of Eight\n</li>\n<li> Locate Missing Officers\n</li>\n<li> Desert Ambush\n<ul>\n<li> Investigate Weapon Remains (0/5)\n</li>\n<li> Fend Off Nearby Scorpions (0/20)\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li> Recover Groups of Downed Officers (0/2)\n</li>\n<li> Confront Two of Eight\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li> Track Down Information on the Triggers\n<ul>\n<li> Go to Law's House\n</li>\n<li> Talk to Law with the Console by his House\n</li>\n<li> Scan Old Consoles  of Defeat Sandworms to Recover Nausicaan Information (0%)\n</li>\n<li> Use the Computer at the Bar to Decipher the Information\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li> Return to Horace Jones\n</li>\n</ul>\n"}]}}}}"""))
		missions.add(new Mission(text: """
{"query":{"pages":{"33654":{"pageid":33654,"ns":0,"title":"Mission: Blind Men Tell All Tales","revisions":[{"*":"<h3><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Mission_Text\\">Mission Text</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Blind_Men_Tell_All_Tales&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\\" title=\\"Edit section: Mission Text\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h3>\n<div class=\\"missiontext\\">\n<p>This blind man must be some sorta mole for the <a href=\\"/Orion_Syndicate\\" title=\\"Orion Syndicate\\">Orion Syndicate</a>, the guys who have those triggers you're lookin' for. Now, I don't know who this guy is, but someone in this town must know.\n</p><p>The only way you're gonna convince folks to help you find this guy is if you show that you're not only strong enough to fight the Syndicate, but that you've got the gumption to defend us from 'em.\n</p><p>You do that, and I bet someone will step forward to tell you who this mole is and where you can find the triggers. If I were you, I'd start with <a href=\\"/Two_of_Eight\\" title=\\"Two of Eight\\">Two of Eight</a>. You get in good with him and you'll be all sorts of good, you know?\n</p>\n</div>\n"}]}}}}"""))
		missions.add(new Mission(text: """
{"query":{"pages":{"35968":{"pageid":35968,"ns":0,"title":"Mission: The Undying","revisions":[{"*":"<h3><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Mission_Text\\">Mission Text</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_The_Undying&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\\" title=\\"Edit section: Mission Text\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h3>\n<div class=\\"missiontext\\">\n<p>You've fond the location of <a href=\\"/Hassan_the_Undying\\" title=\\"Hassan the Undying\\">Hassan the Undying</a>'s stronghold. He's operating out of his \\"pleasure palace\\" \u2013 which is in reality a broken-down old ship that's the closest thing this place has to an underground club.\n</p><p>Men, women, fights, illegal deals, Syndicate merchandise \u2013 whatever you're looking for, Hassan has it there for a price.\n</p><p>What we want is information. Hassan sold the thalaron triggers to someone. All you need to do is convince him to tell you who so we can try to get them back.\n</p>\n</div>\n"}]}}}}"""))
		missions.add(new Mission(text: """
{"query":{"pages":{"35970":{"pageid":35970,"ns":0,"title":"Mission: A Fistful of Gorn","revisions":[{"*":"<h3><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Mission_Text\\">Mission Text</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_A_Fistful_of_Gorn&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\\" title=\\"Edit section: Mission Text\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h3>\n<div class=\\"missiontext\\">\n<p>When you first beamed down here, I wasn't so sure about you, but after what you did to Hassan? Yeah. You have some skills.\n</p><p>So, some Reman escaped with the trigger? Tough break. I bet he's out of the sector by now, but if there's one man on this rock who'd know where to go next, it's Law.\n</p><p>He can help you bring an end to all of this, then we can all celebrate with some drinks at the bar!\n</p>\n</div>\n"}]}}}}"""))
		missions.add(new Mission(text: """
{"query":{"pages":{"35973":{"pageid":35973,"ns":0,"title":"Mission: Installation 18","revisions":[{"*":"<h3><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Mission_Text\\">Mission Text</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Installation_18&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\\" title=\\"Edit section: Mission Text\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h3>\n<div class=\\"missiontext\\">\n<p>Everything points to the communications array as the hub of Tal Shiar activity on Nimbus III. There have also been reports of disappearances in the vicinity, and they have to be releated. The Tal Shiar have been taking people from all over. Makes sense that they're doing it here too.\n</p><p>It's time to find out what's going on inside that comm array. Get ready, &lt;rank&gt; \u2013 I don't think this is going to be easy.\n</p>\n</div>\n"}]}}}}"""))
		missions.add(new Mission(text: """
{"query":{"pages":{"11064":{"pageid":11064,"ns":0,"title":"Mission: The Vault","revisions":[{"*":"<div id=\\"toc\\" class=\\"toc\\"><div id=\\"toctitle\\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\\"><a href=\\"#Mission_Text\\"><span class=\\"tocnumber\\">1</span> <span class=\\"toctext\\">Mission Text</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\\"><a href=\\"#Federation\\"><span class=\\"tocnumber\\">1.1</span> <span class=\\"toctext\\">Federation</span></a></li>\n<li class=\\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\\"><a href=\\"#Klingon\\"><span class=\\"tocnumber\\">1.2</span> <span class=\\"toctext\\">Klingon</span></a></li>\n<li class=\\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\\"><a href=\\"#Romulan_Republic_.28Federation_Aligned.29\\"><span class=\\"tocnumber\\">1.3</span> <span class=\\"toctext\\">Romulan Republic (Federation Aligned)</span></a></li>\n<li class=\\"toclevel-2 tocsection-5\\"><a href=\\"#Romulan_Republic_.28KDF_Aligned.29\\"><span class=\\"tocnumber\\">1.4</span> <span class=\\"toctext\\">Romulan Republic (KDF Aligned)</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h3><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Mission_Text\\">Mission Text</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_The_Vault&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\\" title=\\"Edit section: Mission Text\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h3>\n<h4><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Federation\\">Federation</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_The_Vault&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\\" title=\\"Edit section: Federation\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h4>\n<div class=\\"missiontext\\">\n<p>The Romulans had a base known as the Vault that they used for research into Borg technology.\n</p><p>This facility was abandoned in the chaos after the destruction of the Romulan homeworld, but intelligence suggests that the work there was far enough along that it was used to retrofit Nero's ship before it disappeared along with Ambassador Spock's vessel in the Hobus system.\n</p><p>Long-range sensors have detected energy spikes in the Haakona system, and Starfleet Intelligence believes that someone is bringing the Vault back online. We need to know who and, more importantly, we need to know if there is still Borg technology or restricted weaponry on that base.\n</p><p>I need you to proceed immediately to the Haakona system and investigate the Vault. Engage if you must, but I would prefer if you could gather the information we need without conflict.\n</p>\n<div class=\\"missionnote\\">You must use a shuttlecraft for this mission, such as a type 8 shuttle, a runabout, or a Delta Flyer.</div>\n</div>\n<h4><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Klingon\\">Klingon</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_The_Vault&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\\" title=\\"Edit section: Klingon\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h4>\n<div class=\\"missiontext\\">\n<p>The Romulans researched Borg technology at a base known as the Vault. The Vault was abandoned in the chaos after the destruction of the Romulan homeworld. We sent a group of scout ships into the region a few years later, but they were lost in an ambush by an unknown vessel. Since then we have been monitoring the region for signs of activity.\n</p><p>Long-range sensors have detected energy spikes in the Haakona system, and <a href=\\"/Klingon_Intelligence\\" title=\\"Klingon Intelligence\\">Klingon Intelligence</a> believes that someone is bringing the Vault back online. I want you to find out who. I also want to know if there is any Borg technology or restricted weaponry on that base.\n</p><p>Good luck \u2013 and good hunting.\n</p>\n<div class=\\"missionnote\\">You must use a shuttlecraft for this mission, such as a Toron-class shuttle.</div>\n</div>\n<h4><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Romulan_Republic_.28Federation_Aligned.29\\">Romulan Republic (Federation Aligned)</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_The_Vault&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\\" title=\\"Edit section: Romulan Republic (Federation Aligned)\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h4>\n<div class=\\"missiontext\\">\n<p>Before the destruction of Romulus, the Imperial Navy and the Tal Shiar operated a base known as the Vault. It was a massive starbase in a remote system, designed to facilitate illegal research and construction projects on a tremendous scale. I am sure, however, that a breach of interstellar accords is no surprise to you.\n</p><p>Research at the Vault led to the use of Borg technology in various Romulan ship refits. While the facility was abandoned in the wake of the Hobus supernova, long-rang sensor scans have reported activity and ship traffic in the Haakona system, where the Vault is located.\n</p><p>Starfleet wishes to be certain that nobody is able to use the Vault to acquire Borg technology or Restricted weapons. Command has recommended that you, as a former subject of the Star Empire, may have an advantage in entering the Vault by subterfuge instead of force.\n</p><p>I need you to proceed immediately to the Haakona system and investigate the Vault. Engage if you must, but I would prefer it if you could gather the information we need without conflict.\n</p>\n<div class=\\"missionnote\\">You must use a shuttlecraft or fighter for this mission, such as a Tiercel Shuttle or Kestral runabout.</div>\n</div>\n<h4><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Romulan_Republic_.28KDF_Aligned.29\\">Romulan Republic (KDF Aligned)</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_The_Vault&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\\" title=\\"Edit section: Romulan Republic (KDF Aligned)\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h4>\n<div class=\\"missiontext\\">\n<p>Before the destruction of Romulus, your people's Star Empire researched Borg technology at a base known as the Vault. The Vault was abandoned in the chaos after the destruction of the Romulan homeworld. We sent a group of scout ships into the region a few years later, but they were lost in an ambush by an unknown vessel. Since then we have been monitoring the region for signs of activity.\n</p><p>Long-range sensors have detected energy spikes in the Haakona system, and <a href=\\"/Klingon_Intelligence\\" title=\\"Klingon Intelligence\\">Klingon Intelligence</a> believes that someone is bringing the Vault back online. I want you to find out who. I also want to know if there is any Borg technology or restricted weaponry on that base.\n</p><p>Good luck \u2013 and good hunting.\n</p>\n<div class=\\"missionnote\\">You must use a shuttlecraft or fighter for this mission, such as a Tiercel Shuttle or Kestral runabout.</div>\n</div>\n"}]}}}}"""))
		missions.add(new Mission(text: """
{"query":{"pages":{"11179":{"pageid":11179,"ns":0,"title":"Mission: Mine Enemy","revisions":[{"*":"<div id=\\"toc\\" class=\\"toc\\"><div id=\\"toctitle\\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\\"><a href=\\"#Mission_Text\\"><span class=\\"tocnumber\\">1</span> <span class=\\"toctext\\">Mission Text</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\\"><a href=\\"#Federation\\"><span class=\\"tocnumber\\">1.1</span> <span class=\\"toctext\\">Federation</span></a></li>\n<li class=\\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\\"><a href=\\"#Klingon\\"><span class=\\"tocnumber\\">1.2</span> <span class=\\"toctext\\">Klingon</span></a></li>\n<li class=\\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\\"><a href=\\"#Romulan_Republic\\"><span class=\\"tocnumber\\">1.3</span> <span class=\\"toctext\\">Romulan Republic</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h3><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Mission_Text\\">Mission Text</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Mine_Enemy&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\\" title=\\"Edit section: Mission Text\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h3>\n<h4><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Federation\\">Federation</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Mine_Enemy&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\\" title=\\"Edit section: Federation\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h4>\n<div class=\\"missiontext\\">\n<p><a href=\\"/Starfleet_Intelligence\\" title=\\"Starfleet Intelligence\\">Starfleet Intelligence</a> has decoded the list of <a href=\\"/Reman\\" title=\\"Reman\\">Reman</a> targets that you recovered from <a href=\\"/The_Vault\\" title=\\"The Vault\\">the Vault</a>. I need you to investigate one of these locations and determine why <a href=\\"/Obisek\\" title=\\"Obisek\\">Obisek</a> and <a href=\\"/Reman_Resistance\\" title=\\"Reman Resistance\\">his forces</a> planned an attack there. \n</p><p>The <a href=\\"/Hfihar_System\\" title=\\"Hfihar System\\">Hfihar System</a> is still technically part of the <a href=\\"/Romulan_Star_Empire\\" title=\\"Romulan Star Empire\\">Romulan Star Empire</a>, but <a href=\\"/Ferengi\\" title=\\"Ferengi\\">Ferengi</a> speculators have moved in and the <a href=\\"/Sela\\" title=\\"Sela\\">empress</a> has done nothing to remove them. The <a href=\\"/Ferengi\\" title=\\"Ferengi\\">Ferengi</a> have reopened the mines and are now doing business with anyone with <a href=\\"/Latinum\\" title=\\"Latinum\\" class=\\"mw-redirect\\">latinum</a>. \n</p><p>You will go to the Hfihar system under the pretense of negotiating a possible trade agreement with the <a href=\\"/Federation\\" title=\\"Federation\\" class=\\"mw-redirect\\">Federation</a>. Talk to <a href=\\"/Madran\\" title=\\"Madran\\">Madran</a>, the operator of the mines. Convince him to allow you access. Find out all you can. \n</p><p>Once we know why Obisek and the Remans are targeting these mines, then we will be able to decide how to proceed.\n</p>\n</div>\n<h4><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Klingon\\">Klingon</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Mine_Enemy&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\\" title=\\"Edit section: Klingon\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h4>\n<div class=\\"missiontext\\">\n<p><a href=\\"/Klingon_Intelligence\\" title=\\"Klingon Intelligence\\">Intelligence</a> has decoded the list of Reman targets that you recovered from the Vault. I want you to infiltrate one of these targets and determine why Obisek would attack it. \n</p><p>The Hfihar system is still technically part of the Romulan Star Empire, but Ferengi speculators have moved in and the empress has done nothing to remove them. The big-eared little moneygrubbers have reopened the mines and are now doing business with anyone with latinum. \n</p><p>You will go to the Hfihar system under the pretense of negotiating a trade deal for the <a href=\\"/Klingon_Empire\\" title=\\"Klingon Empire\\">Empire</a>. Talk to Madran, the operator of the mines. Convince him to allow you access. Find out all you can. \n</p><p>Once we know why Obisek and the Remans are targeting these mines, then we will know how to proceed.\n</p>\n</div>\n<h4><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Romulan_Republic\\">Romulan Republic</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Mine_Enemy&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\\" title=\\"Edit section: Romulan Republic\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h4>\n<div class=\\"missiontext\\">\n<p>Starfleet Intelligence has decoded the list of Reman targets that you recovered from the Vault. I need you to imvestigate one of these locations and determine why Obisek and his forces planned an attack there. \n</p><p>The Hifhar system is still technically part of the Romulan Star Empire, but Ferengi speculators have moved in and the empress has done nothing to remove them. The Ferengi have reopened the mines and are now doing business with anyone with latinum.\n</p><p>Several Survivors from the Star Empire have taken up residence at the mines and now work for Madran, the Ferengi who oversees the operation. The presence of one or more refugees should not cause undue suspicion so you should be able to gather information from Madran and the workers.\n</p><p>Once we know why Obisek and the Remans are targeting these mines, then we should be able to decide how to proceed.\n</p>\n</div>\n"}]}}}}"""))
		missions.add(new Mission(text: """
{"query":{"pages":{"11258":{"pageid":11258,"ns":0,"title":"Mission: Frozen","revisions":[{"*":"<div id=\\"toc\\" class=\\"toc\\"><div id=\\"toctitle\\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\\"><a href=\\"#Mission_Text\\"><span class=\\"tocnumber\\">1</span> <span class=\\"toctext\\">Mission Text</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\\"><a href=\\"#Federation\\"><span class=\\"tocnumber\\">1.1</span> <span class=\\"toctext\\">Federation</span></a></li>\n<li class=\\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\\"><a href=\\"#Klingon\\"><span class=\\"tocnumber\\">1.2</span> <span class=\\"toctext\\">Klingon</span></a></li>\n<li class=\\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\\"><a href=\\"#Romulan_Republic\\"><span class=\\"tocnumber\\">1.3</span> <span class=\\"toctext\\">Romulan Republic</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h3><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Mission_Text\\">Mission Text</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Frozen&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\\" title=\\"Edit section: Mission Text\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h3>\n<h4><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Federation\\">Federation</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Frozen&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\\" title=\\"Edit section: Federation\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h4>\n<div class=\\"missiontext\\">\n<p>We know from the information you recovered from the Hfihar system that the Tal Shiar are planning to attack a Reman settlement in the Dera system.\n</p><p>We have an opportunity to reach the settlement first. This may be a completely internal matter, and if so, the Prime Directive will come into play. We will not be able to interfer. \n</p><p>But if there is an outside influence directing these matters, we must know what it is. Our encounters with the Undine and the Changelings have proven that there are entities attempting to move the powers of the quadrant like pieces in a Kal-toh game. It is essential to protecting the Federation to see these attempts for what they are ... and counter them.\n</p><p>I want you to go the Dera system and learn more about the Reman uprising. The Remans will have hidden their base, so you may have to use subterfuge to find it.\n</p><p>One more thing -- i realize this is a dangerous situation and that you may be drawn into conflict. But do not antagonize the Remans or Romulans if you can avoid doing so. We are already at war with the Klingon Empire. I would prefer to avoid another extended conflict.\n</p>\n</div>\n<h4><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Klingon\\">Klingon</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Frozen&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\\" title=\\"Edit section: Klingon\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h4>\n<div class=\\"missiontext\\">\n<p>We know from the information you recovered from the Hfihar system that the Tal Shiar are planning to attack a Reman settlement in the Dera system. \n</p><p>We have an opportunity to reach the settlement first. I want you to go to the Dera system and learn more about the Reman uprising. The Remans will have hidden their base, so you may have to use subterfuge to find it. \n</p><p>I suspect that this affair is more than simple squabbling. The Tal Shiar either have something to gain from persecuting the Remans or they are under orders to do so. I want to know which it is.\n</p>\n</div>\n<h4><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Romulan_Republic\\">Romulan Republic</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Frozen&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\\" title=\\"Edit section: Romulan Republic\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h4>\n<div class=\\"missiontext\\">\n<p>We know from the information you recovered from the Hfihar system that the Tal Shiar are planning to attack a Reman settlement in the Dera system.\n</p><p>We have an opportunity to reach the settlement first. It may be possible for you to gain the trust of the Reman saboteurs, or at least to learn more of their motives and their base of operations.\n</p><p>While Starfleet is constrained against interfering with internal matters of other galactic powers, you are not limited in this fashion. Nevertheless, I must warn you to avoid drawing the Federation any further into confrontations that may be avoidable.\n</p><p>Starfleet Command is extending a great deal of trust to you with this mission. Please try to avoid precipitating an interstellar war with any rash or impetuous actions.\n</p>\n</div>\n"}]}}}}"""))
		missions.add(new Mission(text: """
{"query":{"pages":{"11391":{"pageid":11391,"ns":0,"title":"Mission: Coliseum","revisions":[{"*":"<div id=\\"toc\\" class=\\"toc\\"><div id=\\"toctitle\\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\\"><a href=\\"#Mission_Text\\"><span class=\\"tocnumber\\">1</span> <span class=\\"toctext\\">Mission Text</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\\"><a href=\\"#Federation\\"><span class=\\"tocnumber\\">1.1</span> <span class=\\"toctext\\">Federation</span></a></li>\n<li class=\\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\\"><a href=\\"#Klingon\\"><span class=\\"tocnumber\\">1.2</span> <span class=\\"toctext\\">Klingon</span></a></li>\n<li class=\\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\\"><a href=\\"#Romulan_Republic_.28Starfleet-aligned.29\\"><span class=\\"tocnumber\\">1.3</span> <span class=\\"toctext\\">Romulan Republic (Starfleet-aligned)</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h3><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Mission_Text\\">Mission Text</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Coliseum&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\\" title=\\"Edit section: Mission Text\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h3>\n<h4><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Federation\\">Federation</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Coliseum&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\\" title=\\"Edit section: Federation\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h4>\n<div class=\\"missiontext\\">\n<p>My contacts tell me that Starfleet has rejected my request for military assistance. That is regrettable, but not unexpected. The Tal Shiar are formidable opponents, as are the forces directing their action. I understand why the Federation would hesitate to engage them directly.\n</p><p>So today I appeal to you, not as an ally in battle, but as a person of compassion. My people need your help. I need your help.\n</p><p>One of our ships was carrying a load of thalaron weapons through the Nopada system. That ship has disappeared.\n</p><p>There are no indications that there was a battle. It is as if my ship and its cargo simply... vanished.\n</p><p>I know you have your reservations about the lengths to which I will go to secure the freedom of my people. Tell me - if you do not trust me with thalaron weapons, do you want Hakeev to have them?\n</p><p>I can provide you with the last coordinates of the vessel. Please ... help me. Do what you will with the weapons if they survive, but find my people!\n</p>\n</div>\n<h4><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Klingon\\">Klingon</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Coliseum&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\\" title=\\"Edit section: Klingon\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h4>\n<div class=\\"missiontext\\">\n<p>My contacts tell me that the Empire has rejected my request for military assistance. That is regrettable, but not unexpected. The Tal Shiar are formidable opponents, as are the forces directing their action. I understand if the High Council is reluctant to engage in a battle that is not theirs.\n</p><p>So today I appeal to you, not as a comrade in warfare, but as an honorable warrior. My people need your help. I need your help.\n</p><p>One of our ships was carrying a load of thalaron weapons through the Nopada system. That ship has disappeared.\n</p><p>There are no indications that there was a battle. It is as if my ship and its cargo simply... vanished.\n</p><p>I know you have your reservations about the lengths to which I will go to secure the freedom of my people. Tell me \u2013 if you do not trust me with thalaron weapons, do you want Hakeev to have them?\n</p><p>I can provide you with the last coordinates of the vessel. Please ... help me. Do what you will with the weapons if they survive, but find my people!\n</p>\n</div>\n<h4><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Romulan_Republic_.28Starfleet-aligned.29\\">Romulan Republic (Starfleet-aligned)</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Coliseum&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\\" title=\\"Edit section: Romulan Republic (Starfleet-aligned)\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h4>\n<div class=\\"missiontext\\">\n<p>My contacts tell me that Starfleet has rejected my request for military assistance. That is regrettable, but not unexpected. The Tal Shiar are formidable opponents, as are the forces directing their action. I understand why the Federation would hesitate to engage them directly.\n</p><p>So today I appeal to you, not as an ally in battle, but as a fellow survivor of the persecution of the Tal Shiar. My people need your help. I need your help.\n</p><p>One of our ships was carrying a load of thalaron weapons through the Nopada system. That ship has disappeared.\n</p><p>There are no indications that there was a battle. It is as if my ship and its cargo simply... vanished.\n</p><p>If you are reluctant to become involved, consider this: What will happen if these weapons fall into Hakeev's hands?\n</p><p>I can provide you with the last coordinates of the vessel. Please ... help me. Do what you will with the weapons if they survive, but find my people!\n</p>\n</div>\n"}]}}}}"""))
		missions.add(new Mission(text: """
{"query":{"pages":{"11484":{"pageid":11484,"ns":0,"title":"Mission: Cutting the Cord","revisions":[{"*":"<div id=\\"toc\\" class=\\"toc\\"><div id=\\"toctitle\\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\\"><a href=\\"#Mission_Text\\"><span class=\\"tocnumber\\">1</span> <span class=\\"toctext\\">Mission Text</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\\"><a href=\\"#Federation\\"><span class=\\"tocnumber\\">1.1</span> <span class=\\"toctext\\">Federation</span></a></li>\n<li class=\\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\\"><a href=\\"#Klingon\\"><span class=\\"tocnumber\\">1.2</span> <span class=\\"toctext\\">Klingon</span></a></li>\n<li class=\\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\\"><a href=\\"#Romulan_Republic_.28Federation-aligned.29\\"><span class=\\"tocnumber\\">1.3</span> <span class=\\"toctext\\">Romulan Republic (Federation-aligned)</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h3><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Mission_Text\\">Mission Text</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Cutting_the_Cord&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\\" title=\\"Edit section: Mission Text\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h3>\n<h4><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Federation\\">Federation</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Cutting_the_Cord&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\\" title=\\"Edit section: Federation\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h4>\n<div class=\\"missiontext\\">\n<p>Starfleet Intelligence has completed its analysis of the data you recovered in the Nopada system.\n</p><p>There is a 67.47 percent chance that the Iconians are using the Tal Shiar as a way to influence the Romulan Star Empire, and that their persecution of the Remans is directly related to this. Command is considering lending assistance to Obisek and his forces, but before we come into direct conflict with the Romulans we want to try a more ... discreet approach.\n</p><p>The data you recovered indicates that Hakeev is operating out of the Brea system. Long-range sensor scans indicate that there may be a major Tal Shiar installation there. We want you to infiltrate this system, apprehend Hakeev and destroy the Tal Shiar's base.\n</p><p>Hakeev must not escape. He may be the only person who knows how extensive the Iconian influence in Romulan space is.\n</p>\n</div>\n<h4><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Klingon\\">Klingon</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Cutting_the_Cord&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\\" title=\\"Edit section: Klingon\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h4>\n<div class=\\"missiontext\\">\n<p>Klingon Intelligence has completed its analysis of the data you recovered in the Nopada system.\n</p><p>The Iconians are using the Tal Shiar as a way to influence the Romulan Star Empire. Their persecution of the Remans is directly related to this. They will hound the Remans until they are broken, or until they are too suspicious and beaten to ever trust an ally again.\n</p><p>This is a coward's way to wage war. Are they too afraid to face us directly? We will stop these machinations now. Then we will see if these demons are brave enough to show their faces!\n</p><p>The data you recovered indicates that Hakeev is operating out of the Brea system. Long-range sensor scans suggest that there may be a major Tal Shiar installation there. We want you to infiltrate this system, apprehend Hakeev and destroy the Tal Shiar's base.\n</p><p>Hakeev must not escape. He may be the only person who knows how extensive the Iconian influence in Romulan space is.\n</p>\n</div>\n<h4><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Romulan_Republic_.28Federation-aligned.29\\">Romulan Republic (Federation-aligned)</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Cutting_the_Cord&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\\" title=\\"Edit section: Romulan Republic (Federation-aligned)\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h4>\n<div class=\\"missiontext\\">\n<p>Starfleet Intelligence has completed its analysis of the data you recovered in the Nopada system.\n</p><p>There is a 67.47 percent chance that the Iconians are using the Tal Shiar as a way to influence the Romulan Star Empire, and that their persecution of the Remans is directly related to this. Command is considering lending assistance to Obisek and his forces. As you have directly opposed the Tal Shiar in the past, your assistance has been requested.\n</p><p>The data indicates that Hakeev is operating out of the Brea system. Long-range sensor scans indicate that there may be a major Tal Shiar installation there. You understand Hakeev better than any of our officers, which gives you an advantage in destroying his installation.\n</p><p>Hakeev must not escape. He may be the only person who knows how extensive the Iconian influence in Romulan space is.\n</p>\n</div>\n"}]}}}}"""))
		missions.add(new Mission(text: """
{"query":{"pages":{"11535":{"pageid":11535,"ns":0,"title":"Mission: Darkness Before the Dawn","revisions":[{"*":"<div id=\\"toc\\" class=\\"toc\\"><div id=\\"toctitle\\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\\"><a href=\\"#Mission_Text\\"><span class=\\"tocnumber\\">1</span> <span class=\\"toctext\\">Mission Text</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\\"><a href=\\"#Federation\\"><span class=\\"tocnumber\\">1.1</span> <span class=\\"toctext\\">Federation</span></a></li>\n<li class=\\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\\"><a href=\\"#Klingon\\"><span class=\\"tocnumber\\">1.2</span> <span class=\\"toctext\\">Klingon</span></a></li>\n<li class=\\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\\"><a href=\\"#Romulan_Republic_.28Federation-aligned.29\\"><span class=\\"tocnumber\\">1.3</span> <span class=\\"toctext\\">Romulan Republic (Federation-aligned)</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h3><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Mission_Text\\">Mission Text</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Darkness_Before_the_Dawn&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\\" title=\\"Edit section: Mission Text\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h3>\n<h4><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Federation\\">Federation</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Darkness_Before_the_Dawn&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\\" title=\\"Edit section: Federation\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h4>\n<div class=\\"missiontext\\">\n<p>The Federation has offered the Reman resistance humanitarian aid, and we are working with them to find diplomatic solutions to their disputes with the Romulans.\n</p><p>Obisek has asked to speak with you. You can meet his ship in the Haakona system.\n</p><p>And once again, please accept my congratulations on a job well done.\n</p>\n</div>\n<h4><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Klingon\\">Klingon</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Darkness_Before_the_Dawn&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\\" title=\\"Edit section: Klingon\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h4>\n<div class=\\"missiontext\\">\n<p>I have been in contact with the Remans. The High Council wishes to seek an alliance with them. I do not necessarily agree, but it is not my place to question the will of the Council.\n</p><p>Obisek has aked to speak with you. You can meet his ship in the Haakona system.\n</p><p>You fought well. Continue to bring honor to your ship and your fleet, and you will be one of the heroes of the Empire.\n</p><p>Qapla'!\n</p>\n</div>\n<h4><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Romulan_Republic_.28Federation-aligned.29\\">Romulan Republic (Federation-aligned)</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Darkness_Before_the_Dawn&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\\" title=\\"Edit section: Romulan Republic (Federation-aligned)\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h4>\n<div class=\\"missiontext\\">\n<p>Obisek has aked to speak with you. You can meet his ship in the Haakona system.\n</p><p>Your involvement in this event has earned Obisek's respect ... and mine.\n</p>\n</div>\n"}]}}}}"""))
		missions.add(new Mission(text: """
{"query":{"pages":{"9324":{"pageid":9324,"ns":0,"title":"Mission: Skirmish","revisions":[{"*":"<div id=\\"toc\\" class=\\"toc\\"><div id=\\"toctitle\\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\\"><a href=\\"#Mission_Text\\"><span class=\\"tocnumber\\">1</span> <span class=\\"toctext\\">Mission Text</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\\"><a href=\\"#Federation\\"><span class=\\"tocnumber\\">1.1</span> <span class=\\"toctext\\">Federation</span></a></li>\n<li class=\\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\\"><a href=\\"#Klingon\\"><span class=\\"tocnumber\\">1.2</span> <span class=\\"toctext\\">Klingon</span></a></li>\n<li class=\\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\\"><a href=\\"#Romulan_Republic_.28Federation-allied.29\\"><span class=\\"tocnumber\\">1.3</span> <span class=\\"toctext\\">Romulan Republic (Federation-allied)</span></a></li>\n<li class=\\"toclevel-2 tocsection-5\\"><a href=\\"#Romulan_Republic_.28Klingon-allied.29\\"><span class=\\"tocnumber\\">1.4</span> <span class=\\"toctext\\">Romulan Republic (Klingon-allied)</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h3><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Mission_Text\\">Mission Text</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Skirmish&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\\" title=\\"Edit section: Mission Text\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h3>\n<h4><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Federation\\">Federation</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Skirmish&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\\" title=\\"Edit section: Federation\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h4>\n<div class=\\"missiontext\\">\n<p>We have reports of a <a href=\\"/True_Way\\" title=\\"True Way\\" class=\\"mw-redirect\\">True Way</a> fleet entering the <a href=\\"/Neutral_Zone\\" title=\\"Neutral Zone\\" class=\\"mw-redirect\\">Neutral Zone</a> and picking a fight with the Klingons near the <a href=\\"/Donatu_System\\" title=\\"Donatu System\\">Donatu system</a>.\n</p><p>Having two of our enemies fight is good for the Federation, but I want to know why the True Way is so far out of their territory. Intercept them and deal with them. If you need to engage the Klingons as well, do so.\n</p><p>A Starfleet task force has already been sent to the area; you'll need to join them in the Donatu system as soon as possible.\n</p>\n</div>\n<h4><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Klingon\\">Klingon</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Skirmish&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\\" title=\\"Edit section: Klingon\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h4>\n<div class=\\"missiontext\\">\n<p>We have reports of a True Way fleet entering the Neutral Zone and engaging our ships as well as Federation vessels near the Donatu system.  \n</p><p>We need you to intercept the True Way and learn why they are so far away from their territory. While you're there, destroy the Federation ships as well. \n</p><p>A small fleet has already been sent to the area; you'll need to join them in the Donatu system as soon as possible.\n</p>\n</div>\n<h4><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Romulan_Republic_.28Federation-allied.29\\">Romulan Republic (Federation-allied)</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Skirmish&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\\" title=\\"Edit section: Romulan Republic (Federation-allied)\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h4>\n<div class=\\"missiontext\\">\n<p>I always collect my debts, &lt;rank&gt;. I provided Tal'Mera with assets and materials to assist you in your recent encounters with the Tal Shiar. Now it's your turn to assist me.\n</p><p>We have reports of a True Way fleet entering the Neutral Zone and picking a fight with the Klingons near the Donatu system.  \n</p><p>Having two of our enemies fight is good for the Federation, but I want to know why the True Way is so far out of their territory. Intercept them and deal with them. If you need to engage the Klingons as well, do so. \n</p><p>A Starfleet task force has already been sent to the area; you'll need to join them in the Donatu system as soon as possible.\n</p>\n</div>\n<h4><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Romulan_Republic_.28Klingon-allied.29\\">Romulan Republic (Klingon-allied)</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Skirmish&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\\" title=\\"Edit section: Romulan Republic (Klingon-allied)\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h4>\n<div class=\\"missiontext\\">\n<p>Your Commander <a href=\\"/Tal%27Mera\\" title=\\"Tal'Mera\\">Tal'Mera</a> tells me she doesn't like owing debts. We provided information and assets to assist you in  your recent encounters with the Tal Shiar. Now we're calling in that marker.\n</p><p>We have reports of a True Way fleet entering the Neutral Zone and engaging our ships as well as Federation vessels near the Donatu system.  \n</p><p>We need you to intercept the True Way and learn why they are so far away from their territory. While you're there, destroy the Federation ships as well. \n</p><p>A small fleet has already been sent to the area; you'll need to join them in the Donatu system as soon as possible.\n</p>\n</div>\n"}]}}}}"""))
		missions.add(new Mission(text: """
{"query":{"pages":{"9342":{"pageid":9342,"ns":0,"title":"Mission: Spin the Wheel","revisions":[{"*":"<h3><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Mission_Text\\">Mission Text</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Spin_the_Wheel&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\\" title=\\"Edit section: Mission Text\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h3>\n<div class=\\"missiontext\\">\n<p>I need your assistance with a rather delicate situation.  \n</p><p>We have an intelligence operative undercover at Drozana Station. Her astute observations have given us the edge in several critical engagements in the Neutral Zone.  \n</p><p>Twenty-two hours ago, this operative activated an emergency subspace beacon. Ze'mara would only contact me in this manner if she was about to be discovered by the enemy or her life was in danger. I am understandably concerned.  \n</p><p>I need you to go to Drozana, find Ze'mara, and assist her. Take her to safety if you have to, but don't blow her cover. If you go in there weapons blazing, you may get her killed.  \n</p><p>I've accessed your logs. It's been quite some time since you had some shore leave. I suggest you visit Drozana for some ... down time.\n</p>\n</div>\n"}]}}}}"""))
		missions.add(new Mission(text: """
{"query":{"pages":{"9391":{"pageid":9391,"ns":0,"title":"Mission: What Lies Beneath","revisions":[{"*":"<h3><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Mission_Text\\">Mission Text</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_What_Lies_Beneath&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\\" title=\\"Edit section: Mission Text\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h3>\n<h4><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Federation\\">Federation</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_What_Lies_Beneath&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\\" title=\\"Edit section: Federation\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h4>\n<div class=\\"missiontext\\">\n<p>It's clear that the Devidians are more of a problem than we initally thought.\n</p><p>We know they're in the Neutral Zone. Now we know that they're on Drozana Station as well, and according to Ze'mara there have already been deaths there. In addition, she indicated that the lower levels of the station were a trouble spot.\n</p><p>Those levels aren't used as part of the club there, and they haven't been maintained for years. And the Ferengi are, of course, quite reticent to put any effort into any maintenance that isn't absolutely necessary. That means we don't really know what's down there.\n</p><p>Ze'mara's code should get you access. Take a lift down and check it out. Previous Starfleet encounters with Devidians have indicated that they will create \\"nests\\" around the temporal portals they use, so keep an eye out for anomalies. If we find the portal, we'll know where \u2013 and when \u2013 the Devidians are feeding.\n</p><p>Oh, and I expect it to be messy down there. Don't forget to take an emergency beacon.\n</p>\n</div>\n<h4><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Klingon\\">Klingon</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_What_Lies_Beneath&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\\" title=\\"Edit section: Klingon\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h4>\n<div class=\\"missiontext\\">\n<p>It's clear that the Devidians are more of a problem than we initially thought.\n</p><p>We know they're in the Neutral Zone. Now we know that they're on Drozana Station as well, and according to Ze'mara there have already been death there. In addition, she indicated that the lower levels of the station were a trouble spot.\n</p><p>Those levels aren't used as part of the club there, and they haven't been maintained for years. And the Ferengi are, of course, quite reticent to put any effort into any maintenance that isn't absolutely necessary. That means we don't really know what's down there. I want you to take a lift down and find out.\n</p><p>I have access to Starfleet records of encounters with Devidians that have indicated that they will create \\"nests\\" around the temporal portals they use, so keep an eye out for anomalies. If we find the portal, we'll know where \u2013 and when \u2013 the Devidians are feeding.\n</p>\n</div>\n"}]}}}}"""))
		missions.add(new Mission(text: """
{"query":{"pages":{"9402":{"pageid":9402,"ns":0,"title":"Mission: Everything Old is New","revisions":[{"*":"<h3><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Mission_Text\\">Mission Text</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Everything_Old_is_New&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\\" title=\\"Edit section: Mission Text\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h3>\n<h4><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Federation\\">Federation</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Everything_Old_is_New&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\\" title=\\"Edit section: Federation\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h4>\n<div class=\\"missiontext\\">\n<p>Obviously, the Devidians have found a way to harness this surge of triolic energy. The existence of the Devidian portal means they're traveling freely between the station in the present and the past.\n</p><p>Since 23rd century technology can't detect the Devidian phase-shift. that time period is rife with potential victims. The only choice now is to stop the incursion at the source.\n</p><p>You'll have to take that portal into the past and find out how the Devidians are creating this new surge of triolic energy. Stop them and find a way back without altering the timeline.\n</p><p>Don't worry about Temporal Investigations. I'll pull a few strings. They'll never know you were gone. Best to keep your team small, just in case.\n</p>\n</div>\n<h4><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Klingon\\">Klingon</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Everything_Old_is_New&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\\" title=\\"Edit section: Klingon\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h4>\n<div class=\\"missiontext\\">\n<p>The Devidians must have found some way to generate a portal at the station so that they can feed on the humans in the past. While the humans are no friends of ours, a shift in the balance of power in that sector of space could have drastic repercussions. There is no telling if it would be positive for the Empire ... or not.\n</p><p>We cannot take chances. You must head through the Devidian portal into the past and find out how they are creating the temporal fluctuations.\n</p><p>Fortunately, the Federation in the 23rd century will never recognize a Klingon from our time, so you may be able to pass unnoticed.\n</p><p>Oh, and just in case: Don't kill anyone. We wouldn't want to accidentally change the course of history. Keep your team small, for similar reasons.\n</p>\n</div>\n"}]}}}}"""))
		missions.add(new Mission(text: """
{"query":{"pages":{"9482":{"pageid":9482,"ns":0,"title":"Mission: Night of the Comet","revisions":[{"*":"<h3><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Mission_Text\\">Mission Text</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Night_of_the_Comet&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\\" title=\\"Edit section: Mission Text\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h3>\n<div class=\\"missiontext\\">\n<p>We've determined that the Devidians are using the triolic energy of Driffen's Comet to ease their entry into our phase variance. That is the cause of all of the incidents in the neutral zone.\n</p><p>But it's worse than that. It's possible that, given the amount of triolic and temporal energy in that comet, that the Devidians will be able to destabilize the area of space surrounding the comet enough that they will pull it and everything in it into their phase variance.\n</p><p>In essence, they're trying to \\"steal\\" an entire sector. The resulting effects to the surrounding space would make the the destruction of Romulus look like the popping of a party favor.\n</p><p>The only thing we can do to stop it is destroy the comet before the Devidians can use it. It's not enough to do it in the present, because the Devidians would still have access in the 23rd century when the comet moves past Drozana Station. We have to destroy it there.\n</p><p>You'll need your ship this time, so you can't use the Devidian portal on the station. I can help you get to the past, but you'll need to follow my instructions precisely.\n</p><p>Good luck.\n</p>\n</div>\n"}]}}}}"""))
		missions.add(new Mission(text: """
{"query":{"pages":{"2604":{"pageid":2604,"ns":0,"title":"Mission: Venture into Deep Space","revisions":[{"*":"<h4><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Federation\\">Federation</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Venture_into_Deep_Space&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\\" title=\\"Edit section: Federation\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h4>\n<div class=\\"missiontext\\">\n<p>I have a new assignment for you, <b>&lt;rank&gt;</b>.\n</p><p>Captain Kurland at Deep Space 9 is requesting Starfleet assistance with several problems he has in that area, most notable the <a href=\\"/True_Way\\" title=\\"True Way\\" class=\\"mw-redirect\\">True Way</a>.\n</p><p>That group is an organization of Cardassians who want a return to the old methods of conquest and ruling through fear. They oppose the social reforms put in place by the Cardassian Detapa Council, and they want all Federation personnel and assets removed from Cardassian space. The Federation has made a commitment to the Cardassian people to help them on the road to freedom and democracy. We will not allow a group of malcontents and fearmongers to stop us.\n</p><p>I'm sending the <b>&lt;ship name&gt;</b> to DS9 to assist Captain Kurland. He's a fine officer, <b>&lt;rank&gt;</b>. I predict you and he will work well together.\n</p>\n</div>\n"}]}}}}"""))
		missions.add(new Mission(text: """
{"query":{"pages":{"2982":{"pageid":2982,"ns":0,"title":"Mission: Badlands","revisions":[{"*":"<div id=\\"toc\\" class=\\"toc\\"><div id=\\"toctitle\\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\\"><a href=\\"#Mission_Text\\"><span class=\\"tocnumber\\">1</span> <span class=\\"toctext\\">Mission Text</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\\"><a href=\\"#Federation\\"><span class=\\"tocnumber\\">1.1</span> <span class=\\"toctext\\">Federation</span></a></li>\n<li class=\\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\\"><a href=\\"#Klingon\\"><span class=\\"tocnumber\\">1.2</span> <span class=\\"toctext\\">Klingon</span></a></li>\n<li class=\\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\\"><a href=\\"#Romulan\\"><span class=\\"tocnumber\\">1.3</span> <span class=\\"toctext\\">Romulan</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Mission_Text\\">Mission Text</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Badlands&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\\" title=\\"Edit section: Mission Text\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Federation\\">Federation</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Badlands&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\\" title=\\"Edit section: Federation\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h3>\n<div class=\\"missiontext\\">\n<p><b>&lt;rank&gt;</b>, I'm getting dozens of reports of raiders hitting civilian ships near the <a href=\\"/Badlands_System\\" title=\\"Badlands System\\">Badlands</a>. <a href=\\"/Starfleet\\" title=\\"Starfleet\\">Starfleet</a> Intelligence believes that the raids are related to <a href=\\"/True_Way\\" title=\\"True Way\\" class=\\"mw-redirect\\">True Way</a> activity in that region.\n</p><p>We know that area is a haven for smugglers and criminals of all types. It stands to reason that the <a href=\\"/True_Way\\" title=\\"True Way\\" class=\\"mw-redirect\\">True Way</a> are using it to avoid capture as well. They might even be using some kind of Maquis base that was abandoned before the Cardassian war.\n</p><p>I know the Badlands are dangerous, but I have complete confidence in the <b>&lt;shipname&gt;</b> and her crew.\n</p>\n</div>\n<h3><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Klingon\\">Klingon</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Badlands&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\\" title=\\"Edit section: Klingon\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h3>\n<div class=\\"missiontext\\">\n<p><b>&lt;rank&gt;</b>, we have received reports of so-called \\"<a href=\\"/True_Way\\" title=\\"True Way\\" class=\\"mw-redirect\\">True Way</a>\\" activists in the <a href=\\"/Badlands_System\\" title=\\"Badlands System\\">Badlands</a>, a region of turbulent nebula-like activity near Deep Space 9. The True Way are made up of Cardassians and Dominion elements that refuse to recognize the treaty signed by their government after the Klingon Empire destroyed Cardassia's military power.\n</p><p>The Badlands are a haven for smugglers and criminals of all types. It stands to reason that the True Way are using it to avoid capture as well. They may have even occupied old fortifications used by criminal Federation elements from before the Dominion War.\n</p><p>The Badlands are dangerous and filled with hostile ships. This should be a worthy challenge for the &lt;shipname&gt;. Show the True Way why they should not be so quick to draw the ire of the Empire!\n</p>\n</div>\n<h3><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Romulan\\">Romulan</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Badlands&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\\" title=\\"Edit section: Romulan\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h3>\n<div class=\\"missiontext\\">\n<p><b>&lt;rank&gt;</b>, I'm getting dozens of reports of raiders hitting civilian ships near the Badlands. Starfleet Intelligence believes that the raids are related to True Way activity in that region.\n</p><p>I know that this is a bit far from the Romulan Republic, but this kind of commerce raiding has a tendency to get out of hand if it's not handled quickly and decisively. The last thing we need is the True Way expanding its operations and becoming involved with the Tal Shiar or other organized groups.\n</p><p>The Badlands are a fairly dangerous region of space, but you've already shown that the <b>&lt;shipname&gt;</b> can handle a little danger.\n</p>\n</div>\n"}]}}}}"""))
		missions.add(new Mission(text: """
{"query":{"pages":{"3329":{"pageid":3329,"ns":0,"title":"Mission: Rapier","revisions":[{"*":"<h3><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Federation\\">Federation</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Rapier&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\\" title=\\"Edit section: Federation\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h3>\n<div class=\\"missiontext\\">\n<p><b>&lt;rank&gt;</b>, we have an opportunity to solve one of the greatest mysteries of the past decade.\n</p><p>Six years ago, the <a href=\\"/U.S.S._Rapier\\" title=\\"U.S.S. Rapier\\">U.S.S. Rapier</a> was on its first mission \u2013 a routine trip through the wormhole to survey several planets in the <a href=\\"/Gamma_Quadrant\\" title=\\"Gamma Quadrant\\">Gamma Quadrant</a>. It entered the wormhole and was never heard from again.\n</p><p><a href=\\"/Starfleet\\" title=\\"Starfleet\\">Starfleet</a> believed the ship had been destroyed but several hours ago we picked up an emergency distress signal on a frequency that corresponds with the Rapier. We have to investigate.\n</p><p>Your top priority is to rescue any survivors that might be on board, but the Rapier is special. She's the first of her class, and she has technology on board that is the basis for much of what <a href=\\"/Starfleet\\" title=\\"Starfleet\\">Starfleet</a> uses today. If she were to fall into enemy hands the damage to Starfleet would be significant.\n</p><p>If you find the Rapier, try to bring her home. But I'd rather have her destroyed than in <a href=\\"/Dominion\\" title=\\"Dominion\\">Dominion</a> hands.\n</p>\n</div>\n"}]}}}}"""))
		missions.add(new Mission(text: """
{"query":{"pages":{"3473":{"pageid":3473,"ns":0,"title":"Mission: Forging Bonds","revisions":[{"*":"<div id=\\"toc\\" class=\\"toc\\"><div id=\\"toctitle\\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\\"><a href=\\"#Outline\\"><span class=\\"tocnumber\\">1</span> <span class=\\"toctext\\">Outline</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\\"><a href=\\"#Mission_Text\\"><span class=\\"tocnumber\\">1.1</span> <span class=\\"toctext\\">Mission Text</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\\"toclevel-3 tocsection-3\\"><a href=\\"#Federation\\"><span class=\\"tocnumber\\">1.1.1</span> <span class=\\"toctext\\">Federation</span></a></li>\n<li class=\\"toclevel-3 tocsection-4\\"><a href=\\"#Klingon\\"><span class=\\"tocnumber\\">1.1.2</span> <span class=\\"toctext\\">Klingon</span></a></li>\n<li class=\\"toclevel-3 tocsection-5\\"><a href=\\"#Romulan_.28Federation-aligned.29\\"><span class=\\"tocnumber\\">1.1.3</span> <span class=\\"toctext\\">Romulan (Federation-aligned)</span></a></li>\n<li class=\\"toclevel-3 tocsection-6\\"><a href=\\"#Romulan_.28Klingon-aligned.29\\"><span class=\\"tocnumber\\">1.1.4</span> <span class=\\"toctext\\">Romulan (Klingon-aligned)</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\\"toclevel-2 tocsection-7\\"><a href=\\"#Goal\\"><span class=\\"tocnumber\\">1.2</span> <span class=\\"toctext\\">Goal</span></a></li>\n<li class=\\"toclevel-2 tocsection-8\\"><a href=\\"#Objectives\\"><span class=\\"tocnumber\\">1.3</span> <span class=\\"toctext\\">Objectives</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Outline\\">Outline</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Forging_Bonds&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\\" title=\\"Edit section: Outline\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Mission_Text\\">Mission Text</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Forging_Bonds&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\\" title=\\"Edit section: Mission Text\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h3>\n<h4><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Federation\\">Federation</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Forging_Bonds&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\\" title=\\"Edit section: Federation\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h4>\n<div class=\\"missiontext\\">\n<p><b>&lt;rank&gt;</b>, your new assignment is to patrol the <a href=\\"/Algira_System\\" title=\\"Algira System\\">Algira system</a>.\n</p><p>The <a href=\\"/True_Way\\" title=\\"True Way\\" class=\\"mw-redirect\\">True Way</a> considers themselves to be the true leaders of <a href=\\"/Cardassia\\" title=\\"Cardassia\\" class=\\"mw-redirect\\">Cardassia</a> \u2013 a sort of government in exile. As far as the <a href=\\"/Federation\\" title=\\"Federation\\" class=\\"mw-redirect\\">Federation</a> and the <a href=\\"/Cardassian\\" title=\\"Cardassian\\">Cardassian</a> <a href=\\"/index.php?title=Detapa_Council&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\\" class=\\"new\\" title=\\"Detapa Council (page does not exist)\\">Detapa Council</a> are concerned, they're little better than terrorists.\n</p><p>The True Way has been harassing ships through the sector, but the Algira system seems to be a focal point for their activity. <a href=\\"/Starfleet\\" title=\\"Starfleet\\">Starfleet</a> wants to know why.\n</p><p>Patrol the system and assist any ships in trouble. Maybe the presence of the <b>&lt;shipname&gt;.</b> in the area will convince the True Way that their campaign against the Federation is more trouble than it's worth.\n</p>\n</div>\n<h4><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Klingon\\">Klingon</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Forging_Bonds&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\\" title=\\"Edit section: Klingon\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h4>\n<div class=\\"missiontext\\">\n<p><b>&lt;rank&gt;</b>, your new assignment is to patrol the Algira system.  \n</p><p>The True Way considers themselves to be the true leaders of Cardassia -- a sort of government in exile. As far as both the Federation and the Empire are concerned, they're little better than terrorists.  \n</p><p>The True Way has been harassing ships throughout the sector, but the Algira system seems to be a focal point for their activity. That makes it the most sensible place to start searching for them. \n</p><p>Patrol the system and engage any True Way ships that you find. Perhaps the presence of the <b>&lt;shipname&gt;</b> will convince the True Way that it is not worth their trouble to attract the attentions of the Empire!\n</p>\n</div>\n<h4><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Romulan_.28Federation-aligned.29\\">Romulan (Federation-aligned)</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Forging_Bonds&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\\" title=\\"Edit section: Romulan (Federation-aligned)\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h4>\n<div class=\\"missiontext\\">\n<p><b>&lt;rank&gt;</b>, I need you to look into some disturbing rumors from the Algira system.\n</p><p>The True Way considers themselves to be the true leaders of Cardassia \u2013 a sort of government in exile. As far as the Federation and the Cardassian Detapa Council are concerned, they're little better than terrorists. Worse still, they contain elements of the old <a href=\\"/index.php?title=Obsidian_Order&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\\" class=\\"new\\" title=\\"Obsidian Order (page does not exist)\\">Obsidian Order</a>, who have ties to the <a href=\\"/Tal_Shiar\\" title=\\"Tal Shiar\\">Tal Shiar</a>, and I don't need to remind you of how bad that situation is.\n</p><p>The True Way has been harassing ships throughout the sector, but the Algira system seems to be a focal point for their activity. With your skill in gathering intelligence and information, I'd like to ask the <b>&lt;shipname&gt;</b> to head to that system and take a look.\n</p>\n</div>\n<h4><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Romulan_.28Klingon-aligned.29\\">Romulan (Klingon-aligned)</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Forging_Bonds&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\\" title=\\"Edit section: Romulan (Klingon-aligned)\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h4>\n<div class=\\"missiontext\\">\n<p><b>&lt;rank&gt;</b>, new information has placed elements of the True Way in the Algira system. Your expertise at information gathering may be useful in discovering exactly what they are planning.\n</p><p>It is likely that the True Way are looking for allies. Let us be certain that they do not find any.\n</p><p>Patrol the system and discover what you can about True Way organization in that sector. Perhaps the presence of the <b>&lt;ship name&gt;</b> will convince the True Way that it is not worth their trouble to attract the attention of the Empire!\n</p>\n</div>\n<h3><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Goal\\">Goal</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Forging_Bonds&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7\\" title=\\"Edit section: Goal\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h3>\n<div class=\\"missiongoal\\">Patrol the Algira System, located in the Algira Sector of the Alpha Trianguli Sector Block, and look for signs of True Way activity.</div>\n<h3><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Objectives\\">Objectives</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Forging_Bonds&amp;action=edit&amp;section=8\\" title=\\"Edit section: Objectives\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h3>\n<ul>\n<li> Transport Trouble\n<ul>\n<li> Go To <a href=\\"/Algira_System\\" title=\\"Algira System\\">Algira System</a>\n</li>\n<li> Rescue the Batris\n</li>\n<li> Analyse the Situation\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li> Miners under Siege\n<ul>\n<li> Defeat Cardassian Squadrons (0/3)\n</li>\n<li> Destroy Turret Emplacements (0/4)\n</li>\n<li> Beam to Planet\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li> Beating the Drums of War\n<ul>\n<li> Go To Algira III\n</li>\n<li> Scan Buildings Near Mining Site (0/4)\n</li>\n<li> Locate Replication Facility Entrance\n</li>\n<li> Enter Replication Facility\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li> Breached Defenses\n<ul>\n<li> Go To Algira III Mining Facility\n</li>\n<li> Sabotage Replicators (0/3)\n</li>\n<li> Destroy the Control Room (0/3)\n</li>\n<li> Return to Ship\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li> Armed Resistance\n<ul>\n<li> Go To Algira System\n</li>\n<li> Destroy True Way Squadrons (0/3)\n</li>\n<li> Return to Sector Space\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li> Report to Starfleet / Report to Ambassador S'taass\n</li>\n</ul>\n"}]}}}}"""))
		missions.add(new Mission(text: """
{"query":{"pages":{"4157":{"pageid":4157,"ns":0,"title":"Mission: The Long Night","revisions":[{"*":"<div id=\\"toc\\" class=\\"toc\\"><div id=\\"toctitle\\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\\"><a href=\\"#Outline\\"><span class=\\"tocnumber\\">1</span> <span class=\\"toctext\\">Outline</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\\"><a href=\\"#Mission_Text\\"><span class=\\"tocnumber\\">1.1</span> <span class=\\"toctext\\">Mission Text</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\\"toclevel-3 tocsection-3\\"><a href=\\"#Federation\\"><span class=\\"tocnumber\\">1.1.1</span> <span class=\\"toctext\\">Federation</span></a></li>\n<li class=\\"toclevel-3 tocsection-4\\"><a href=\\"#Klingon\\"><span class=\\"tocnumber\\">1.1.2</span> <span class=\\"toctext\\">Klingon</span></a></li>\n<li class=\\"toclevel-3 tocsection-5\\"><a href=\\"#Romulan_.28Federation-aligned.29\\"><span class=\\"tocnumber\\">1.1.3</span> <span class=\\"toctext\\">Romulan (Federation-aligned)</span></a></li>\n<li class=\\"toclevel-3 tocsection-6\\"><a href=\\"#Romulan_.28Klingon-aligned.29\\"><span class=\\"tocnumber\\">1.1.4</span> <span class=\\"toctext\\">Romulan (Klingon-aligned)</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\\"toclevel-2 tocsection-7\\"><a href=\\"#Goal\\"><span class=\\"tocnumber\\">1.2</span> <span class=\\"toctext\\">Goal</span></a></li>\n<li class=\\"toclevel-2 tocsection-8\\"><a href=\\"#Objectives\\"><span class=\\"tocnumber\\">1.3</span> <span class=\\"toctext\\">Objectives</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Outline\\">Outline</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_The_Long_Night&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\\" title=\\"Edit section: Outline\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Mission_Text\\">Mission Text</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_The_Long_Night&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\\" title=\\"Edit section: Mission Text\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h3>\n<h4><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Federation\\">Federation</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_The_Long_Night&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\\" title=\\"Edit section: Federation\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h4>\n<div class=\\"missiontext\\">\n<p>Starfleet Intelligence has received information that leads us to believe that the leaders of the <a href=\\"/True_Way\\" title=\\"True Way\\" class=\\"mw-redirect\\">True Way</a> are on Empok Nor.\n</p><p>The <a href=\\"/Cardassian\\" title=\\"Cardassian\\">Cardassians</a> abandoned the station decades ago. It's practically space junk now, and lingering memories of the Occupation keep most people away.\n</p><p>A good friend of the <a href=\\"/Federation\\" title=\\"Federation\\" class=\\"mw-redirect\\">Federation</a>, <a href=\\"/index.php?title=Elim_Garak&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\\" class=\\"new\\" title=\\"Elim Garak (page does not exist)\\">Elim Garak</a>, has provided us with a passcode that should get you into the Central Corridor. But to use it, you'll have to dock at Empok Nor and send an away team through the docking ring.\n</p><p>I know this is dangerous, <b>&lt;name&gt;</b>, but we have a chance to end the threat of the True Way for good.\n</p>\n</div>\n<h4><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Klingon\\">Klingon</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_The_Long_Night&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\\" title=\\"Edit section: Klingon\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h4>\n<h4><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Romulan_.28Federation-aligned.29\\">Romulan (Federation-aligned)</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_The_Long_Night&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\\" title=\\"Edit section: Romulan (Federation-aligned)\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h4>\n<div class=\\"missiontext\\">\n<p>Starfleet Intelligence has received information that leads us to believe that the leaders of the True Way are on Empok Nor.\n</p><p>The Cardassians abandoned the station decades ago. It's practically space junk now, and lingering memories of the Occupation keep most people away.\n</p><p>I've acquired some personal passcodes that will allow you to enter the station and get past some of its internal security. We need to end the threat of the True Way, and capturing their leaders from their own base is a good way to solve this in one swift strike.\n</p><p>I won't undersell this: the True Way are dangerous, and this mission won't be without risks. I wouldn't ask for your help if I weren't confident in your ability to pull this off, <b>&lt;name&gt;</b>.\n</p>\n</div>\n<h4><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Romulan_.28Klingon-aligned.29\\">Romulan (Klingon-aligned)</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_The_Long_Night&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\\" title=\\"Edit section: Romulan (Klingon-aligned)\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h4>\n<div class=\\"missiontext\\">\n<p>Our analysis of True Way movements in the area has led us to believe that their leaders are using the ancient Cardassian space station known as Empok Nor.\n</p><p>The station was once a base for Cardassian work impressment and defenses, but it is now little more than space junk. It is remote enough and secure enough for the True Way to use it while avoiding detection.\n</p><p>The Klingon Defense Force has acquired certain military override codes that will grant access to much of the station. I'm sure that your people would be just as interested as mine in accessing whatever information the True Way has hidden away in the station's data banks.\n</p>\n</div>\n<h3><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Goal\\">Goal</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_The_Long_Night&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7\\" title=\\"Edit section: Goal\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h3>\n<div class=\\"missiongoal\\">Find the leaders of the True Way on the abandoned space station Empok Nor in the Trivas System, located in the Almatha Sector of the Alpha Trianguli Sector Block.</div>\n<h3><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Objectives\\">Objectives</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_The_Long_Night&amp;action=edit&amp;section=8\\" title=\\"Edit section: Objectives\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h3>\n<ul>\n<li> Empok Nor\n<ul>\n<li> Go To <a href=\\"/Trivas_System\\" title=\\"Trivas System\\">Trivas System</a>\n</li>\n<li> Defeat True Way Squadrons (0/4)\n</li>\n<li> Dock with Empok Nor\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li> Breaking and Entering\n<ul>\n<li> Go To Empok Nor\n</li>\n<li> Destroy Laser Tripwire Consoles (optional) (0/3)\n</li>\n<li> Use Security Console\n</li>\n<li> Analyze Situation\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li> Cut the Ties\n<ul>\n<li> Deactivate Subspace Communications\n</li>\n<li> Activate Ventilation Systems (0/3)\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li> Wanted\n<ul>\n<li> Subdue and Beam Up <a href=\\"/Madred\\" title=\\"Madred\\">Gul Madred</a>\n</li>\n<li> Disarm Bombs Hidden in Crates (0/3)\n</li>\n<li> Return to Ship\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li> On The Run\n<ul>\n<li> Go To Trivas System\n</li>\n<li> Destroy Inner Ring Turrets\n</li>\n<li> Destroy Outer Ring Turrets\n</li>\n<li> Defeat True Way Squadrons (0/3)\n</li>\n<li> Return to Sector Space\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li> Report to Starfleet \n</li>\n</ul>\n"}]}}}}"""))
