{"query":{"pages":{"4515":{"pageid":4515,"ns":0,"title":"Mission: Crack in the Mirror","revisions":[{"*":"<div id=\\"toc\\" class=\\"toc\\"><div id=\\"toctitle\\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\\"><a href=\\"#Outline\\"><span class=\\"tocnumber\\">1</span> <span class=\\"toctext\\">Outline</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\\"><a href=\\"#Mission_Text\\"><span class=\\"tocnumber\\">1.1</span> <span class=\\"toctext\\">Mission Text</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\\"toclevel-3 tocsection-3\\"><a href=\\"#Federation\\"><span class=\\"tocnumber\\">1.1.1</span> <span class=\\"toctext\\">Federation</span></a></li>\n<li class=\\"toclevel-3 tocsection-4\\"><a href=\\"#Klingon\\"><span class=\\"tocnumber\\">1.1.2</span> <span class=\\"toctext\\">Klingon</span></a></li>\n<li class=\\"toclevel-3 tocsection-5\\"><a href=\\"#Romulan_.28Federation-aligned.29\\"><span class=\\"tocnumber\\">1.1.3</span> <span class=\\"toctext\\">Romulan (Federation-aligned)</span></a></li>\n<li class=\\"toclevel-3 tocsection-6\\"><a href=\\"#Romulan_.28Klingon-aligned.29\\"><span class=\\"tocnumber\\">1.1.4</span> <span class=\\"toctext\\">Romulan (Klingon-aligned)</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\\"toclevel-2 tocsection-7\\"><a href=\\"#Goal\\"><span class=\\"tocnumber\\">1.2</span> <span class=\\"toctext\\">Goal</span></a></li>\n<li class=\\"toclevel-2 tocsection-8\\"><a href=\\"#Objectives\\"><span class=\\"tocnumber\\">1.3</span> <span class=\\"toctext\\">Objectives</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Outline\\">Outline</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Crack_in_the_Mirror&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\\" title=\\"Edit section: Outline\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Mission_Text\\">Mission Text</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Crack_in_the_Mirror&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\\" title=\\"Edit section: Mission Text\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h3>\n<h4><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Federation\\">Federation</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Crack_in_the_Mirror&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\\" title=\\"Edit section: Federation\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h4>\n<div class=\\"missiontext\\">\n<p>Hello, <b>&lt;rank&gt;</b>. I'm short-handed and I need some help.\n</p><p>We've been experiencing intermittent power failures in half a dozen systems today. Internal communications and sensors are down, and we've got forcefields popping up in odd places.\n</p><p><a href=\\"/DS9\\" title=\\"DS9\\" class=\\"mw-redirect\\">DS9</a> is an old station, but this is getting ridiculous!\n</p><p>All my Engineering teams are out fixing problems. I need my Chief Engineer in Ops to coordinate the repairs, but he went to the docking ring more than an hour ago to fix a fused power coupling and now I can't reach him.\n</p><p>Will you go find Commander Maxwell and escort him to Ops? I'd really appreciate the assistance.\n</p>\n</div>\n<h4><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Klingon\\">Klingon</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Crack_in_the_Mirror&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\\" title=\\"Edit section: Klingon\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h4>\n<div class=\\"missiontext\\">\n<p><b>Rank</b>, this station has been experiencing odd power failures and sudden force field appearances for several hours now. Captain Kurland isn't giving me any information, but his senior officer are suddenly very busy.\n</p><p>I want to know what's going on. Chief Engineer Maxwell has been gone for two hours, and there are no signs of the problems abating. Head to the cargo ring and see if you can find out what's happening.\n</p>\n</div>\n<h4><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Romulan_.28Federation-aligned.29\\">Romulan (Federation-aligned)</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Crack_in_the_Mirror&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\\" title=\\"Edit section: Romulan (Federation-aligned)\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h4>\n<div class=\\"missiontext\\">\n<p>Hello, <b>&lt;rank&gt;</b>. I'm short-handed and I need some help.\n</p><p>We've been experiencing intermittent power failures in half a dozen systems today. Internal communications and sensors are down, and we've got forcefields popping up in odd places.\n</p><p>DS9 is an old station, but this is getting ridiculous!\n</p><p>Would you mind hunting down Commander Maxwell for me? The computer registers his combadge out on the ring. I know it's a bit of a chore, but at least it should be pretty straightforward.\n</p>\n</div>\n<h4><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Romulan_.28Klingon-aligned.29\\">Romulan (Klingon-aligned)</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Crack_in_the_Mirror&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\\" title=\\"Edit section: Romulan (Klingon-aligned)\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h4>\n<div class=\\"missiontext\\">\n<p><b>Rank</b>, this station has been experiencing odd power failures and sudden force field appearances for several hours now. Captain Kurland isn't giving me any information, but his senior officer are suddenly very busy.\n</p><p>I want to know what's going on. Chief Engineer Maxwell has been gone for two hours, and there are no signs of the problems abating. Head to the cargo ring and see if you can find out what's happening.\n</p>\n</div>\n<h3><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Goal\\">Goal</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Crack_in_the_Mirror&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7\\" title=\\"Edit section: Goal\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h3>\n<div class=\\"missiongoal\\">Find Commander Maxwell. He should be in the cargo ring of DS9.</div>\n<h3><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Objectives\\">Objectives</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Crack_in_the_Mirror&amp;action=edit&amp;section=8\\" title=\\"Edit section: Objectives\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h3>\n<ul>\n<li> Go to DS9 Cargo Ring\n<ul>\n<li> Go To Deep Space Nine\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li> Invasion\n<ul>\n<li> Locate Commander Maxwell\n</li>\n<li> Lower Force Field\n</li>\n<li> Deactivate the Devices (0/5)\n</li>\n<li> Beam to Ship\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li> Fight or Flee\n<ul>\n<li> Go To Deep Space Nine System\n</li>\n<li> Stop the Mirror Troop Transports\n</li>\n<li> Destroy the Mirror Escorts\n</li>\n<li> Warp to <a href=\\"/Bajor_VII\\" title=\\"Bajor VII\\">Bajor VII</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li> Staging Point\n<ul>\n<li> Go To <a href=\\"/Bajor_System\\" title=\\"Bajor System\\">Bajor System</a>\n</li>\n<li> Destroy the Mirror Universe Ships\n</li>\n<li> Beam Down to Mining Facility\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li> Mine Investigation\n<ul>\n<li> Go To Bajor VII Mining Station\n</li>\n<li> Investigate Mining Facility\n<ul>\n<li> Search for Clues (0/2)\n</li>\n<li> Locate the Mirror Leader\n</li>\n<li> Speak with Mirror Leader\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li> Return to Ship\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li> O'Brien's Folly <small>[<a href=\\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sic\\" class=\\"extiw\\" title=\\"w:Sic\\"><i>sic</i></a>]</small>\n<ul>\n<li> Go To Bajor System\n</li>\n<li> Incoming Message\n</li>\n<li> Destroy Mirror Universe Ships\n</li>\n<li> Follow <a href=\\"/James_O%27Brien\\" title=\\"James O'Brien\\">O'Brien</a> to <a href=\\"/DS9\\" title=\\"DS9\\" class=\\"mw-redirect\\">DS9</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li> Seek and Destroy\n<ul>\n<li> Go To Deep Space Nine System\n</li>\n<li> Defeat Mirror Ships\n</li>\n<li> Incoming Message\n</li>\n<li> Defeat O'Brien\n</li>\n<li> Destroy the Mirror Runabouts\n</li>\n<li> Scan the Wormhole\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li> Strange Readings\n<ul>\n<li> Go To Celestial Temple\n</li>\n<li> Speak to The Prophet\n</li>\n<li> Leave the Temple\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n<li> Report to <i>&lt;mission giver&gt;</i>\n</li>\n</ul>\n"}]}}}}"""))
