{"query":{"pages":{"24244":{"pageid":24244,"ns":0,"title":"Mission: Of Bajor","revisions":[{"*":"<div id=\\"toc\\" class=\\"toc\\"><div id=\\"toctitle\\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\\"><a href=\\"#Outline\\"><span class=\\"tocnumber\\">1</span> <span class=\\"toctext\\">Outline</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\\"><a href=\\"#Mission_Text\\"><span class=\\"tocnumber\\">1.1</span> <span class=\\"toctext\\">Mission Text</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\\"toclevel-3 tocsection-3\\"><a href=\\"#Federation\\"><span class=\\"tocnumber\\">1.1.1</span> <span class=\\"toctext\\">Federation</span></a></li>\n<li class=\\"toclevel-3 tocsection-4\\"><a href=\\"#Klingon\\"><span class=\\"tocnumber\\">1.1.2</span> <span class=\\"toctext\\">Klingon</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\\"toclevel-2 tocsection-5\\"><a href=\\"#Goal\\"><span class=\\"tocnumber\\">1.2</span> <span class=\\"toctext\\">Goal</span></a></li>\n<li class=\\"toclevel-2 tocsection-6\\"><a href=\\"#Objectives\\"><span class=\\"tocnumber\\">1.3</span> <span class=\\"toctext\\">Objectives</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Outline\\">Outline</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Of_Bajor&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\\" title=\\"Edit section: Outline\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Mission_Text\\">Mission Text</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Of_Bajor&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\\" title=\\"Edit section: Mission Text\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h3>\n<h4><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Federation\\">Federation</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Of_Bajor&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\\" title=\\"Edit section: Federation\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h4>\n<div class=\\"missiontext\\">\n<p>We've evacuated everyone we can to Bajor, and we're setting up a base there to coordinate our counter-attack against the Dominion.\n</p><p>I won't lie to you though \u2013 it's not going to be easy. We were caught completely off guard by Kar'ukan and his fleet. And the Bajorans are none too pleased to have houseguests. We must balance the needs of the civillian populace with those of the Starfleet and Klingon forces currently on the surface.\n</p><p>Starfleet needs all the help it can get planetside now. Transport down to our staging area there. You'll find me there.\n</p><p>Captain Kurland will join us as soon as he can.\n</p>\n</div>\n<h4><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Klingon\\">Klingon</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Of_Bajor&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\\" title=\\"Edit section: Klingon\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h4>\n<div class=\\"missiontext\\">\n<p>We have evacuated everyone we can to Bajor, and we're setting up a base there to coordinate our counter-attack against the Dominion.\n</p><p>I won't lie to you though \u2013 it's not going to be easy. We were caught completely off guard by Kar'ukan and his fleet. And the Bajorans are none too pleased to have houseguests.\n</p><p>You proved yourself in the fight against the Dominion on DS9, and right now I can use all the help I can get. Your government has agreed to allow you to assist in our campaign, and we'll have a better chance of defeating the Jem'Hadar with warriors like you on our side.\n</p><p>Transport down to our staging area on Bajor. You'll find me there.\n</p><p>Captain Kurland will join us as soon as he can.\n</p>\n</div>\n<h3><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Goal\\">Goal</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Of_Bajor&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\\" title=\\"Edit section: Goal\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h3>\n<div class=\\"missiongoal\\">Report to Commander Mesi Achebe on Bajor, which is located in the Bajor Sector of the Beta Ursae Sector Block.</div>\n<h3><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Objectives\\">Objectives</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Of_Bajor&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\\" title=\\"Edit section: Objectives\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h3>\n<div class=\\"thumb tright\\"><div class=\\"thumbinner\\" style=\\"width:182px;\\"><a href=\\"/File:Mesi_Achebe.png\\" class=\\"image\\"><img alt=\\"\\" src=\\"http://hydra-media.cursecdn.com/sto.gamepedia.com/thumb/8/8a/Mesi_Achebe.png/180px-Mesi_Achebe.png?version=aa0491d43b5f1985c8747125042ce6ed\\" width=\\"180\\" height=\\"211\\" class=\\"thumbimage\\" srcset=\\"http://hydra-media.cursecdn.com/sto.gamepedia.com/thumb/8/8a/Mesi_Achebe.png/270px-Mesi_Achebe.png 1.5x, http://hydra-media.cursecdn.com/sto.gamepedia.com/8/8a/Mesi_Achebe.png 2x\\" /></a>  <div class=\\"thumbcaption\\"><div class=\\"magnify\\"><a href=\\"/File:Mesi_Achebe.png\\" class=\\"internal\\" title=\\"Enlarge\\"><img src=\\"/skins/common/images/magnify-clip.png\\" width=\\"15\\" height=\\"11\\" alt=\\"\\" /></a></div><a href=\\"/Mesi_Achebe\\" title=\\"Mesi Achebe\\">Mesi Achebe</a></div></div></div>\n<ul>\n<li> Go to Bajor: Hathon\n</li>\n<li> Report to Commander <a href=\\"/Mesi_Achebe\\" title=\\"Mesi Achebe\\">Mesi Achebe</a> on Bajor.\n</li>\n<li> Report to Lieutenant <a href=\\"/Jirelle_Kav\\" title=\\"Jirelle Kav\\">Jirelle Kav</a>\n</li>\n<li> Help Set Up the Base\n<ul>\n<li> Get a Mission From Jirelle Kav\n</li>\n<li> [Starfleet] Aggressive Assimilation\n<ul>\n<li> Break up Arguments in the Bar\n</li>\n<li> Assist Bajorans in the Alleys\n</li>\n<li> Calm Down Klingons at the Checkpoint\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li> [KDF] Eavesdropping on Electronics\n<ul>\n<li> Bug the Starfleet Base\n<ul>\n<li> Plant a Bug Inside Starfleet Command\n</li>\n<li> Plant a Bug Outside Starfleet Command\n</li>\n<li> Plant a Bug Inside the <a href=\\"/Holodeck\\" title=\\"Holodeck\\">Holodeck</a>\n</li>\n<li> Plant a Bug Inside Starfleet Operations\n</li>\n<li> Plant a Bug Inside the <a href=\\"/Chief_Medical_Officer_(Hathon)\\" title=\\"Chief Medical Officer (Hathon)\\">Chief Medical Officer's</a> Office\n</li>\n<li> Plant a Bug Inside Infirmary\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li> [Science] Walking Wounded\n<ul>\n<li> Escort Injured DS9 Crew to the Infirmary\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li> [Tactical] System Security\n<ul>\n<li> Examine Base Network Protocols\n</li>\n<li> Search for Flaws in the Firewall\n</li>\n<li> Trace Network Links\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li> [Engineering] Required Renovations\n<ul>\n<li> Make Necessary Repairs\n<ul>\n<li> Repair Equipment in Starfleet Operations\n</li>\n<li> Repair Equipment in the Infirmary\n</li>\n<li> Repair Equipment in Starfleet Command\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li> Return to Jirelle Kav\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li> Train for Combat Against the <a href=\\"/Dominion\\" title=\\"Dominion\\">Dominion</a> Ground Forces\n<ul>\n<li> Contemplating Captains\n<ul>\n<li> Complete Combat Training: Changeling\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li> Studying Soldiers\n<ul>\n<li> Complete Combat Training: <a href=\\"/Jem%27Hadar\\" title=\\"Jem'Hadar\\">Jem'Hadar</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li> Return to Jirelle Kav\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li> Train for Combat Against the Dominion Fleet\n<ul>\n<li> Scrutinizing Starships\n<ul>\n<li> Combat Training: Capital Ships\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li> Fleet Findings\n<ul>\n<li> Combat Training: Small Craft\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li> Return to Jirelle Kav\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li> Report to Colonel <a href=\\"/Kubus_Pohl\\" title=\\"Kubus Pohl\\">Kubus Pohl</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\\"thumb tright\\"><div class=\\"thumbinner\\" style=\\"width:182px;\\"><a href=\\"/File:The_central_square_of_Hathon_on_Bajor.png\\" class=\\"image\\"><img alt=\\"\\" src=\\"http://hydra-media.cursecdn.com/sto.gamepedia.com/thumb/1/18/The_central_square_of_Hathon_on_Bajor.png/180px-The_central_square_of_Hathon_on_Bajor.png?version=01492536f1459a736dc40e27eb62b9d6\\" width=\\"180\\" height=\\"113\\" class=\\"thumbimage\\" srcset=\\"http://hydra-media.cursecdn.com/sto.gamepedia.com/thumb/1/18/The_central_square_of_Hathon_on_Bajor.png/270px-The_central_square_of_Hathon_on_Bajor.png 1.5x, http://hydra-media.cursecdn.com/sto.gamepedia.com/thumb/1/18/The_central_square_of_Hathon_on_Bajor.png/360px-The_central_square_of_Hathon_on_Bajor.png 2x\\" /></a>  <div class=\\"thumbcaption\\"><div class=\\"magnify\\"><a href=\\"/File:The_central_square_of_Hathon_on_Bajor.png\\" class=\\"internal\\" title=\\"Enlarge\\"><img src=\\"/skins/common/images/magnify-clip.png\\" width=\\"15\\" height=\\"11\\" alt=\\"\\" /></a></div>Hathon central square</div></div></div>\n<ul>\n<li> Appease the Local Bajoran Population\n<ul>\n<li> Get a Mission from Kubus Pohl\n</li>\n<li> Religious Requirements\n<ul>\n<li> Talk to Ranjen <a href=\\"/Ravel\\" title=\\"Ravel\\">Ravel</a>\n</li>\n<li> Research Bajoran Religious Practices\n</li>\n<li> Burn Bateret Leaf Incense Around Hathon\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li> Occupation Overreaction\n<ul>\n<li> Talk the Protester Down\n</li>\n<li> Don't Incite a Riot\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li> Return to Kubus Pohl\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\\"thumb tright\\"><div class=\\"thumbinner\\" style=\\"width:182px;\\"><a href=\\"/File:Prophet_(B%27vat).jpg\\" class=\\"image\\"><img alt=\\"\\" src=\\"http://hydra-media.cursecdn.com/sto.gamepedia.com/thumb/5/5b/Prophet_%28B%27vat%29.jpg/180px-Prophet_%28B%27vat%29.jpg?version=f51c3e276a4d6e01f2b4d6deefc50c5a\\" width=\\"180\\" height=\\"179\\" class=\\"thumbimage\\" srcset=\\"http://hydra-media.cursecdn.com/sto.gamepedia.com/thumb/5/5b/Prophet_%28B%27vat%29.jpg/270px-Prophet_%28B%27vat%29.jpg 1.5x, http://hydra-media.cursecdn.com/sto.gamepedia.com/thumb/5/5b/Prophet_%28B%27vat%29.jpg/360px-Prophet_%28B%27vat%29.jpg 2x\\" /></a>  <div class=\\"thumbcaption\\"><div class=\\"magnify\\"><a href=\\"/File:Prophet_(B%27vat).jpg\\" class=\\"internal\\" title=\\"Enlarge\\"><img src=\\"/skins/common/images/magnify-clip.png\\" width=\\"15\\" height=\\"11\\" alt=\\"\\" /></a></div>A <a href=\\"/Prophet\\" title=\\"Prophet\\">Prophet</a> appearing as <a href=\\"/B%27vat\\" title=\\"B'vat\\">B'vat</a> in an Orb vision.</div></div></div>\n<ul>\n<li> Learn About Bajor\n<ul>\n<li> Petition the <a href=\\"/Prophet\\" title=\\"Prophet\\">Prophets</a>\n<ul>\n<li> Use the Orb of Prophecy and Change at The Ha'dara Temple\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li> Soil Saver\n<ul>\n<li> Increase Soil Fertility in the Greenhouse\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li> Return to Kubus Pohl\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li> Report to Commander Mesi Achebe\n</li>\n<li> Gather Intel on the Dominion Presence on DS9\n<ul>\n<li> Subspace Spyworks\n<ul>\n<li> Scan Subspace Signals from DS9 \n<ul>\n<li> Note: The signal is generated randomly. Players will have to scan all frequencies. Scan for a connection to a \\"Private Network\\".\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li> Make Contact With an <a href=\\"/Hadron\\" title=\\"Hadron\\">Ally</a> on DS9\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li> Return to Commander Mesi Achebe\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li> Use Communications Hardware in Bajoran Militia HQ\n</li>\n<li> Return to Commander Mesi Achebe\n</li>\n</ul>\n"}]}}}}"""))
