{"query":{"pages":{"24997":{"pageid":24997,"ns":0,"title":"Mission: Facility 4028","revisions":[{"*":"<div id=\\"toc\\" class=\\"toc\\"><div id=\\"toctitle\\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\\"><a href=\\"#Outline\\"><span class=\\"tocnumber\\">1</span> <span class=\\"toctext\\">Outline</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\\"><a href=\\"#Mission_Text\\"><span class=\\"tocnumber\\">1.1</span> <span class=\\"toctext\\">Mission Text</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\\"toclevel-3 tocsection-3\\"><a href=\\"#Federation\\"><span class=\\"tocnumber\\">1.1.1</span> <span class=\\"toctext\\">Federation</span></a></li>\n<li class=\\"toclevel-3 tocsection-4\\"><a href=\\"#Klingon\\"><span class=\\"tocnumber\\">1.1.2</span> <span class=\\"toctext\\">Klingon</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\\"toclevel-2 tocsection-5\\"><a href=\\"#Goal\\"><span class=\\"tocnumber\\">1.2</span> <span class=\\"toctext\\">Goal</span></a></li>\n<li class=\\"toclevel-2 tocsection-6\\"><a href=\\"#Objectives\\"><span class=\\"tocnumber\\">1.3</span> <span class=\\"toctext\\">Objectives</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Outline\\">Outline</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Facility_4028&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\\" title=\\"Edit section: Outline\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Mission_Text\\">Mission Text</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Facility_4028&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\\" title=\\"Edit section: Mission Text\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h3>\n<h4><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Federation\\">Federation</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Facility_4028&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\\" title=\\"Edit section: Federation\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h4>\n<div class=\\"missiontext\\">\n<p>The Federation Council has authorized the release of the Founder from the detention facility where she is currently being held.\n</p><p>I need someone who Eraun and the Founder will respect to complete the transfer. You're the best candidate for the task.\n</p><p>I don't expect any problems, but I didn't expect Jem'Hadar from the past to crash the Borg conference, either. So take my recommendations with a grain of salt.\n</p><p>The important thing is the safety of Eraun and the Founder. We need their help if we want to end this standoff without more bloodshed.\n</p>\n</div>\n<h4><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Klingon\\">Klingon</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Facility_4028&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\\" title=\\"Edit section: Klingon\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h4>\n<h3><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Goal\\">Goal</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Facility_4028&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\\" title=\\"Edit section: Goal\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h3>\n<div class=\\"missiongoal\\">Go to the Ayala System, which is located in the Kassae Sector of the Regulus Sector Block, and find the Female Founder.</div>\n<h3><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Objectives\\">Objectives</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Facility_4028&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\\" title=\\"Edit section: Objectives\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h3>\n<ul>\n<li> Visiting Hours\n<ul>\n<li> Go To <a href=\\"/Ayala_System\\" title=\\"Ayala System\\">Ayala System</a>\n</li>\n<li> Approach the Facility\n</li>\n<li> Hail Facility 4028\n</li>\n<li> Hail Eraun\n</li>\n<li> Beam Down\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li> Lockdown\n<ul>\n<li> Enter Isolation Zone A\n<ul>\n<li> Access I.S.I.S. Panel\n</li>\n<li> Extend Walkway\n</li>\n<li> Enter Control Room\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li> Speak to <a href=\\"/index.php?title=The_Warden&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\\" class=\\"new\\" title=\\"The Warden (page does not exist)\\">Warden</a>\n</li>\n<li> Extend Secondary Walkway\n</li>\n<li> Speak to Inmate 53160\n</li>\n<li> Speak to Warden\n</li>\n<li> Speak to Eraun\n</li>\n<li> Go to Isolation Zone B\n</li>\n<li> Release the Founder\n<ul>\n<li> Use I.S.I.S. Panel\n</li>\n<li> Open Cell Door\n</li>\n<li> Lower Secondary Force Field\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li> Speak to Founder\n</li>\n<li> Defeat Ambush\n</li>\n<li> Incoming Message\n</li>\n<li> Run Diagnostic\n</li>\n<li> Secure Prison\n<ul>\n<li> Section 01 Secured\n</li>\n<li> Section 02 Secured\n</li>\n<li> Section 03 Secured\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li> Speak to Final Prisoner\n</li>\n<li> Bring ISIS Back Online\n</li>\n<li> Speak to Warden\n</li>\n<li> Use Transporter Pad\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li> Final Flight\n<ul>\n<li> Depart System\n</li>\n<li> Return to Commander Mesi Achebe\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n"}]}}}}"""))
		missions.add(new Mission(text: """
{"query":{"pages":{"24998":{"pageid":24998,"ns":0,"title":"Mission: Boldly They Rode","revisions":[{"*":"<div id=\\"toc\\" class=\\"toc\\"><div id=\\"toctitle\\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\\"><a href=\\"#Outline\\"><span class=\\"tocnumber\\">1</span> <span class=\\"toctext\\">Outline</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\\"><a href=\\"#Mission_Text\\"><span class=\\"tocnumber\\">1.1</span> <span class=\\"toctext\\">Mission Text</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\\"toclevel-3 tocsection-3\\"><a href=\\"#Federation\\"><span class=\\"tocnumber\\">1.1.1</span> <span class=\\"toctext\\">Federation</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\\"><a href=\\"#Goal\\"><span class=\\"tocnumber\\">1.2</span> <span class=\\"toctext\\">Goal</span></a></li>\n<li class=\\"toclevel-2 tocsection-5\\"><a href=\\"#Objectives\\"><span class=\\"tocnumber\\">1.3</span> <span class=\\"toctext\\">Objectives</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Outline\\">Outline</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Boldly_They_Rode&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\\" title=\\"Edit section: Outline\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Mission_Text\\">Mission Text</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Boldly_They_Rode&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\\" title=\\"Edit section: Mission Text\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h3>\n<h4><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Federation\\">Federation</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Boldly_They_Rode&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\\" title=\\"Edit section: Federation\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h4>\n<div class=\\"missiontext\\">\n<p>Now that we have the aid of one of the Founders, we should have no trouble convincing the Jem'Hadar at Deep Space 9 to stand down and return to the Gamma Quadrant. Starfleet and the Klingon Empire are assembling a unified fleet to garrison the station and repair the damage from the battle. We want you to go with the Founder to negotiate the surrender of the remaining Jem'Hadar.\n</p><p>Rendezvous with a Jem'Hadar ship near Deep Space 9. You'll represent the interests of the Alpha Quadrant, but this should be a simple formality.\n</p><p>Captain Kurland is headed to Deep Space 9 in the <i>Defiant</i>, along with the rest of the task force. Oh, he said to tell you that he's looking forward to seeing you on the station again.\n</p>\n</div>\n<h3><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Goal\\">Goal</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Boldly_They_Rode&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\\" title=\\"Edit section: Goal\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h3>\n<div class=\\"missiongoal\\">\n<p>Head to Deep Space 9 to rendezvous with a Dominion ship.\n</p><p>Deep Space 9 is located in the Bajor Sector of the Beta Ursae Sector Block.\n</p>\n</div>\n<h3><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Objectives\\">Objectives</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Boldly_They_Rode&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\\" title=\\"Edit section: Objectives\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h3>\n<div class=\\"thumb tright\\"><div class=\\"thumbinner\\" style=\\"width:182px;\\"><a href=\\"/File:Kurland_Defiant_bridge.png\\" class=\\"image\\"><img alt=\\"\\" src=\\"http://hydra-media.cursecdn.com/sto.gamepedia.com/thumb/6/6f/Kurland_Defiant_bridge.png/180px-Kurland_Defiant_bridge.png?version=2664f242841df7916958d36c4344c544\\" width=\\"180\\" height=\\"96\\" class=\\"thumbimage\\" srcset=\\"http://hydra-media.cursecdn.com/sto.gamepedia.com/thumb/6/6f/Kurland_Defiant_bridge.png/270px-Kurland_Defiant_bridge.png 1.5x, http://hydra-media.cursecdn.com/sto.gamepedia.com/thumb/6/6f/Kurland_Defiant_bridge.png/360px-Kurland_Defiant_bridge.png 2x\\" /></a>  <div class=\\"thumbcaption\\"><div class=\\"magnify\\"><a href=\\"/File:Kurland_Defiant_bridge.png\\" class=\\"internal\\" title=\\"Enlarge\\"><img src=\\"/skins/common/images/magnify-clip.png\\" width=\\"15\\" height=\\"11\\" alt=\\"\\" /></a></div>Cpt. <a href=\\"/Kurland\\" title=\\"Kurland\\" class=\\"mw-redirect\\">Kurland</a> on the bridge of the <a href=\\"/U.S.S._Defiant\\" title=\\"U.S.S. Defiant\\">U.S.S. <i>Defiant</i></a>.</div></div></div>\n<div class=\\"thumb tright\\"><div class=\\"thumbinner\\" style=\\"width:182px;\\"><a href=\\"/File:On_the_hull_of_DS9.jpg\\" class=\\"image\\"><img alt=\\"\\" src=\\"http://hydra-media.cursecdn.com/sto.gamepedia.com/thumb/f/f6/On_the_hull_of_DS9.jpg/180px-On_the_hull_of_DS9.jpg?version=a31519d6ac6403a7348fabde4a518c6b\\" width=\\"180\\" height=\\"89\\" class=\\"thumbimage\\" srcset=\\"http://hydra-media.cursecdn.com/sto.gamepedia.com/thumb/f/f6/On_the_hull_of_DS9.jpg/270px-On_the_hull_of_DS9.jpg 1.5x, http://hydra-media.cursecdn.com/sto.gamepedia.com/thumb/f/f6/On_the_hull_of_DS9.jpg/360px-On_the_hull_of_DS9.jpg 2x\\" /></a>  <div class=\\"thumbcaption\\"><div class=\\"magnify\\"><a href=\\"/File:On_the_hull_of_DS9.jpg\\" class=\\"internal\\" title=\\"Enlarge\\"><img src=\\"/skins/common/images/magnify-clip.png\\" width=\\"15\\" height=\\"11\\" alt=\\"\\" /></a></div>On the hull of <a href=\\"/Deep_Space_9\\" title=\\"Deep Space 9\\">Deep Space 9</a></div></div></div>\n<div class=\\"thumb tright\\"><div class=\\"thumbinner\\" style=\\"width:182px;\\"><a href=\\"/File:DS9_hull_map.png\\" class=\\"image\\"><img alt=\\"\\" src=\\"http://hydra-media.cursecdn.com/sto.gamepedia.com/thumb/3/33/DS9_hull_map.png/180px-DS9_hull_map.png?version=076345638f554f468fd97ea7187bb038\\" width=\\"180\\" height=\\"296\\" class=\\"thumbimage\\" srcset=\\"http://hydra-media.cursecdn.com/sto.gamepedia.com/thumb/3/33/DS9_hull_map.png/270px-DS9_hull_map.png 1.5x, http://hydra-media.cursecdn.com/sto.gamepedia.com/thumb/3/33/DS9_hull_map.png/360px-DS9_hull_map.png 2x\\" /></a>  <div class=\\"thumbcaption\\"><div class=\\"magnify\\"><a href=\\"/File:DS9_hull_map.png\\" class=\\"internal\\" title=\\"Enlarge\\"><img src=\\"/skins/common/images/magnify-clip.png\\" width=\\"15\\" height=\\"11\\" alt=\\"\\" /></a></div>Map of DS9's hull during the space walk</div></div></div>\n<div class=\\"thumb tright\\"><div class=\\"thumbinner\\" style=\\"width:182px;\\"><a href=\\"/File:Bird-of-Prey_wreckage_on_DS9.png\\" class=\\"image\\"><img alt=\\"\\" src=\\"http://hydra-media.cursecdn.com/sto.gamepedia.com/thumb/3/37/Bird-of-Prey_wreckage_on_DS9.png/180px-Bird-of-Prey_wreckage_on_DS9.png?version=10281adacee929630847c2a018ef4d83\\" width=\\"180\\" height=\\"126\\" class=\\"thumbimage\\" srcset=\\"http://hydra-media.cursecdn.com/sto.gamepedia.com/thumb/3/37/Bird-of-Prey_wreckage_on_DS9.png/270px-Bird-of-Prey_wreckage_on_DS9.png 1.5x, http://hydra-media.cursecdn.com/sto.gamepedia.com/thumb/3/37/Bird-of-Prey_wreckage_on_DS9.png/360px-Bird-of-Prey_wreckage_on_DS9.png 2x\\" /></a>  <div class=\\"thumbcaption\\"><div class=\\"magnify\\"><a href=\\"/File:Bird-of-Prey_wreckage_on_DS9.png\\" class=\\"internal\\" title=\\"Enlarge\\"><img src=\\"/skins/common/images/magnify-clip.png\\" width=\\"15\\" height=\\"11\\" alt=\\"\\" /></a></div>The wreckage of a Klingon <a href=\\"/Bird-of-Prey\\" title=\\"Bird-of-Prey\\">Bird-of-Prey</a> blocks the player's path on the hull of Deep Space 9.</div></div></div>\n<ul>\n<li> Voice of the Gods\n<ul>\n<li> Go To <a href=\\"/Deep_Space_9\\" title=\\"Deep Space 9\\">Deep Space 9</a>\n</li>\n<li> Speak with the Vorta, Eraun\n</li>\n<li> Hail Deep Space 9\n</li>\n<li> Strategize with the Founder\n</li>\n<li> Activate an Environment Suit\n</li>\n<li> Exit the Airlock\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li> Black Ops\n<ul>\n<li> Traverse the Crossover\n<ul>\n<li> Activate Maintenance Safety Posts\n</li>\n<li> Use Reaction Thrusters to Jump to the Crossover\n</li>\n<li> Jump from Post to Post Along the Crossover\n</li>\n<li> Go to Sensor Maintenance Panel\n</li>\n<li> Reroute External Sensors\n</li>\n<li> Keep Moving Along the Maintenance Posts\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li> Head Around the Crashed Ship\n</li>\n<li> Jump!\n</li>\n<li> Jump Back Down to the Station\n</li>\n<li> Cross the Power Junctions\n</li>\n<li> Use the Control Junction to the Right\n</li>\n<li> Mind the Gap\n</li>\n<li> Jump to the Promenade\n</li>\n<li> Override the Security Systems\n</li>\n<li> Enter the Promenade\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li> Intruder\n<ul>\n<li> Cross the Exchange to the Promenade\n</li>\n<li> Reach the Ops Turbolift\n<ul>\n<li> Use Force Field Controls to Defenestrate Jem'Hadar (Optional)\n</li>\n<li> Trigger Trapped Environmental Controls (Optional)\n</li>\n<li> Find Useful Supplies (Optional)\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li> Confront Kar'ukan\n</li>\n<li> Beam Up and Pursue Kar'ukan\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li> Fight of Angels\n<ul>\n<li> Engage Kar'ukan's Forces\n</li>\n<li> Finish the Remaining Jem'Hadar Ships\n</li>\n<li> Beam Down to Deep Space 9\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li> Honor the Charge\n<ul>\n<li> Talk to James Kurland in DS9's Ops\n</li>\n<li> Hail the Enterprise from Ops on DS9 (Optional)\n</li>\n<li> Hail the Dominion from Ops on DS9 (Optional)\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n"}]}}}}"""))
		missions.add(new Mission(text: """
{"query":{"pages":{"4394":{"pageid":4394,"ns":0,"title":"Mission: Report to Gamma Orionis","revisions":[{"*":"<h4><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Romulan_Republic_.28Federation-aligned.29\\">Romulan Republic (Federation-aligned)</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Report_to_Gamma_Orionis&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\\" title=\\"Edit section: Romulan Republic (Federation-aligned)\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h4>\n<div class=\\"missiontext\\">\n<p>Our Starfleet allies have located a Borg presence in the Gamma Orionis Sector Block. A fleet already begun massing in the Cestus Sector in response.\n</p><p>Report immediately to Four of Ten. She is a liberated Borg who has been providing Starfleet with strategic information. Last I heard, she was stationed on the <a href=\\"/U.S.S._Victory\\" title=\\"U.S.S. Victory\\">U.S.S. Victory</a>.\n</p>\n</div>\n&lt;/div&gt;<div class=\\"rightcolumn\\"></div>\n"}]}}}}"""))
		missions.add(new Mission(text: """
{"query":{"pages":{"43682":{"pageid":43682,"ns":0,"title":"Mission: Where Angels Fear to Tread","revisions":[{"*":"<h3><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Goal\\">Goal</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Where_Angels_Fear_to_Tread&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\\" title=\\"Edit section: Goal\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h3>\n<div class=\\"missiongoal\\">Investigate reports of Borg activity in the Burgus system, which is located in the Gamma Orionis Sector Block.</div>\n"}]}}}}"""))
		missions.add(new Mission(text: """
{"query":{"pages":{"43690":{"pageid":43690,"ns":0,"title":"Mission: A Gathering Darkness","revisions":[{"*":"<h4><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Federation\\">Federation</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_A_Gathering_Darkness&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\\" title=\\"Edit section: Federation\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h4>\n<div class=\\"missiontext\\">\n<p><b>&lt;rank&gt;</b>, what do you know about the <a href=\\"/Borg\\" title=\\"Borg\\">Borg</a> nanovirus?\n</p><p>The Borg aren't just assimilating individuals anymore. They've found a way to assimilate entire areas. They infect the technology, the water, the flora ... even the air. After that, it's only a matter of time until the entire planet is Borg.\n</p><p>If this process is allowed to continue unchecked, they'll assimilate the entire sector. And from there? They could assimilate the entire <a href=\\"/Federation\\" title=\\"Federation\\" class=\\"mw-redirect\\">Federation</a>.\n</p><p>Starfleet has a team working on a counteragent on <a href=\\"/Kessik_IV\\" title=\\"Kessik IV\\">Kessik IV</a>. We lost contact with them, and with the entire planet. We fear that the nanovirus escaped confinement and infected the planet.\n</p><p>We need that team and the data they have collected. Our defense plans are useless without them.\n</p><p>I need the <b>&lt;ship name&gt;</b> to the Kessik system. Find the researchers and bring them back.\n</p><p>I don't need to tell you how dangerous this is, <b>&lt;rank&gt;</b>. Watch your back ... and good luck.\n</p>\n</div>\n"}]}}}}"""))
		missions.add(new Mission(text: """
{"query":{"pages":{"43696":{"pageid":43696,"ns":0,"title":"Mission: Assimilation","revisions":[{"*":"<h3><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Goal\\">Goal</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Assimilation&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\\" title=\\"Edit section: Goal\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h3>\n<div class=\\"missiongoal\\">Investigate the Borg presence in NGC-4447, which is located in the Gamma Orionis Sector Block.</div>\n"}]}}}}"""))
		missions.add(new Mission(text: """
{"query":{"pages":{"43693":{"pageid":43693,"ns":0,"title":"Mission: Fluid Dynamics","revisions":[{"*":"<h4><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Federation\\">Federation</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Fluid_Dynamics&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\\" title=\\"Edit section: Federation\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h4>\n<div class=\\"missiontext\\">\n<p>The data you recovered from the <a href=\\"/Borg_Cube\\" title=\\"Borg Cube\\" class=\\"mw-redirect\\">Borg Cube</a> indicates that the <a href=\\"/Borg\\" title=\\"Borg\\">Borg</a> have established a foothold in <a href=\\"/Undine\\" title=\\"Undine\\">Undine</a> space. The Undine seem to make very little distinction between alien races, so it's quite possible that the Borg presence in their home is causing their aggressive behavior.\n</p><p>We can not afford a full-out war with the Undine. Their biotechnology surpasses even our most advanced technology. Therefore, we have assembled an expedition to remove the Borg presence from <a href=\\"/Fluidic_Space\\" title=\\"Fluidic Space\\" class=\\"mw-redirect\\">Fluidic Space</a>. We've found a system where the fabric of the two dimensions are breaking down. This is our best shot at creating a stable quantum singularity.\n</p><p>The expedition will include <a href=\\"/U.S.S._Voyager\\" title=\\"U.S.S. Voyager\\">U.S.S. <i>Voyager</i></a>, commanded by Admiral <a href=\\"/Tuvok\\" title=\\"Tuvok\\">Tuvok</a>. He has analyzed the data you recieved from the Borg cube and is confident he can create an artificial singularity. Your orders are to create an artificial singularity. Your orders are to cross into Fluidic Space with <i>Voyager</i>, locate the Borg, and remove them if possible.\n</p><p>Avoid conflict with the Undine. They will have the advantage, and you'll end up in a fight you can't win.\n</p>\n</div>\n"}]}}}}"""))
		missions.add(new Mission(text: """
{"query":{"pages":{"8351":{"pageid":8351,"ns":0,"title":"Mission: Cold Call","revisions":[{"*":"<h3><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Mission_Text\\">Mission Text</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Cold_Call&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\\" title=\\"Edit section: Mission Text\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h3>\n<h4><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Federation_.26_Romulan_Republic_allies\\">Federation &amp; Romulan Republic allies</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Cold_Call&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\\" title=\\"Edit section: Federation &amp; Romulan Republic allies\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h4>\n<div class=\\"missiontext\\">\n<p>I was quite impressed with the successful outcome of the recent trade negotiations at <a href=\\"/Starbase_39-Sierra\\" title=\\"Starbase 39-Sierra\\" class=\\"mw-redirect\\">Starbase 39-Sierra</a>, and I am pleased to invite the <a href=\\"/Federation\\" title=\\"Federation\\" class=\\"mw-redirect\\">Federation</a> to send an envoy to the <a href=\\"/Defera_System\\" title=\\"Defera System\\">Defera system</a> for a more formal meeting.\n</p><p>This could be a great opportunity for both of our peoples. The Federation has requested an alliance with us on several occasions, but my people's adherence to Balance has prevented it. Now they are more open to the idea of ties with other worlds.\n</p><p>Perhaps your visit will be the start of a lasting friendship between our peoples.\n</p>\n</div>\n<h4><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Klingon\\">Klingon</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Cold_Call&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\\" title=\\"Edit section: Klingon\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h4>\n<div class=\\"missiontext\\">\n<p>Honorable servant of the Empire, I need you to undertake what could be a rather unusual mission.\n</p><p>I understand that <a href=\\"/Diplomacy\\" title=\\"Diplomacy\\">diplomacy</a> can be seen as a task unworthy of a warrior in the <a href=\\"/Klingon_Empire\\" title=\\"Klingon Empire\\">Klingon Empire</a>, but I sincerely believe that you are the best person for this task.\n</p><p>Your <a href=\\"/Klingon_High_Council\\" title=\\"Klingon High Council\\">High Council</a> has agree to send a representative to <a href=\\"/Defera\\" title=\\"Defera\\" class=\\"mw-redirect\\">Defera</a> for formal diplomatic discussions. You will be that representative.\n</p><p>We have been friends of the Empire since the time of Emperor <a href=\\"http://memory-alpha.org/wiki/Sompek\\" class=\\"extiw\\" title=\\"ma:Sompek\\"><span style=\\"cursor: help;\\" title=\\"Sompek at Memory Alpha\\">Sompek</span></a>. We were happy to assist his fleet in time of need, and we have been most ... gratified by your loyalty to us over the years since then.\n</p><p>Go to the Defera system. You will be given more instructions there.\n</p><p>And ... thank you. This means more to us than you realize.\n</p>\n</div>\n<p><br />\n</p>"}]}}}}"""))
		missions.add(new Mission(text: """
{"query":{"pages":{"8572":{"pageid":8572,"ns":0,"title":"Mission: Out in the Cold","revisions":[{"*":"<h3><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Mission_Text\\">Mission Text</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Out_in_the_Cold&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\\" title=\\"Edit section: Mission Text\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h3>\n<div class=\\"missiontext\\">\n<p>We have lost contact with two transports en route to the outer colonies. There were more than 400 <a href=\\"/Deferi\\" title=\\"Deferi\\">Deferi</a> on those vessels, and with the rising threat from the <a href=\\"/Breen\\" title=\\"Breen\\">Breen</a> I fear the worst. Their last known location was near <a href=\\"/VZA-4001_System\\" title=\\"VZA-4001 System\\">VZA-4001</a>, and I suggest that you start your search there.\n</p><p>The Breen have no compunction against attacking civilian ships. We seek peace with the Breen, as we do with all beings, but they answer our offers of friendship with death and destruction.\n</p><p>Find our ships. If there are any survivors, please bring them home safely.\n</p>\n</div>\n"}]}}}}"""))
		missions.add(new Mission(text: """
{"query":{"pages":{"8668":{"pageid":8668,"ns":0,"title":"Mission: Cold Comfort","revisions":[{"*":"<h3><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Mission_Text\\">Mission Text</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Cold_Comfort&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\\" title=\\"Edit section: Mission Text\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h3>\n<div class=\\"missiontext\\">\n<p>We are receiving a distress signal in the <a href=\\"/Raveh_System\\" title=\\"Raveh System\\">Raveh system</a>. A <a href=\\"/index.php?title=Deferi_Ship&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\\" class=\\"new\\" title=\\"Deferi Ship (page does not exist)\\">Deferi transport</a> weathered a <a href=\\"/Breen\\" title=\\"Breen\\">Breen</a> attack, but they've taken heavy casualties and are requesting immediate assistance. My people do not have military ships, <i>&lt;rank&gt;</i>, and I am loathe to send a lightly-armored rescue vessel into such a dangerous situation.\n</p><p>Please, you must do whatever you can to help them!\n</p>\n</div>\n"}]}}}}"""))
		missions.add(new Mission(text: """
{"query":{"pages":{"8971":{"pageid":8971,"ns":0,"title":"Mission: Cold Case","revisions":[{"*":"<h3><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Mission_Text\\">Mission Text</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Cold_Case&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\\" title=\\"Edit section: Mission Text\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h3>\n<div class=\\"missiontext\\">\n<p>You must return to <a href=\\"/Defera\\" title=\\"Defera\\" class=\\"mw-redirect\\">Defera</a> immediately!\n</p><p>The <a href=\\"/Breen\\" title=\\"Breen\\">Breen</a> are searching for <a href=\\"/Preserver\\" title=\\"Preserver\\">Preserver</a> technology, and they have once again targeted the ruins near our city. I fear that more of my people will die, and with each death the Balance shifts. These attacks need to stop!\n</p><p>We are depending on you. Stop the Breen, and keep the secrets of the Preservers safe from their treachery.\n</p>\n</div>\n"}]}}}}"""))
		missions.add(new Mission(text: """
{"query":{"pages":{"9027":{"pageid":9027,"ns":0,"title":"Mission: Cold Storage","revisions":[{"*":"<h3><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Mission_Text\\">Mission Text</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Cold_Storage&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\\" title=\\"Edit section: Mission Text\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h3>\n<div class=\\"missiontext\\">\n<p>Our scientists have consulted with your commanders and they concur with your crew's theory.\n</p><p>If there is an intact Preserver library, it is likely to be located in the Lae'nas system. I suggest that you begin your search on Lae'nas III. It has a climate very similar to <a href=\\"/Defera\\" title=\\"Defera\\" class=\\"mw-redirect\\">Defera</a>. If the Preservers settled here eons ago, it is possible that they would have chosen a similar world for this facility.\n</p><p>Please, be safe, but be quick. Long range sensors have detected Breen vessels in the space near the Lae'nas system. I fear that they have made the same conclusions we have. You must find the Preserver technology before they do!\n</p>\n</div>\n"}]}}}}"""))
		missions.add(new Mission(text: """
{"query":{"pages":{"39564":{"pageid":39564,"ns":0,"title":"Mission: Sphere of Influence","revisions":[{"*":"<h3><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Mission_Text\\">Mission Text</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Sphere_of_Influence&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\\" title=\\"Edit section: Mission Text\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h3>\n<div class=\\"missiontext\\">\n<p>The <a href=\\"/Iconian_gateway\\" title=\\"Iconian gateway\\">gateway</a> discovered beneath the surface of <a href=\\"/New_Romulus\\" title=\\"New Romulus\\">New Romulus</a> is prepared and ready for activation.\n</p><p>Because the <a href=\\"/Romulan_Republic\\" title=\\"Romulan Republic\\">Romulan Republic</a> is dedicated to sharing the gateway and all we learn from it with our allies, we are inviting representatives of the Romulan Republic, the <a href=\\"/Federation\\" title=\\"Federation\\" class=\\"mw-redirect\\">Federation</a> and the <a href=\\"/Klingon_Defense_Force\\" title=\\"Klingon Defense Force\\">Klingon Defense Force</a> to join us on New Romulus for the first trip through the gateway.\n</p><p>I would be honored if you would join us, &lt;rank&gt;.\n</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\\"missionnote\\">This mission can only be completed as a single player.</div>\n<p><br style=\\"clear: both; height: 0px;\\" />\n</p>"}]}}}}"""))
		missions.add(new Mission(text: """
{"query":{"pages":{"40153":{"pageid":40153,"ns":0,"title":"Mission: Circles within Circles","revisions":[{"*":"<div id=\\"toc\\" class=\\"toc\\"><div id=\\"toctitle\\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\\"><a href=\\"#Outline\\"><span class=\\"tocnumber\\">1</span> <span class=\\"toctext\\">Outline</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\\"><a href=\\"#Mission_Text\\"><span class=\\"tocnumber\\">1.1</span> <span class=\\"toctext\\">Mission Text</span></a></li>\n<li class=\\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\\"><a href=\\"#Goal\\"><span class=\\"tocnumber\\">1.2</span> <span class=\\"toctext\\">Goal</span></a></li>\n<li class=\\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\\"><a href=\\"#Objectives\\"><span class=\\"tocnumber\\">1.3</span> <span class=\\"toctext\\">Objectives</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Outline\\">Outline</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Circles_within_Circles&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\\" title=\\"Edit section: Outline\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Mission_Text\\">Mission Text</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Circles_within_Circles&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\\" title=\\"Edit section: Mission Text\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h3>\n<div class=\\"missiontext\\">\n<p>The discovery and activation of the <a href=\\"/Iconian_gateway\\" title=\\"Iconian gateway\\">gateway</a> in the <a href=\\"/Jouret_System\\" title=\\"Jouret System\\">Jouret System</a> means we can send ships rapidly to explore the <a href=\\"/Solanae_Dyson_Sphere\\" title=\\"Solanae Dyson Sphere\\">Solanae Dyson Sphere</a>.\n</p><p>An alliance force comprised of ships from the <a href=\\"/Romulan_Republic\\" title=\\"Romulan Republic\\">Romulan Republic</a>, the <a href=\\"/Federation\\" title=\\"Federation\\" class=\\"mw-redirect\\">Federation</a> and the <a href=\\"/Klingon_Empire\\" title=\\"Klingon Empire\\">Klingon Empire</a> have agreed to work together to study the sphere and establish a zone of control there, but they need skilled captains and crews willing to join the fight.\n</p><p>Travel through the gateway and contact <a href=\\"/Dyson_Sphere_Joint_Command\\" title=\\"Dyson Sphere Joint Command\\">Allied Joint Command</a> once you reach the Solanae Dyson Sphere in the <a href=\\"/Delta_Quadrant\\" title=\\"Delta Quadrant\\">Delta Quadrant</a>.\n</p>\n</div>\n<h3><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Goal\\">Goal</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Circles_within_Circles&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\\" title=\\"Edit section: Goal\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h3>\n<div class=\\"missiongoal\\">Travel to the Jouret System in the Tau Dewa Sector Block and pass through the Iconian gateway there to the Solanae Dyson Sphere.</div>\n<h3><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Objectives\\">Objectives</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Circles_within_Circles&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\\" title=\\"Edit section: Objectives\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h3>\n<ul>\n<li> Use tha Gateway in the <a href=\\"/Tau_Dewa_Sector_Block\\" title=\\"Tau Dewa Sector Block\\">Tau Dewa Sector Block</a> to enter the Dyson Sphere\n</li>\n<li> Speak to the Chief Logistics Officer\n</li>\n<li> Speak to Chief Scientist\n</li>\n<li> Meet with Subcommander <a href=\\"/Kaol\\" title=\\"Kaol\\">Kaol</a>\n</li>\n<li> Report to Subcommander Kaol\n</li>\n</ul>\n"}]}}}}"""))
		missions.add(new Mission(text: """
{"query":{"pages":{"40156":{"pageid":40156,"ns":0,"title":"Mission: Supply Woes","revisions":[{"*":"<div id=\\"toc\\" class=\\"toc\\"><div id=\\"toctitle\\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\\"><a href=\\"#Outline\\"><span class=\\"tocnumber\\">1</span> <span class=\\"toctext\\">Outline</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\\"><a href=\\"#Mission_Text\\"><span class=\\"tocnumber\\">1.1</span> <span class=\\"toctext\\">Mission Text</span></a></li>\n<li class=\\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\\"><a href=\\"#Goal\\"><span class=\\"tocnumber\\">1.2</span> <span class=\\"toctext\\">Goal</span></a></li>\n<li class=\\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\\"><a href=\\"#Objectives\\"><span class=\\"tocnumber\\">1.3</span> <span class=\\"toctext\\">Objectives</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Outline\\">Outline</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Supply_Woes&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\\" title=\\"Edit section: Outline\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Mission_Text\\">Mission Text</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Supply_Woes&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\\" title=\\"Edit section: Mission Text\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h3>\n<div class=\\"missiontext\\">\n<p>While the minefield helps to keep Voth ships from entering allied space en masse, occasionally the Voth will slip one or two small vessels through with their advanced cloaking devices.\n</p><p>We have a range of tachyon probe frequencies that can sometimes detect Voth ships, but we need to get up close to have any chance of success. We want the &lt;shipname&gt; to search this zone for any Voth ships that might be hiding.\n</p>\n</div>\n<h3><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Goal\\">Goal</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Supply_Woes&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\\" title=\\"Edit section: Goal\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h3>\n<div class=\\"missiongoal\\">Head to the indicated locations in the Allied Zone of the Solanae Dyson Sphere and search for cloaked Voth ships.</div>\n<div class=\\"missionnote\\">This episode is required to unlock Found Missions within the Solanae Dyson Sphere.</div>\n<h3><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Objectives\\">Objectives</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Supply_Woes&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\\" title=\\"Edit section: Objectives\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h3>\n<ul>\n<li> Return to your Ship in the Dyson Sphere Allied System\n</li>\n<li> Expose Cloaked Ships\n<ul>\n<li> Scan for Cloaked Ships Near the Supply Depot\n<ul>\n<li> Defeat Voth Ambushers (0/2)\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li> Assist the <a href=\\"/U.S.S._Hypatia\\" title=\\"U.S.S. Hypatia\\">U.S.S. <i>Hypatia</i></a> in the Ion Stream Section\n</li>\n<li> Store Charges from Ion Stream Currents (0/3)\n</li>\n<li> Transfer Stored Charges to the Allied Minefield Tower\n</li>\n<li> Scan 3 Disabled Mines (0/3)\n</li>\n<li> Report to Joint Command\n</li>\n</ul>\n"}]}}}}"""))
		missions.add(new Mission(text: """
{"query":{"pages":{"40157":{"pageid":40157,"ns":0,"title":"Mission: The Contested Zone","revisions":[{"*":"<div id=\\"toc\\" class=\\"toc\\"><div id=\\"toctitle\\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\\"><a href=\\"#Outline\\"><span class=\\"tocnumber\\">1</span> <span class=\\"toctext\\">Outline</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\\"><a href=\\"#Mission_Text\\"><span class=\\"tocnumber\\">1.1</span> <span class=\\"toctext\\">Mission Text</span></a></li>\n<li class=\\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\\"><a href=\\"#Goal\\"><span class=\\"tocnumber\\">1.2</span> <span class=\\"toctext\\">Goal</span></a></li>\n<li class=\\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\\"><a href=\\"#Objectives\\"><span class=\\"tocnumber\\">1.3</span> <span class=\\"toctext\\">Objectives</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Outline\\">Outline</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_The_Contested_Zone&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\\" title=\\"Edit section: Outline\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Mission_Text\\">Mission Text</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_The_Contested_Zone&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\\" title=\\"Edit section: Mission Text\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h3>\n<div class=\\"missiontext\\">\n<p>We have more operations outside of the Allied Zone, Admiral.\n</p><p>The Contested Zone is right near our borders, and it is where our forces are currently engaged with the Voth, both in the atmosphere and on the ground.\n</p><p>It's a constant fight for control in the area. If we slip, the Voth will overwhelm us.\n</p><p>We could use your help out there. Travel to the Contested Zone and see what you can do.\n</p>\n</div>\n<h3><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Goal\\">Goal</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_The_Contested_Zone&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\\" title=\\"Edit section: Goal\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h3>\n<div class=\\"missiongoal\\">Travel to the Dyson Sphere Contested Zone. You can reach it through the Allied Zone.</div>\n<h3><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Objectives\\">Objectives</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_The_Contested_Zone&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\\" title=\\"Edit section: Objectives\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h3>\n<ul>\n<li> Go To Sphere Space - Contested Zone\n</li>\n<li> Report to Dyson Joint Command\n</li>\n</ul>\n"}]}}}}"""))
		missions.add(new Mission(text: """
{"query":{"pages":{"40159":{"pageid":40159,"ns":0,"title":"Mission: The Omega Standoff","revisions":[{"*":"<div id=\\"toc\\" class=\\"toc\\"><div id=\\"toctitle\\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\\"><a href=\\"#Outline\\"><span class=\\"tocnumber\\">1</span> <span class=\\"toctext\\">Outline</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\\"><a href=\\"#Mission_Text\\"><span class=\\"tocnumber\\">1.1</span> <span class=\\"toctext\\">Mission Text</span></a></li>\n<li class=\\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\\"><a href=\\"#Goal\\"><span class=\\"tocnumber\\">1.2</span> <span class=\\"toctext\\">Goal</span></a></li>\n<li class=\\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\\"><a href=\\"#Objectives\\"><span class=\\"tocnumber\\">1.3</span> <span class=\\"toctext\\">Objectives</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Outline\\">Outline</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_The_Omega_Standoff&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\\" title=\\"Edit section: Outline\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Mission_Text\\">Mission Text</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_The_Omega_Standoff&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\\" title=\\"Edit section: Mission Text\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h3>\n<div class=\\"missiontext\\">\n<p>There is a ground war waging as we speak in the battlezone. Commander Arnold is commanding allied forces in an attempt to gain control over Omega Particle Silos.\n</p><p>Unfortunately, the allied forces there are understaffed and underequipped. They're too far away from the supply depot for us to reliably send supplies supply shipments, and they can always use more combat ready recruits.\n</p><p>Commander Arnold and his forces could use your help, Admiral. Can you spare it?\n</p>\n</div>\n<h3><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Goal\\">Goal</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_The_Omega_Standoff&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\\" title=\\"Edit section: Goal\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h3>\n<div class=\\"missiongoal\\">Travel to the Dyson Sphere Battlezone. You can reach it through the Contested Zone, or by taking a shuttle in the Allied Zone.</div>\n<h3><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Objectives\\">Objectives</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_The_Omega_Standoff&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\\" title=\\"Edit section: Objectives\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h3>\n<ul>\n<li> Go To Dyson Sphere Battlezone\n</li>\n<li> Report to Dyson Joint Command\n</li>\n</ul>\n"}]}}}}"""))
		missions.add(new Mission(text: """
{"query":{"pages":{"40160":{"pageid":40160,"ns":0,"title":"Mission: Tower Control","revisions":[{"*":"<div id=\\"toc\\" class=\\"toc\\"><div id=\\"toctitle\\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\\"><a href=\\"#Outline\\"><span class=\\"tocnumber\\">1</span> <span class=\\"toctext\\">Outline</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\\"><a href=\\"#Mission_Text\\"><span class=\\"tocnumber\\">1.1</span> <span class=\\"toctext\\">Mission Text</span></a></li>\n<li class=\\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\\"><a href=\\"#Goal\\"><span class=\\"tocnumber\\">1.2</span> <span class=\\"toctext\\">Goal</span></a></li>\n<li class=\\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\\"><a href=\\"#Objectives\\"><span class=\\"tocnumber\\">1.3</span> <span class=\\"toctext\\">Objectives</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Outline\\">Outline</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Tower_Control&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\\" title=\\"Edit section: Outline\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Mission_Text\\">Mission Text</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Tower_Control&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\\" title=\\"Edit section: Mission Text\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h3>\n<div class=\\"missiontext\\">\n<p>We could use your help driving the Voth away from the control towers in the Contested Zone.\n</p><p>Those towers are integral to our control of the area. If the Voth hold them, they'll be able to call in reinforcements and overwhelm us.\n</p><p>Can you take the fight to the Voth and help us gain control over the area?\n</p>\n</div>\n<h3><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Goal\\">Goal</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Tower_Control&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\\" title=\\"Edit section: Goal\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h3>\n<div class=\\"missiongoal\\">\n<p>Defeat Voth around control towers in the Contested Zone.\n</p><p>Higher ranked Voth will count more towards progress.\n</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\\"missionnote\\">Two or more players are recommended to complete this mission.</div>\n<h3><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Objectives\\">Objectives</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Tower_Control&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\\" title=\\"Edit section: Objectives\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h3>\n<ul>\n<li> Go To Sphere Space - Contested Zone\n</li>\n<li> Defeat Voth around Control Towers (0%)\n</li>\n<li> Report to Dyson Joint Command\n</li>\n</ul>\n"}]}}}}"""))
		missions.add(new Mission(text: """
{"query":{"pages":{"42559":{"pageid":42559,"ns":0,"title":"Mission: A Step Between Stars","revisions":[{"*":"<h3><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Mission_Text\\">Mission Text</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_A_Step_Between_Stars&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\\" title=\\"Edit section: Mission Text\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h3>\n<div class=\\"missiontext\\">\n<p>&lt;rank&gt;, we have discovered a station near the center of the <a href=\\"/Solanae_Dyson_Sphere\\" title=\\"Solanae Dyson Sphere\\">Solanae Dyson sphere</a> that controls the station's ability to \\"jump\\" to other areas of space, utilizing the vast amounts of <a href=\\"/index.php?title=Omega_particles&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\\" class=\\"new\\" title=\\"Omega particles (page does not exist)\\">Omega particles</a> it generates as fuel.\n</p><p>This could be disasterous for the <a href=\\"/Delta_Quadrant\\" title=\\"Delta Quadrant\\">Delta Quadrant</a>. If the reaction is not perfect, vast areas of subspace would be damaged, rendering space travel in that region almost impossible.\n</p><p>Our intel indicates that the <a href=\\"/Voth\\" title=\\"Voth\\">Voth</a> intend to take control of the station and jump the sphere back to their space. We cannot allow this to happen.\n</p><p>Report to <a href=\\"/index.php?title=Joint_Command&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\\" class=\\"new\\" title=\\"Joint Command (page does not exist)\\">Joint Command</a>. We'll need your help to stop this.\n</p>\n</div>\n"}]}}}}"""))
		missions.add(new Mission(text: """
{"query":{"pages":{"43761":{"pageid":43761,"ns":0,"title":"Mission: Fluidic Destruction","revisions":[{"*":"<div id=\\"toc\\" class=\\"toc\\"><div id=\\"toctitle\\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\\"><a href=\\"#Outline\\"><span class=\\"tocnumber\\">1</span> <span class=\\"toctext\\">Outline</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\\"><a href=\\"#Mission_Text\\"><span class=\\"tocnumber\\">1.1</span> <span class=\\"toctext\\">Mission Text</span></a></li>\n<li class=\\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\\"><a href=\\"#Goal\\"><span class=\\"tocnumber\\">1.2</span> <span class=\\"toctext\\">Goal</span></a></li>\n<li class=\\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\\"><a href=\\"#Objectives\\"><span class=\\"tocnumber\\">1.3</span> <span class=\\"toctext\\">Objectives</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Outline\\">Outline</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Fluidic_Destruction&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\\" title=\\"Edit section: Outline\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Mission_Text\\">Mission Text</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Fluidic_Destruction&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\\" title=\\"Edit section: Mission Text\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h3>\n<div class=\\"missiontext\\">\n<p>The <a href=\\"/Undine\\" title=\\"Undine\\">Undine</a> have started to invade the <a href=\\"/Solanae_Dyson_Sphere\\" title=\\"Solanae Dyson Sphere\\">Dyson Sphere</a>, Admiral.\n</p><p>They have employed massive planet killers to destroy the <a href=\\"/Voth\\" title=\\"Voth\\">Voth</a> that we were previously engaging in the \\"Voth Zone\\".\n</p><p>Now, the Undine have taken full control of a portion of the sphere and are seeking to destroy it.\n</p><p>The alliance has sent Admiral <a href=\\"/Chal_Rexx\\" title=\\"Chal Rexx\\">Chal Rexx</a> to lead the charge against the Undine. He could use your help, if you can spare it.\n</p>\n</div>\n<h3><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Goal\\">Goal</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Fluidic_Destruction&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\\" title=\\"Edit section: Goal\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h3>\n<div class=\\"missiongoal\\">Travel to the Dyson Sphere Undine Battlezone. You can reach it through the Contested Zone, near the gateway in the Allied Zone, or through the Dyson Ground Battlezone.</div>\n<h3><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Objectives\\">Objectives</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Fluidic_Destruction&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\\" title=\\"Edit section: Objectives\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h3>\n<ul>\n<li> Travel to the Dyson Sphere Undine Battlezone\n<ul>\n<li> Go To Sphere Space - Battlezone\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li> Report to Dyson Joint Command\n</li>\n</ul>\n"}]}}}}"""))
		missions.add(new Mission(text: """
{"query":{"pages":{"43780":{"pageid":43780,"ns":0,"title":"Mission: Surface Tension","revisions":[{"*":"<h3><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Mission_Text\\">Mission Text</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Surface_Tension&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\\" title=\\"Edit section: Mission Text\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h3>\n<div class=\\"missiontext\\">\n<p>Recent events have underscored the threat posed by the <a href=\\"/Undine\\" title=\\"Undine\\">Undine</a>.\n</p><p>The native species of fluidic space, these aliens have infiltrated galactic powers, including the Federation, by using their shapeshifting and telepathic abilities. In an attempt to form a united front against this threat, I have called for a summit to discuss the means by which the various governments of the Alpha and Beta Quadrants can detect and neutralize the Undine presence.\n</p><p>The location for the talks will be the Jenolan Dyson sphere. Control of this site is currently under dispute by the Federation, the Klingon Empire and the Romulan Republic. However, I believe that access to the sphere should be a secondary concern to that of the threat of the Undine.\n</p><p>Your experiences in the field may prove to provide a valuable perspective, as well as a moderating influence. Please attend as a representative of the Federation.\n</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\\"missionnote\\">This mission can only be completed as a single player.</div>\n"}]}}}}"""))
		missions.add(new Mission(text: """
{"query":{"pages":{"46436":{"pageid":46436,"ns":0,"title":"Mission: Escalation","revisions":[{"*":"<h3><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Mission_Text\\">Mission Text</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Escalation&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\\" title=\\"Edit section: Mission Text\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h3>\n<div class=\\"missiontext\\">\n<p>The activation of the gateway at the heart of the Solanae Dyson Sphere has given us access to another Dyson Sphere, originally found near the Jenolan System, that is now located deep in the Delta Quadrant.\n</p><p>The Romulan Republic, the Federation and the Klingon Empire have put aside their differences in order to unite against common enemies, but they need skilled captains and crews willing to join the fight.\n</p><p>Travel through the gateway and contact Delta Command once you reach the Jenolan Dyson Sphere in the Delta Quadrant.\n</p>\n</div>\n"}]}}}}"""))
		missions.add(new Mission(text: """
{"query":{"pages":{"46448":{"pageid":46448,"ns":0,"title":"Mission: Mindscape","revisions":[{"*":"<h3><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Mission_Text\\">Mission Text</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Mindscape&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\\" title=\\"Edit section: Mission Text\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h3>\n<div class=\\"missiontext\\">\n<p>&lt;Rank&gt;, Admiral <a href=\\"/Tuvok\\" title=\\"Tuvok\\">Tuvok</a> has requested that you meet <a href=\\"/U.S.S._Voyager\\" title=\\"U.S.S. Voyager\\">Voyager</a> in the <a href=\\"/Syllerran_System\\" title=\\"Syllerran System\\">Syllerran system</a>. I believe he requires your assistance with a personal issue.\n</p><p>While you're there, you should be able to get a briefing on the current state of the <a href=\\"/Delta_Quadrant\\" title=\\"Delta Quadrant\\">Delta Quadrant</a>.\n</p>\n</div>\n"}]}}}}"""))
		missions.add(new Mission(text: """
{"query":{"pages":{"46459":{"pageid":46459,"ns":0,"title":"Mission: Reunion","revisions":[{"*":"<h3><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Mission_Text\\">Mission Text</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Reunion&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\\" title=\\"Edit section: Mission Text\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h3>\n<div class=\\"missiontext\\">\n<p>Our first task in the Delta Quadrant is a familiar one \u2013 helping a species to find a new home.\n</p><p>A group of Talaxians living in the <a href=\\"/Entaba_System\\" title=\\"Entaba System\\">Entaba system</a> are ready to move to a new homeworld nearby. Admiral Tuvok and Voyager have gone ahead to their main asteriod base to begin the preparations for the transition.\n</p><p>The admiral has requested your presence as well. You two work well together. I recommend you take advantage of his expertise. There's no one who knows more about the Delta Quadrant than he does.\n</p>\n</div>\n"}]}}}}"""))
		missions.add(new Mission(text: """
{"query":{"pages":{"46476":{"pageid":46476,"ns":0,"title":"Mission: Friends in Unlikely Places","revisions":[{"*":"<h3><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Mission_Text\\">Mission Text</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Friends_in_Unlikely_Places&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\\" title=\\"Edit section: Mission Text\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h3>\n<div class=\\"missiontext\\">\n<p>It's been more than 30 years since Voyager passed through this region of space, but the echoes of what Captain Janeway and her crew did linger.\n</p><p>We need to re-establish relationships here. I'm assigning you a region of space to patrol. Meet the locals and find out how things stand in the Delta Quadrant today.\n</p>\n</div>\n"}]}}}}"""))
		missions.add(new Mission(text: """
{"query":{"pages":{"46487":{"pageid":46487,"ns":0,"title":"Mission: Revelations","revisions":[{"*":"<div id=\\"toc\\" class=\\"toc\\"><div id=\\"toctitle\\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\\"><a href=\\"#Mission_Text\\"><span class=\\"tocnumber\\">1</span> <span class=\\"toctext\\">Mission Text</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\\"><a href=\\"#Federation\\"><span class=\\"tocnumber\\">1.1</span> <span class=\\"toctext\\">Federation</span></a></li>\n<li class=\\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\\"><a href=\\"#Klingon\\"><span class=\\"tocnumber\\">1.2</span> <span class=\\"toctext\\">Klingon</span></a></li>\n<li class=\\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\\"><a href=\\"#Romulan\\"><span class=\\"tocnumber\\">1.3</span> <span class=\\"toctext\\">Romulan</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h3><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Mission_Text\\">Mission Text</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Revelations&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\\" title=\\"Edit section: Mission Text\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h3>\n<h4><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Federation\\">Federation</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Revelations&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\\" title=\\"Edit section: Federation\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h4>\n<div class=\\"missiontext\\">\n<p>&lt;Rank&gt;, we have recieved a distress call from the <a href=\\"/U.S.S._Callisto\\" title=\\"U.S.S. Callisto\\">U.S.S. <i>Callisto</i></a>, which was on a research mission in a little-explored area of the <a href=\\"/Delta_Quadrant\\" title=\\"Delta Quadrant\\">Delta Quadrant</a>.\n</p><p>We're not sure what happened to the <i>Callisto</i>, but we need someone to check it out. There are a lot of people on the <i>Callisto</i>, good <a href=\\"/Starfleet\\" title=\\"Starfleet\\">Starfleet</a> officers and researchers. Bring them home.\n</p>\n</div>\n<h4><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Klingon\\">Klingon</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Revelations&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\\" title=\\"Edit section: Klingon\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h4>\n<div class=\\"missiontext\\">\n<p>&lt;Rank&gt;, we have recieved a distress call from a Federation starship, the <a href=\\"/U.S.S._Callisto\\" title=\\"U.S.S. Callisto\\">U.S.S. <i>Callisto</i></a>. It seems their researchers found more trouble than they can handle while exploring the Delta Quadrant.\n</p><p>Find the Federation ship and either defeat their foes for the Glory and Honor of the Empire, or avenge the fallen! Show this quadrant that not everyone from the Alpha Quadrant is weak.\n</p>\n</div>\n<h4><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Romulan\\">Romulan</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Revelations&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\\" title=\\"Edit section: Romulan\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h4>\n<div class=\\"missiontext\\">\n<p>&lt;Rank&gt;, A Federation starship on a research mission for the alliance, the U.S.S. Callisto, has sent out a general distress signal. Intelligence needs you to find them.\n</p><p>If they were preyed upon by one of the more aggressive species here in the Delta Quadrant, we need to know who it was. And if they stumbled onto something one of those species didn't want us to find, well, then it's even more imperative that we find that ship and its crew.\n</p>\n</div>\n"}]}}}}"""))
		missions.add(new Mission(text: """
{"query":{"pages":{"46537":{"pageid":46537,"ns":0,"title":"Mission: Enemies in All the Usual Places","revisions":[{"*":"<h3><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Mission_Text\\">Mission Text</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Enemies_in_All_the_Usual_Places&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\\" title=\\"Edit section: Mission Text\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h3>\n<div class=\\"missiontext\\">\n<p>Not all of the experiences of the crew of the U.S.S. Voyager from their time in the Delta Quadrant were positive. Captain Janeway made some tough decisions to get her crew home \u2013 and more than one species felt like they'd had a run-in with a supernova after she'd been through their space.\n</p><p>These ill feelings have had decades to fester, and they haven't aged well. We need to do what we can to soothe them.\n</p>\n</div>\n"}]}}}}"""))
		missions.add(new Mission(text: """
{"query":{"pages":{"46541":{"pageid":46541,"ns":0,"title":"Mission: The Kobali Front","revisions":[{"*":"<h3><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Mission_Text\\">Mission Text</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_The_Kobali_Front&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\\" title=\\"Edit section: Mission Text\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h3>\n<div class=\\"missiontext\\">\n<p>&lt;Rank&gt;, are you familiar with the Kobali? Their homeworld is under attack by the Vaadwaur and they've requested your aid.\n</p><p>I informed the head of their military that you would render them support on the ground. Their city has been under siege for months and cannot take much more.\n</p><p>Please, do what you can on Kobali Prime to stop the Vaadwaur from destroying the Kobali.\n</p>\n</div>\n"}]}}}}"""))
		missions.add(new Mission(text: """
{"query":{"pages":{"46558":{"pageid":46558,"ns":0,"title":"Mission: With Friends Like These...","revisions":[{"*":"<div id=\\"toc\\" class=\\"toc\\"><div id=\\"toctitle\\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\\"><a href=\\"#Mission_Text\\"><span class=\\"tocnumber\\">1</span> <span class=\\"toctext\\">Mission Text</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\\"><a href=\\"#Federation\\"><span class=\\"tocnumber\\">1.1</span> <span class=\\"toctext\\">Federation</span></a></li>\n<li class=\\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\\"><a href=\\"#Klingon\\"><span class=\\"tocnumber\\">1.2</span> <span class=\\"toctext\\">Klingon</span></a></li>\n<li class=\\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\\"><a href=\\"#Romulan\\"><span class=\\"tocnumber\\">1.3</span> <span class=\\"toctext\\">Romulan</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h3><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Mission_Text\\">Mission Text</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_With_Friends_Like_These...&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\\" title=\\"Edit section: Mission Text\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h3>\n<h4><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Federation\\">Federation</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_With_Friends_Like_These...&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\\" title=\\"Edit section: Federation\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h4>\n<div class=\\"missiontext\\">\n<p>After their experiences with the U.S.S. Voyager, many species in the Delta Quadrant have taken more efforts to travel across this part of space. Unfortunately many of them have not found common ground among one another.\n</p><p>Your task is to survey the current political landscape for us. Voyager often rendered assistance without expectation of reward because it was the right thing to do. You will carry their example forward, showing the benefits of cooperation while discovering the divisions between groups out here.\n</p>\n</div>\n<h4><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Klingon\\">Klingon</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_With_Friends_Like_These...&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\\" title=\\"Edit section: Klingon\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h4>\n<div class=\\"missiontext\\">\n<p>After their experiences with the Federation ship, the U.S.S. Voyager, many species in the Delta Quadrant have become more bold, travelling across this part of space. However, they have found and created conflicts among themselves.\n</p><p>Survey the battlefield. Discover what grievances lie among these Delta Quadrant species. A wise warrior knows the state of the battlefield.\n</p>\n</div>\n<h4><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Romulan\\">Romulan</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_With_Friends_Like_These...&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\\" title=\\"Edit section: Romulan\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h4>\n<div class=\\"missiontext\\">\n<p>The Federation Starship, the U.S.S. Voyager, stirred this area of space. Their experiences here helped to embolden many, and the species in the Delta Quadrant have taken more efforts to travel across this part of space. Unfortunately many of them have not found common ground among one another.\n</p><p>We need to see this region stabilized, or threats like the <a href=\\"/Iconian\\" title=\\"Iconian\\">Iconians</a> or the <a href=\\"/Undine\\" title=\\"Undine\\">Undine</a> will march through the Sphere gateways and into the <a href=\\"/Alpha_Quadrant\\" title=\\"Alpha Quadrant\\">Alpha Quadrant</a>. Your task is to survey where the political winds are blowing. The more knowledge we have, the better able we will be to react to the situation out here.\n</p>\n</div>\n"}]}}}}"""))
		missions.add(new Mission(text: """
{"query":{"pages":{"46559":{"pageid":46559,"ns":0,"title":"Mission: All That Glitters","revisions":[{"*":"<h3><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Mission_Text\\">Mission Text</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_All_That_Glitters&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\\" title=\\"Edit section: Mission Text\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h3>\n<div class=\\"missiontext\\">\n<p>Are you familiar with Voyager's Emergency Medical Hologram? He's quite unique, even for an old EMH Mark I. Now he holds rank in Starfleet in his own right!\n</p><p>We've received a message that the Doctor requires assistance to deal with a medical situation on an Ocampa freighter in the <a href=\\"/Shenda_System\\" title=\\"Shenda System\\">Shenda system</a>. He is currently en route in one of Voyager's shuttles.\n</p><p>Normally I would send a medical Vessel, but we have seen a spike in Vaadwaur attacks and I want to make sure he has all the resources he will need. Could you go to the Shenda system and assist the Doctor?\n</p>\n</div>\n"}]}}}}"""))
		missions.add(new Mission(text: """
{"query":{"pages":{"46598":{"pageid":46598,"ns":0,"title":"Mission: Know Your Enemies","revisions":[{"*":"<h3><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Mission_Text\\">Mission Text</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Know_Your_Enemies&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\\" title=\\"Edit section: Mission Text\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h3>\n<div class=\\"missiontext\\">\n<p>The Vaadwaur have increased their efforts to control the <a href=\\"/Delta_Quadrant\\" title=\\"Delta Quadrant\\">Delta Quadrant</a>. We're going to have to work fast if we want to keep them in check.\n</p><p>I need the &lt;ship name&gt; to take on some routine patrols. We've marked several system that have had particularly high activities in them as of late.\n</p><p>We'll need you to patrol those systems and give aid to whomever you find. Hopefully we can gain more allies and find out what exactly the Vaadwaur are planning.\n</p>\n</div>\n"}]}}}}"""))
		missions.add(new Mission(text: """
{"query":{"pages":{"46577":{"pageid":46577,"ns":0,"title":"Mission: Capture the Flag","revisions":[{"*":"<h3><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Mission_Text\\">Mission Text</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Capture_the_Flag&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\\" title=\\"Edit section: Mission Text\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h3>\n<div class=\\"missiontext\\">\n<p>&lt;Rank&gt;, the alliance needs your help.\n</p><p>A group of alliance ships are currently under attack by the <a href=\\"/Vaadwaur\\" title=\\"Vaadwaur\\">Vaadwaur</a> in the <a href=\\"/Orlitus_System\\" title=\\"Orlitus System\\" class=\\"mw-redirect\\">Orlitus system</a>.\n</p><p>The <i>Lleiset</i> is making its way there to render assistance. I want you to back them up. We don't know what the Vaadwaur have there, and I want to give us the best possible chance of victory.\n</p>\n</div>\n"}]}}}}"""))
		missions.add(new Mission(text: """
{"query":{"pages":{"46708":{"pageid":46708,"ns":0,"title":"Mission: The Dragon's Deceit","revisions":[{"*":"<h3><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Mission_Text\\">Mission Text</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_The_Dragon%27s_Deceit&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\\" title=\\"Edit section: Mission Text\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h3>\n<div class=\\"missiontext\\">\n<p>&lt;Rank&gt;, We know there's something going on with the Vaadwaur in the <a href=\\"/Kartella_System\\" title=\\"Kartella System\\">Kartella system</a>, but we haven't been able to get any ships close enough to determine what that is. I think you'll have better luck.\n</p><p>The area doesn't have a lot of resources, but there's enough Vaadwaur ship traffic in the area to indicate a major base. But they're guarding it so closely that it could have something to do with their sudden jump in power.\n</p><p>Given the aggressive nature of the Vaadwaur, getting close enough to investigate without attracting their attention will be difficult. We've made contact with a Hazari bounty hunter in possession of equimpemnt that should allow you to approach and infiltrate their base.\n</p>\n</div>\n"}]}}}}"""))
		missions.add(new Mission(text: """
{"query":{"pages":{"46709":{"pageid":46709,"ns":0,"title":"Mission: Alliances","revisions":[{"*":"<h3><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Mission_Text\\">Mission Text</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Alliances&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\\" title=\\"Edit section: Mission Text\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h3>\n<div class=\\"missiontext\\">\n<p>The data from your mission against the Vaadwaur shows they are a bigger threat than we ever anticipated.\n</p><p>Our forces are stretched thin, &lt;Rank&gt;. The Alpha Quadrant alliance cannot fight a prolonged conflict in the Delta Quadrant.\n</p><p>We must work to form an alliance of species here. Admiral Tuvok and Captain Kim are working on a plan and have requested your assistance.\n</p>\n</div>\n"}]}}}}"""))
		missions.add(new Mission(text: """
{"query":{"pages":{"46782":{"pageid":46782,"ns":0,"title":"Mission: Better with Friends","revisions":[{"*":"<h3><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Mission_Text\\">Mission Text</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Better_with_Friends&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\\" title=\\"Edit section: Mission Text\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h3>\n<div class=\\"missiontext\\">\n<p>The best chance we have at defeating the Vaadwaur is to build an alliance of all Delta Quadrant species.\n</p><p>Some of them will need convincing. Go out there and show them that it's better to have us as a friend than an enemy.\n</p>\n</div>\n"}]}}}}"""))
		missions.add(new Mission(text: """
{"query":{"pages":{"46785":{"pageid":46785,"ns":0,"title":"Mission: Revolution","revisions":[{"*":"<h3><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Mission_Text\\">Mission Text</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Revolution&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\\" title=\\"Edit section: Mission Text\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h3>\n<div class=\\"missiontext\\">\n<p>We've received a coded message from your <a href=\\"/Vaadwaur\\" title=\\"Vaadwaur\\">Vaadwaur</a> friend, Commander <a href=\\"/Eldex\\" title=\\"Eldex\\">Eldex</a>. It seems he's finally ready to help up. He wants to meet, and he asked for you by name. He said he wouldn't deal with anyone else.\n</p><p>I'm still skeptical, however. This wouldn't be the first time the Vaadwaur have tried to set a trap for us. So be careful. I've spoken to Admiral <a href=\\"/Tuvok\\" title=\\"Tuvok\\">Tuvok</a>, and he suggested that <a href=\\"/Seven_of_Nine\\" title=\\"Seven of Nine\\">Seven of Nine</a> could join you as a technical expert. I see no reason why she shouldn't, and if things go wrong it will be good to have an ally you can trust.\n</p><p>Eldex sent us coordinates for a location in the <a href=\\"/Molinya_System\\" title=\\"Molinya System\\">Molinya system</a>. It's not Vaadwaur space, but there is a <a href=\\"/Hirogen\\" title=\\"Hirogen\\">Hirogen</a> relay in the area. Watch out for unwanted guests.\n</p>\n</div>\n"}]}}}}"""))
		missions.add(new Mission(text: """
{"query":{"pages":{"46985":{"pageid":46985,"ns":0,"title":"Mission: Taking Care of Enemies","revisions":[{"*":"<h3><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Mission_Text\\">Mission Text</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Taking_Care_of_Enemies&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\\" title=\\"Edit section: Mission Text\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h3>\n<div class=\\"missiontext\\">\n<p>Our alliance is going to need more help if we want to succeed against the Vaadwaur. We'll need to make pacts with other species in the quadrant, and not everyone is going to this our way. That's where the &lt;shipname&gt; comes in. Go out there and show them the value of cooperation.\n</p>\n</div>\n"}]}}}}"""))
		missions.add(new Mission(text: """
{"query":{"pages":{"47086":{"pageid":47086,"ns":0,"title":"Mission: Takedown","revisions":[{"*":"<h3><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Mission_Text\\">Mission Text</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Takedown&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\\" title=\\"Edit section: Mission Text\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h3>\n<div class=\\"missiontext\\">\n<p>The time has come to end the <a href=\\"/Vaadwaur\\" title=\\"Vaadwaur\\">Vaadwaur</a> threat to the Delta Quadrant. Our allies are assembling at the <a href=\\"/Jenolan_Dyson_Sphere\\" title=\\"Jenolan Dyson Sphere\\">Jenolan Dyson Sphere</a> to plan our assault on the Vaadwaur homeworld. You will serve as the battle commander for the assault.\n</p><p>Admiral <a href=\\"/Tuvok\\" title=\\"Tuvok\\">Tuvok</a> is waiting for you at the Jenolan Dyson Sphere. He will brief you, and our allies, on our strategy.\n</p><p>Good hunting, &lt;Rank&gt;.\n</p>\n</div>\n"}]}}}}"""))
		missions.add(new Mission(text: """
{"query":{"pages":{"47263":{"pageid":47263,"ns":0,"title":"Mission: What's Left Behind","revisions":[{"*":"<h3><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Mission_Text\\">Mission Text</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_What%27s_Left_Behind&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\\" title=\\"Edit section: Mission Text\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h3>\n<div class=\\"missiontext\\">\n<p>Admiral <a href=\\"/Tuvok\\" title=\\"Tuvok\\">Tuvok</a> and Captain <a href=\\"/Harry_Kim\\" title=\\"Harry Kim\\">Kim</a> are leading the analysis of the artifact you found on <a href=\\"/index.php?title=Vaadwaur_Prime&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\\" class=\\"new\\" title=\\"Vaadwaur Prime (page does not exist)\\">Vaadwaur Prime</a>.\n</p><p>I knew you'd wanted to be there for the great reveal, so I've arranged for you and your crew to be part of the team. Rendezvous with Voyager to get started.\n</p>\n</div>\n"}]}}}}"""))
		missions.add(new Mission(text: """
{"query":{"pages":{"49427":{"pageid":49427,"ns":0,"title":"Mission: Dust to Dust","revisions":[{"*":"<h3><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Mission_text\\">Mission text</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Dust_to_Dust&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\\" title=\\"Edit section: Mission text\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h3>\n<div class=\\"missiontext\\">\n<p><i>&lt;rank&gt;</i>, we have a situation on <a href=\\"/Kobali_Prime\\" title=\\"Kobali Prime\\">Kobali Prime</a>. You and I were both asked by name to help.\n</p><p>All that we've been told is that the <a href=\\"/Vaadwaur\\" title=\\"Vaadwaur\\">Vaadwaur</a> have launched a large offensive and have retaken the area in front of their \\"temple\\"... the place where they keep unconscious Vaadwaur stored.\n</p><p>They need our help to retake the area, though I have a feeling something else is going on. Can you help with the situation?\n</p>\n</div>\n"}]}}}}"""))
		missions.add(new Mission(text: """
{"query":{"pages":{"34080":{"pageid":34080,"ns":0,"title":"Mission: A Day on the Farm","revisions":[{"*":"<h3><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Mission_text\\">Mission text</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_A_Day_on_the_Farm&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\\" title=\\"Edit section: Mission text\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h3>\n<div class=\\"missiontext\\">\n<p>Welcome to Star Trek Online!\n</p><p>You are surviving on the agricultural world of <a href=\\"/Virinat\\" title=\\"Virinat\\">Virinat</a> after the destruction of the planets <a href=\\"/Romulus\\" title=\\"Romulus\\">Romulus</a> and <a href=\\"/Remus\\" title=\\"Remus\\">Remus</a>. Now you are trying to rebuild in the wake of cataclysmic changes to the <a href=\\"/Romulan_Star_Empire\\" title=\\"Romulan Star Empire\\">Romulan Star Empire</a> and its people.\n</p><p>Building a self-sufficient settlement takes a significant amount of work, especially since the surviving <a href=\\"/Romulan\\" title=\\"Romulan\\">Romulans</a> must find a way to maintain their presence among the stars or they will fade into the obscurity of history.\n</p>\n</div>\n"}]}}}}"""))
		missions.add(new Mission(text: """
{"query":{"pages":{"34170":{"pageid":34170,"ns":0,"title":"Mission: A Day in the Sun","revisions":[{"*":"<h3><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Mission_Text\\">Mission Text</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_A_Day_in_the_Sun&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\\" title=\\"Edit section: Mission Text\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h3>\n<div class=\\"missiontext\\">Your investigations of the Khellid problem have left you somewhat battered. You've been given the afternoon to rest.</div>\n"}]}}}}"""))
		missions.add(new Mission(text: """
{"query":{"pages":{"34161":{"pageid":34161,"ns":0,"title":"Mission: Virinat, Invaded","revisions":[{"*":"<h3><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Mission_Text\\">Mission Text</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Virinat,_Invaded&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\\" title=\\"Edit section: Mission Text\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h3>\n<div class=\\"missiontext\\">Virinat is under attack! Help the settlers while you try to find a way to escape!</div>\n"}]}}}}"""))
		missions.add(new Mission(text: """
{"query":{"pages":{"34164":{"pageid":34164,"ns":0,"title":"Mission: Flight from Virinat","revisions":[{"*":"<h3><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Mission_Text\\">Mission Text</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Flight_from_Virinat&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\\" title=\\"Edit section: Mission Text\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h3>\n<div class=\\"missiontext\\">Your only chance of escape is to reach D'Vex's Warbird and flee from Virinat!</div>\n"}]}}}}"""))
		missions.add(new Mission(text: """
{"query":{"pages":{"33234":{"pageid":33234,"ns":0,"title":"Mission: Explore the Flotilla","revisions":[{"*":"<div id=\\"toc\\" class=\\"toc\\"><div id=\\"toctitle\\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\\"><a href=\\"#Outline\\"><span class=\\"tocnumber\\">1</span> <span class=\\"toctext\\">Outline</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\\"><a href=\\"#Mission_Text\\"><span class=\\"tocnumber\\">1.1</span> <span class=\\"toctext\\">Mission Text</span></a></li>\n<li class=\\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\\"><a href=\\"#Goal\\"><span class=\\"tocnumber\\">1.2</span> <span class=\\"toctext\\">Goal</span></a></li>\n<li class=\\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\\"><a href=\\"#Objectives\\"><span class=\\"tocnumber\\">1.3</span> <span class=\\"toctext\\">Objectives</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Outline\\">Outline</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Explore_the_Flotilla&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\\" title=\\"Edit section: Outline\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Mission_Text\\">Mission Text</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Explore_the_Flotilla&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\\" title=\\"Edit section: Mission Text\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h3>\n<div class=\\"missiontext\\">\n<p>I've outlined important people you should talk to while visiting the Flotilla.\n</p><p>Speak with the Tailor to customize your appearance.\n</p><p>After that, speak with the Ship Tailor for ship customization options.\n</p>\n</div>\n<h3><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Goal\\">Goal</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Explore_the_Flotilla&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\\" title=\\"Edit section: Goal\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h3>\n<div class=\\"missiongoal\\">Learn to use the services around the flotilla. Welcome to your new home!</div>\n<h3><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Objectives\\">Objectives</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Explore_the_Flotilla&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\\" title=\\"Edit section: Objectives\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h3>\n<ul>\n<li> Speak with Lieutenant Deletham to Customize Your Outfit\n</li>\n<li> Speak with the Lieutenant Nalah to Customize Your Ship\n</li>\n<li> Speak with D'Tan\n</li>\n<li> Go to Sector Space\n</li>\n</ul>\n"}]}}}}"""))
