{"query":{"pages":{"33279":{"pageid":33279,"ns":0,"title":"Mission: The Helix","revisions":[{"*":"<div id=\\"toc\\" class=\\"toc\\"><div id=\\"toctitle\\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\\"><a href=\\"#Outline\\"><span class=\\"tocnumber\\">1</span> <span class=\\"toctext\\">Outline</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\\"><a href=\\"#Mission_text\\"><span class=\\"tocnumber\\">1.1</span> <span class=\\"toctext\\">Mission text</span></a></li>\n<li class=\\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\\"><a href=\\"#Goal\\"><span class=\\"tocnumber\\">1.2</span> <span class=\\"toctext\\">Goal</span></a></li>\n<li class=\\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\\"><a href=\\"#Objectives\\"><span class=\\"tocnumber\\">1.3</span> <span class=\\"toctext\\">Objectives</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Outline\\">Outline</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_The_Helix&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\\" title=\\"Edit section: Outline\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Mission_text\\">Mission text</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_The_Helix&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\\" title=\\"Edit section: Mission text\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h3>\n<div class=\\"missiontext\\">\n<p>If we're going to have a chance at breaking away from <a href=\\"/Sela\\" title=\\"Sela\\">Sela</a> and the <a href=\\"/Tal_Shiar\\" title=\\"Tal Shiar\\">Tal Shiar</a>, we need allies. \n</p><p>There are a lot of little settlements like yours out there. We're in contact with some of them, but we're always reaching out to try to make new alliances.\n</p><p>I've heard that a group of Romulans has taken up residence in a Suliban Helix in the <a href=\\"/Tau_Dewa_Sector_Block\\" title=\\"Tau Dewa Sector Block\\">Tau Dewa Sector Block</a>. I'd like you to visit them. Feel them out, help them if you can, but most of all, find out if they would be willing to join <a href=\\"/D%27Tan\\" title=\\"D'Tan\\">D'Tan</a> in his search for a new homeworld.\n</p>\n</div>\n<h3><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Goal\\">Goal</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_The_Helix&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\\" title=\\"Edit section: Goal\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h3>\n<div class=\\"missiongoal\\">Proceed to the Suliban Helix System in the Tau Dewa Sector Block and attempt to contact the Romulan colonists living there.</div>\n<h3><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Objectives\\">Objectives</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_The_Helix&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\\" title=\\"Edit section: Objectives\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h3>\n<ul>\n<li> Runaway Helix\n<ul>\n<li> Answer Incoming Hail\n</li>\n<li> Defeat the <a href=\\"/I.R.W._Sharrdar\\" title=\\"I.R.W. Sharrdar\\">I.R.W. Sharrdar</a>\n</li>\n<li> Contact the <a href=\\"/Suliban_Helix\\" title=\\"Suliban Helix\\">Suliban Helix</a>\n</li>\n<li> Restore Helix - Alpha Arm\n</li>\n<li> Restore Helix - Beta Arm\n</li>\n<li> Restore Helix - Delta Arm\n</li>\n<li> Defend Delta Arm\n</li>\n<li> Negotiate Transfer\n<ul>\n<li> Transport Refugees\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li> Defeat the <a href=\\"/I.R.W._Koval\\" title=\\"I.R.W. Koval\\">I.R.W. Koval</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li> Hail Temer to Report\n</li>\n</ul>\n"}]}}}}"""))
