i>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li> Interrogation\n<ul>\n<li> Plant Explosive\n</li>\n<li> Speak with the Romulan Subcommander\n</li>\n<li> Investigate Security Subcomannder's Office\n<ul>\n<li> Search the Computer for Useful Information\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li> Answer Khimek's Hail\n</li>\n<li> Alter Surveillance System\n</li>\n<li> Bully Security to Control Interrogation\n</li>\n<li> Lock the Interrogation Room Door\n</li>\n<li> Speak with the Prisoner\n</li>\n<li> \\"Interrogate\\" the Prisoner\n</li>\n<li> Speak with the Prisoner\n</li>\n<li> Set Off Explosives\n</li>\n<li> Speak with the Security Subcommander\n</li>\n<li> Speak with Subcommander Khimek\n</li>\n<li> Go to the Yhisu's Bridge\n</li>\n<li> Rig EPS Conduct to Explode\n</li>\n<li> Speak with Commander Janek\n</li>\n<li> Speak with Subcommander Khimek\n</li>\n<li> Return to Your Ship\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li> Return to Commander Tal'Mera\n</li>\n</ul>\n<div style=\\"clear: both\\"></div>\n<h2><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Accolades\\">Accolades</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Template:NoAccolades&amp;action=edit&amp;section=T-1\\" title=\\"Template:NoAccolades\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h2>\n<dl>\n<dd><i>There are no <a href=\\"/Accolade\\" title=\\"Accolade\\">accolades</a> specific to this mission.</i>\n</dd>\n</dl>\n<h2><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Walkthrough\\">Walkthrough</span></h2>\n<dl>\n<dd><i>There is no walkthrough for this mission, yet. You can help STOWiki by <a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Enemy_Action/Walkthrough&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\\" class=\\"new\\" title=\\"Mission: Enemy Action/Walkthrough (page does not exist)\\">writing it here</a>.</i>\n</dd>\n</dl>\n"}]}}}}"""))
