{"query":{"pages":{"33718":{"pageid":33718,"ns":0,"title":"Mission: Secrets of Nimbus","revisions":[{"*":"<div id=\\"toc\\" class=\\"toc\\"><div id=\\"toctitle\\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\\"><a href=\\"#Outline\\"><span class=\\"tocnumber\\">1</span> <span class=\\"toctext\\">Outline</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\\"><a href=\\"#Mission_Text\\"><span class=\\"tocnumber\\">1.1</span> <span class=\\"toctext\\">Mission Text</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\\"toclevel-3 tocsection-3\\"><a href=\\"#Federation\\"><span class=\\"tocnumber\\">1.1.1</span> <span class=\\"toctext\\">Federation</span></a></li>\n<li class=\\"toclevel-3 tocsection-4\\"><a href=\\"#Klingon\\"><span class=\\"tocnumber\\">1.1.2</span> <span class=\\"toctext\\">Klingon</span></a></li>\n<li class=\\"toclevel-3 tocsection-5\\"><a href=\\"#Romulan\\"><span class=\\"tocnumber\\">1.1.3</span> <span class=\\"toctext\\">Romulan</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\\"toclevel-2 tocsection-6\\"><a href=\\"#Goal\\"><span class=\\"tocnumber\\">1.2</span> <span class=\\"toctext\\">Goal</span></a></li>\n<li class=\\"toclevel-2 tocsection-7\\"><a href=\\"#Objectives\\"><span class=\\"tocnumber\\">1.3</span> <span class=\\"toctext\\">Objectives</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Outline\\">Outline</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Secrets_of_Nimbus&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\\" title=\\"Edit section: Outline\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Mission_Text\\">Mission Text</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Secrets_of_Nimbus&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\\" title=\\"Edit section: Mission Text\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h3>\n<h4><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Federation\\">Federation</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Secrets_of_Nimbus&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\\" title=\\"Edit section: Federation\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h4>\n<div class=\\"missiontext\\">\n<p>We have a situation in the Nimbus system, <b>&lt;Rank&gt;</b>. <a href=\\"/Romulan_Republic\\" title=\\"Romulan Republic\\">Romulan Republic</a> intelligence suggests that there are triggers for thalaron weapons somewhere on the planet Nimbus III. There are also increasing reports of <a href=\\"/Tal_Shiar\\" title=\\"Tal Shiar\\">Tal Shiar</a> activity on the planet.\n</p><p>Most people steer clear of Nimbus III these days \u2013 the Orion Syndicate basically runs the planet. Obviously, though, it would be a disaster if the Tal Shiar managed to get their hands on the thalaron triggers or take control of the planet. Stopping them not only helps a planet that needs Starfleet assistance, it provides a diplomatic connection with the Romulan Republic.\n</p><p>I know that I can count on you to do the right thing.\n</p>\n</div>\n<h4><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Klingon\\">Klingon</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Secrets_of_Nimbus&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\\" title=\\"Edit section: Klingon\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h4>\n<div class=\\"missiontext\\">\n<p>We have a situation in the Nimbus system, <b>&lt;Rank&gt;</b>. <a href=\\"/Romulan_Republic\\" title=\\"Romulan Republic\\">Romulan Republic</a> intelligence suggests that there are triggers for thalaron weapons somewhere on the planet Nimbus III. There are also increasing reports of <a href=\\"/Tal_Shiar\\" title=\\"Tal Shiar\\">Tal Shiar</a> activity on the planet.\n</p><p>Those Tal Shiar dogs cannot be allowed to have those triggers! We have sent a team to Nimbus III already, but they have failed to report in. Something must have happened.\n</p><p>I'm leaving this task in your hands. May you find glory in the sands of Nimbus.\n</p>\n</div>\n<h4><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Romulan\\">Romulan</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Secrets_of_Nimbus&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\\" title=\\"Edit section: Romulan\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h4>\n<div class=\\"missiontext\\">\n<p>&lt;rank&gt;, after what you've been through, I wouldn't blame you if you decided to take a leave of absence. But you seem to be recovering from the vestiges of indoctrination as well as can be expected.\n</p><p>I hope you're feeling better. The psychologists assure us that the nightmares and flashbacks will pass.\n</p><p>At the moment, we're trying to follow up on scattered intel regarding a missing chache of thalaron triggers. Our best information places them on <a href=\\"/Nimbus_III\\" title=\\"Nimbus III\\">Nimbus III</a>. We're also getting increasing reports of <a href=\\"/Tal_Shiar\\" title=\\"Tal Shiar\\">Tal Shiar</a> activity on the planet.\n</p><p>Naturally, we want to keep the triggers out of the hands of <a href=\\"/Hakeev\\" title=\\"Hakeev\\">Hakeev</a> and the Tal Shiar. But I'd also like to know exactly what they're doing on \\"the planet of galactic peace.\\"\n</p><p>Nimbus III has been a derelict planet for many years now, and it has only gotten worse under the influence of the <a href=\\"/Orion_Syndicate\\" title=\\"Orion Syndicate\\">Orion Syndicate</a>. Hassan the Undying has turned the planet into his personal fiefdom. Both Starfleet and the Klingon Defense Force have sent people to investigate, but they haven't found much.\n</p><p>Our operatives have been following leads provided by an itinerant trader there named <a href=\\"/Horace_Jones\\" title=\\"Horace Jones\\">Horace Jones</a>. So far nothing's turned up. If you're feeling up to it, perhaps you'll have better luck.\n</p>\n</div>\n<h3><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Goal\\">Goal</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Secrets_of_Nimbus&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\\" title=\\"Edit section: Goal\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h3>\n<div class=\\"missiongoal\\">Go to Nimbus III, which is located in the Tau Dewa Sector Block, and follow up on leads regarding banned weapons.</div>\n<h3><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Objectives\\">Objectives</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Secrets_of_Nimbus&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7\\" title=\\"Edit section: Objectives\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h3>\n<ul>\n<li> Go to Nimbus III\n</li>\n<li> Contact Horace Jones\n</li>\n</ul>\n"}]}}}}"""))
		missions.add(new Mission(text: """
{"query":{"pages":{"35908":{"pageid":35908,"ns":0,"title":"Mission: The Lost City of Paradise","revisions":[{"*":"<div id=\\"toc\\" class=\\"toc\\"><div id=\\"toctitle\\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\\"><a href=\\"#Outline\\"><span class=\\"tocnumber\\">1</span> <span class=\\"toctext\\">Outline</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\\"><a href=\\"#Mission_Text\\"><span class=\\"tocnumber\\">1.1</span> <span class=\\"toctext\\">Mission Text</span></a></li>\n<li class=\\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\\"><a href=\\"#Goal\\"><span class=\\"tocnumber\\">1.2</span> <span class=\\"toctext\\">Goal</span></a></li>\n<li class=\\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\\"><a href=\\"#Objectives\\"><span class=\\"tocnumber\\">1.3</span> <span class=\\"toctext\\">Objectives</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Outline\\">Outline</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_The_Lost_City_of_Paradise&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\\" title=\\"Edit section: Outline\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Mission_Text\\">Mission Text</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_The_Lost_City_of_Paradise&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\\" title=\\"Edit section: Mission Text\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h3>\n<div class=\\"missiontext\\">\n<p>Funny seeing you folks here. No one seems to bat an eye about our little planet until the Orions get their hands on something nasty. Now between that and the Romulans, this joint is jumpin'!\n</p><p>You want info? Sure, I'll give you info. The owner of the local bar, a reformed Borg by the name of <a href=\\"/Two_of_Eight\\" title=\\"Two of Eight\\">Two of Eight</a>, has his ear close to the ground.\n</p><p>He can tell you more about the <a href=\\"/Tal_Shiar\\" title=\\"Tal Shiar\\">Tal Shiar</a>. Just don't tell too many people I told you, alright?\n</p>\n</div>\n<h3><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Goal\\">Goal</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_The_Lost_City_of_Paradise&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\\" title=\\"Edit section: Goal\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h3>\n<div class=\\"missiongoal\\">Speak with Two of Eight in the bar on Nimbus III and uncover information about missing thalaron triggers.</div>\n<h3><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Objectives\\">Objectives</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_The_Lost_City_of_Paradise&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\\" title=\\"Edit section: Objectives\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h3>\n<ul>\n<li> Find Leads on Thalaron Weapons\n<ul>\n<li> Talk to the Bar Owner, Two of Eight\n</li>\n<li> Locate Missing Officers\n</li>\n<li> Desert Ambush\n<ul>\n<li> Investigate Weapon Remains (0/5)\n</li>\n<li> Fend Off Nearby Scorpions (0/20)\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li> Recover Groups of Downed Officers (0/2)\n</li>\n<li> Confront Two of Eight\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li> Track Down Information on the Triggers\n<ul>\n<li> Go to Law's House\n</li>\n<li> Talk to Law with the Console by his House\n</li>\n<li> Scan Old Consoles  of Defeat Sandworms to Recover Nausicaan Information (0%)\n</li>\n<li> Use the Computer at the Bar to Decipher the Information\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li> Return to Horace Jones\n</li>\n</ul>\n"}]}}}}"""))
		missions.add(new Mission(text: """
{"query":{"pages":{"33654":{"pageid":33654,"ns":0,"title":"Mission: Blind Men Tell All Tales","revisions":[{"*":"<h3><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Mission_Text\\">Mission Text</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Blind_Men_Tell_All_Tales&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\\" title=\\"Edit section: Mission Text\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h3>\n<div class=\\"missiontext\\">\n<p>This blind man must be some sorta mole for the <a href=\\"/Orion_Syndicate\\" title=\\"Orion Syndicate\\">Orion Syndicate</a>, the guys who have those triggers you're lookin' for. Now, I don't know who this guy is, but someone in this town must know.\n</p><p>The only way you're gonna convince folks to help you find this guy is if you show that you're not only strong enough to fight the Syndicate, but that you've got the gumption to defend us from 'em.\n</p><p>You do that, and I bet someone will step forward to tell you who this mole is and where you can find the triggers. If I were you, I'd start with <a href=\\"/Two_of_Eight\\" title=\\"Two of Eight\\">Two of Eight</a>. You get in good with him and you'll be all sorts of good, you know?\n</p>\n</div>\n"}]}}}}"""))
		missions.add(new Mission(text: """
{"query":{"pages":{"35968":{"pageid":35968,"ns":0,"title":"Mission: The Undying","revisions":[{"*":"<h3><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Mission_Text\\">Mission Text</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_The_Undying&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\\" title=\\"Edit section: Mission Text\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h3>\n<div class=\\"missiontext\\">\n<p>You've fond the location of <a href=\\"/Hassan_the_Undying\\" title=\\"Hassan the Undying\\">Hassan the Undying</a>'s stronghold. He's operating out of his \\"pleasure palace\\" \u2013 which is in reality a broken-down old ship that's the closest thing this place has to an underground club.\n</p><p>Men, women, fights, illegal deals, Syndicate merchandise \u2013 whatever you're looking for, Hassan has it there for a price.\n</p><p>What we want is information. Hassan sold the thalaron triggers to someone. All you need to do is convince him to tell you who so we can try to get them back.\n</p>\n</div>\n"}]}}}}"""))
		missions.add(new Mission(text: """
{"query":{"pages":{"35970":{"pageid":35970,"ns":0,"title":"Mission: A Fistful of Gorn","revisions":[{"*":"<h3><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Mission_Text\\">Mission Text</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_A_Fistful_of_Gorn&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\\" title=\\"Edit section: Mission Text\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h3>\n<div class=\\"missiontext\\">\n<p>When you first beamed down here, I wasn't so sure about you, but after what you did to Hassan? Yeah. You have some skills.\n</p><p>So, some Reman escaped with the trigger? Tough break. I bet he's out of the sector by now, but if there's one man on this rock who'd know where to go next, it's Law.\n</p><p>He can help you bring an end to all of this, then we can all celebrate with some drinks at the bar!\n</p>\n</div>\n"}]}}}}"""))
		missions.add(new Mission(text: """
{"query":{"pages":{"35973":{"pageid":35973,"ns":0,"title":"Mission: Installation 18","revisions":[{"*":"<h3><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Mission_Text\\">Mission Text</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Installation_18&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\\" title=\\"Edit section: Mission Text\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h3>\n<div class=\\"missiontext\\">\n<p>Everything points to the communications array as the hub of Tal Shiar activity on Nimbus III. There have also been reports of disappearances in the vicinity, and they have to be releated. The Tal Shiar have been taking people from all over. Makes sense that they're doing it here too.\n</p><p>It's time to find out what's going on inside that comm array. Get ready, &lt;rank&gt; \u2013 I don't think this is going to be easy.\n</p>\n</div>\n"}]}}}}"""))
