{"query":{"pages":{"4825":{"pageid":4825,"ns":0,"title":"Mission: The New Link","revisions":[{"*":"<div id=\\"toc\\" class=\\"toc\\"><div id=\\"toctitle\\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\\"><a href=\\"#Outline\\"><span class=\\"tocnumber\\">1</span> <span class=\\"toctext\\">Outline</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\\"><a href=\\"#Mission_Text\\"><span class=\\"tocnumber\\">1.1</span> <span class=\\"toctext\\">Mission Text</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\\"toclevel-3 tocsection-3\\"><a href=\\"#Federation\\"><span class=\\"tocnumber\\">1.1.1</span> <span class=\\"toctext\\">Federation</span></a></li>\n<li class=\\"toclevel-3 tocsection-4\\"><a href=\\"#Klingon\\"><span class=\\"tocnumber\\">1.1.2</span> <span class=\\"toctext\\">Klingon</span></a></li>\n<li class=\\"toclevel-3 tocsection-5\\"><a href=\\"#Romulan_.28Federation-aligned.29\\"><span class=\\"tocnumber\\">1.1.3</span> <span class=\\"toctext\\">Romulan (Federation-aligned)</span></a></li>\n<li class=\\"toclevel-3 tocsection-6\\"><a href=\\"#Romulan_.28Klingon-aligned.29\\"><span class=\\"tocnumber\\">1.1.4</span> <span class=\\"toctext\\">Romulan (Klingon-aligned)</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\\"toclevel-2 tocsection-7\\"><a href=\\"#Goal\\"><span class=\\"tocnumber\\">1.2</span> <span class=\\"toctext\\">Goal</span></a></li>\n<li class=\\"toclevel-2 tocsection-8\\"><a href=\\"#Objectives\\"><span class=\\"tocnumber\\">1.3</span> <span class=\\"toctext\\">Objectives</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\\"toclevel-3 tocsection-9\\"><a href=\\"#Federation_2\\"><span class=\\"tocnumber\\">1.3.1</span> <span class=\\"toctext\\">Federation</span></a></li>\n<li class=\\"toclevel-3 tocsection-10\\"><a href=\\"#Klingon_2\\"><span class=\\"tocnumber\\">1.3.2</span> <span class=\\"toctext\\">Klingon</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Outline\\">Outline</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_The_New_Link&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\\" title=\\"Edit section: Outline\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Mission_Text\\">Mission Text</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_The_New_Link&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\\" title=\\"Edit section: Mission Text\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h3>\n<h4><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Federation\\">Federation</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_The_New_Link&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\\" title=\\"Edit section: Federation\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h4>\n<div class=\\"missiontext\\">\n<p>With Gul <a href=\\"/Madred\\" title=\\"Madred\\">Madred</a> in custody, we need to make a decisive strike to end the threat of this \\"new <a href=\\"/Dominion\\" title=\\"Dominion\\">Dominion</a>\\" once and for all.\n</p><p><a href=\\"/Starfleet\\" title=\\"Starfleet\\">Starfleet</a> is preparing for an assault on Orias III, which we believe is a stronghold for the Alpha Jem'Hadar. You have some experience fighting both the True Way and the Jem'Hadar, so we want your ship in the battle group.\n</p><p>Make no mistake, <b>&lt;rank&gt;</b>, this is the real thing. Depending on what happens, we could either be ending a war ... or starting one.\n</p><p>Good luck.\n</p>\n</div>\n<h4><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Klingon\\">Klingon</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_The_New_Link&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\\" title=\\"Edit section: Klingon\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h4>\n<h4><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Romulan_.28Federation-aligned.29\\">Romulan (Federation-aligned)</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_The_New_Link&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\\" title=\\"Edit section: Romulan (Federation-aligned)\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h4>\n<div class=\\"missiontext\\">\n<p>With Gul Madred in custody, we need to make a decisive strike to end the threat of this \\"new Dominion\\" once and for all.\n</p><p>Starfleet is preparing for an assault on Orias III, which we believe is a stronghold for the Alpha Jem'Hadar. We'd like to make this a joint operation and invite the <b>&lt;shipname&gt;</b> to participate. Having your ship alongside Starfleet's will improve our strike team's chances and provide a powerful image of cooperation.\n</p><p>Make no mistake, <b>&lt;rank&gt;</b>, this is the real thing. Depending on what happens, we could either be ending a war ... or starting one.\n</p><p>Good luck.\n</p>\n</div>\n<h4><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Romulan_.28Klingon-aligned.29\\">Romulan (Klingon-aligned)</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_The_New_Link&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\\" title=\\"Edit section: Romulan (Klingon-aligned)\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h4>\n<div class=\\"missiontext\\">\n<p>Gul Madred has already given us some useful information. In conjunction with Alpha-quadrant Jem'Hadar, Madred and his True Way allies hoped to forge a new Dominion. They established a base on Orias III, where they have been creating and training more Jem'Hadar.\n</p><p>Orias III is in Zeta Andromeda, far enough away that the Federation has not yet turned an eye toward that corner of space. This has afforded the would-be new Dominion an opportunity to build its strength in secrecy.\n</p><p>I have arranged for a small task force of ships to meet you in Orias III under cloak. The task group will skirt the edge of Alpha Trianguli in order to avoid Federation sensor outposts. With your skill, this operation should be concluded before Starfleet even knows that the group is present.\n</p>\n</div>\n<h3><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Goal\\">Goal</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_The_New_Link&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7\\" title=\\"Edit section: Goal\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h3>\n<div class=\\"missiongoal\\">Join the battle group in the Orias System, located in the Orias Sector of the Zeta Andromedae Sector Block.</div>\n<h3><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Objectives\\">Objectives</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_The_New_Link&amp;action=edit&amp;section=8\\" title=\\"Edit section: Objectives\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h3>\n<div class=\\"leftcolumn\\">\n<h4><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Federation_2\\">Federation</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_The_New_Link&amp;action=edit&amp;section=9\\" title=\\"Edit section: Federation\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h4>\n<ul>\n<li> Leading the Charge\n<ul>\n<li> Go to <a href=\\"/Orias_System\\" title=\\"Orias System\\">Orias System</a>\n</li>\n<li> Destroy All True Way Ships\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li> Fatal Mistake\n<ul>\n<li> Hail <a href=\\"/U.S.S._Indianapolis\\" title=\\"U.S.S. Indianapolis\\">U.S.S. Indianapolis</a>\n</li>\n<li> Rescue Escape Pods (0/4)\n</li>\n<li> Defeat True Way Reinforcements\n</li>\n<li> Beam to Orias III\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li> Rescue and Recovery\n<ul>\n<li> Go To Orias III\n</li>\n<li> Beam Up Groups of Crewmen (0/4)\n</li>\n<li> Analyze Situation\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li> Homeworld\n<ul>\n<li> Investigate Jem'Hadar Facility\n</li>\n<li> Destroy Jem'Hadar Hatchery (0/3)\n</li>\n<li> Defeat <a href=\\"/Lamat%27Ukan\\" title=\\"Lamat'Ukan\\">Lamat'Ukan</a>\n</li>\n<li> Analyze Situation\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li> Rejection\n<ul>\n<li> Confirm Existence of a <a href=\\"/New_Link\\" title=\\"New Link\\">New Link</a>\n</li>\n<li> Talk to the Changeling\n</li>\n<li> Defeat and Capture <a href=\\"/Laas\\" title=\\"Laas\\">Laas</a>\n</li>\n<li> Depart System\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li> Report to Starfleet\n</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<div class=\\"rightcolumn\\">\n<h4><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Klingon_2\\">Klingon</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_The_New_Link&amp;action=edit&amp;section=10\\" title=\\"Edit section: Klingon\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h4>\n<ul>\n<li> Leading the Charge\n<ul>\n<li> Go to <a href=\\"/Orias_System\\" title=\\"Orias System\\">Orias System</a>\n</li>\n<li> Destroy All True Way Ships\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li> Fatal Mistake\n<ul>\n<li> Hail <a href=\\"/I.K.S._Norgh\\" title=\\"I.K.S. Norgh\\">I.K.S. Norgh</a>\n</li>\n<li> Defeat True Way Reinforcements\n</li>\n<li> Beam to Orias III\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li> Rescue and Recovery\n<ul>\n<li> Go To Orias III\n</li>\n<li> Beam Up Groups of Crewmen (0/4)\n</li>\n<li> Analyze Situation\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li> Homeworld\n<ul>\n<li> Investigate Jem'Hadar Facility\n</li>\n<li> Destroy Jem'Hadar Hatchery (0/3)\n</li>\n<li> Defeat Lamat'Ukan\n</li>\n<li> Analyze Situation\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li> Rejection\n<ul>\n<li> Confirm Existence of a <a href=\\"/New_Link\\" title=\\"New Link\\">New Link</a>\n</li>\n<li> Talk to the Changeling\n</li>\n<li> Defeat and Capture Laas\n</li>\n<li> Depart System\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li> Report to <a href=\\"/S%27taass\\" title=\\"S'taass\\">Ambassador S'taass</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<p><br style=\\"clear: both; height: 0px;\\" />\n</p>"}]}}}}"""))
