{"query":{"pages":{"24997":{"pageid":24997,"ns":0,"title":"Mission: Facility 4028","revisions":[{"*":"<div id=\\"toc\\" class=\\"toc\\"><div id=\\"toctitle\\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\\"><a href=\\"#Outline\\"><span class=\\"tocnumber\\">1</span> <span class=\\"toctext\\">Outline</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\\"><a href=\\"#Mission_Text\\"><span class=\\"tocnumber\\">1.1</span> <span class=\\"toctext\\">Mission Text</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\\"toclevel-3 tocsection-3\\"><a href=\\"#Federation\\"><span class=\\"tocnumber\\">1.1.1</span> <span class=\\"toctext\\">Federation</span></a></li>\n<li class=\\"toclevel-3 tocsection-4\\"><a href=\\"#Klingon\\"><span class=\\"tocnumber\\">1.1.2</span> <span class=\\"toctext\\">Klingon</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\\"toclevel-2 tocsection-5\\"><a href=\\"#Goal\\"><span class=\\"tocnumber\\">1.2</span> <span class=\\"toctext\\">Goal</span></a></li>\n<li class=\\"toclevel-2 tocsection-6\\"><a href=\\"#Objectives\\"><span class=\\"tocnumber\\">1.3</span> <span class=\\"toctext\\">Objectives</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Outline\\">Outline</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Facility_4028&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\\" title=\\"Edit section: Outline\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Mission_Text\\">Mission Text</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Facility_4028&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\\" title=\\"Edit section: Mission Text\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h3>\n<h4><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Federation\\">Federation</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Facility_4028&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\\" title=\\"Edit section: Federation\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h4>\n<div class=\\"missiontext\\">\n<p>The Federation Council has authorized the release of the Founder from the detention facility where she is currently being held.\n</p><p>I need someone who Eraun and the Founder will respect to complete the transfer. You're the best candidate for the task.\n</p><p>I don't expect any problems, but I didn't expect Jem'Hadar from the past to crash the Borg conference, either. So take my recommendations with a grain of salt.\n</p><p>The important thing is the safety of Eraun and the Founder. We need their help if we want to end this standoff without more bloodshed.\n</p>\n</div>\n<h4><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Klingon\\">Klingon</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Facility_4028&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\\" title=\\"Edit section: Klingon\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h4>\n<h3><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Goal\\">Goal</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Facility_4028&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\\" title=\\"Edit section: Goal\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h3>\n<div class=\\"missiongoal\\">Go to the Ayala System, which is located in the Kassae Sector of the Regulus Sector Block, and find the Female Founder.</div>\n<h3><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Objectives\\">Objectives</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Facility_4028&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\\" title=\\"Edit section: Objectives\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h3>\n<ul>\n<li> Visiting Hours\n<ul>\n<li> Go To <a href=\\"/Ayala_System\\" title=\\"Ayala System\\">Ayala System</a>\n</li>\n<li> Approach the Facility\n</li>\n<li> Hail Facility 4028\n</li>\n<li> Hail Eraun\n</li>\n<li> Beam Down\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li> Lockdown\n<ul>\n<li> Enter Isolation Zone A\n<ul>\n<li> Access I.S.I.S. Panel\n</li>\n<li> Extend Walkway\n</li>\n<li> Enter Control Room\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li> Speak to <a href=\\"/index.php?title=The_Warden&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\\" class=\\"new\\" title=\\"The Warden (page does not exist)\\">Warden</a>\n</li>\n<li> Extend Secondary Walkway\n</li>\n<li> Speak to Inmate 53160\n</li>\n<li> Speak to Warden\n</li>\n<li> Speak to Eraun\n</li>\n<li> Go to Isolation Zone B\n</li>\n<li> Release the Founder\n<ul>\n<li> Use I.S.I.S. Panel\n</li>\n<li> Open Cell Door\n</li>\n<li> Lower Secondary Force Field\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li> Speak to Founder\n</li>\n<li> Defeat Ambush\n</li>\n<li> Incoming Message\n</li>\n<li> Run Diagnostic\n</li>\n<li> Secure Prison\n<ul>\n<li> Section 01 Secured\n</li>\n<li> Section 02 Secured\n</li>\n<li> Section 03 Secured\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li> Speak to Final Prisoner\n</li>\n<li> Bring ISIS Back Online\n</li>\n<li> Speak to Warden\n</li>\n<li> Use Transporter Pad\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li> Final Flight\n<ul>\n<li> Depart System\n</li>\n<li> Return to Commander Mesi Achebe\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n"}]}}}}"""))
		missions.add(new Mission(text: """
{"query":{"pages":{"24998":{"pageid":24998,"ns":0,"title":"Mission: Boldly They Rode","revisions":[{"*":"<div id=\\"toc\\" class=\\"toc\\"><div id=\\"toctitle\\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\\"><a href=\\"#Outline\\"><span class=\\"tocnumber\\">1</span> <span class=\\"toctext\\">Outline</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\\"><a href=\\"#Mission_Text\\"><span class=\\"tocnumber\\">1.1</span> <span class=\\"toctext\\">Mission Text</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\\"toclevel-3 tocsection-3\\"><a href=\\"#Federation\\"><span class=\\"tocnumber\\">1.1.1</span> <span class=\\"toctext\\">Federation</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\\"><a href=\\"#Goal\\"><span class=\\"tocnumber\\">1.2</span> <span class=\\"toctext\\">Goal</span></a></li>\n<li class=\\"toclevel-2 tocsection-5\\"><a href=\\"#Objectives\\"><span class=\\"tocnumber\\">1.3</span> <span class=\\"toctext\\">Objectives</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Outline\\">Outline</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Boldly_They_Rode&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\\" title=\\"Edit section: Outline\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Mission_Text\\">Mission Text</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Boldly_They_Rode&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\\" title=\\"Edit section: Mission Text\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h3>\n<h4><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Federation\\">Federation</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Boldly_They_Rode&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\\" title=\\"Edit section: Federation\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h4>\n<div class=\\"missiontext\\">\n<p>Now that we have the aid of one of the Founders, we should have no trouble convincing the Jem'Hadar at Deep Space 9 to stand down and return to the Gamma Quadrant. Starfleet and the Klingon Empire are assembling a unified fleet to garrison the station and repair the damage from the battle. We want you to go with the Founder to negotiate the surrender of the remaining Jem'Hadar.\n</p><p>Rendezvous with a Jem'Hadar ship near Deep Space 9. You'll represent the interests of the Alpha Quadrant, but this should be a simple formality.\n</p><p>Captain Kurland is headed to Deep Space 9 in the <i>Defiant</i>, along with the rest of the task force. Oh, he said to tell you that he's looking forward to seeing you on the station again.\n</p>\n</div>\n<h3><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Goal\\">Goal</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Boldly_They_Rode&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\\" title=\\"Edit section: Goal\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h3>\n<div class=\\"missiongoal\\">\n<p>Head to Deep Space 9 to rendezvous with a Dominion ship.\n</p><p>Deep Space 9 is located in the Bajor Sector of the Beta Ursae Sector Block.\n</p>\n</div>\n<h3><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Objectives\\">Objectives</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Boldly_They_Rode&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\\" title=\\"Edit section: Objectives\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h3>\n<div class=\\"thumb tright\\"><div class=\\"thumbinner\\" style=\\"width:182px;\\"><a href=\\"/File:Kurland_Defiant_bridge.png\\" class=\\"image\\"><img alt=\\"\\" src=\\"http://hydra-media.cursecdn.com/sto.gamepedia.com/thumb/6/6f/Kurland_Defiant_bridge.png/180px-Kurland_Defiant_bridge.png?version=2664f242841df7916958d36c4344c544\\" width=\\"180\\" height=\\"96\\" class=\\"thumbimage\\" srcset=\\"http://hydra-media.cursecdn.com/sto.gamepedia.com/thumb/6/6f/Kurland_Defiant_bridge.png/270px-Kurland_Defiant_bridge.png 1.5x, http://hydra-media.cursecdn.com/sto.gamepedia.com/thumb/6/6f/Kurland_Defiant_bridge.png/360px-Kurland_Defiant_bridge.png 2x\\" /></a>  <div class=\\"thumbcaption\\"><div class=\\"magnify\\"><a href=\\"/File:Kurland_Defiant_bridge.png\\" class=\\"internal\\" title=\\"Enlarge\\"><img src=\\"/skins/common/images/magnify-clip.png\\" width=\\"15\\" height=\\"11\\" alt=\\"\\" /></a></div>Cpt. <a href=\\"/Kurland\\" title=\\"Kurland\\" class=\\"mw-redirect\\">Kurland</a> on the bridge of the <a href=\\"/U.S.S._Defiant\\" title=\\"U.S.S. Defiant\\">U.S.S. <i>Defiant</i></a>.</div></div></div>\n<div class=\\"thumb tright\\"><div class=\\"thumbinner\\" style=\\"width:182px;\\"><a href=\\"/File:On_the_hull_of_DS9.jpg\\" class=\\"image\\"><img alt=\\"\\" src=\\"http://hydra-media.cursecdn.com/sto.gamepedia.com/thumb/f/f6/On_the_hull_of_DS9.jpg/180px-On_the_hull_of_DS9.jpg?version=a31519d6ac6403a7348fabde4a518c6b\\" width=\\"180\\" height=\\"89\\" class=\\"thumbimage\\" srcset=\\"http://hydra-media.cursecdn.com/sto.gamepedia.com/thumb/f/f6/On_the_hull_of_DS9.jpg/270px-On_the_hull_of_DS9.jpg 1.5x, http://hydra-media.cursecdn.com/sto.gamepedia.com/thumb/f/f6/On_the_hull_of_DS9.jpg/360px-On_the_hull_of_DS9.jpg 2x\\" /></a>  <div class=\\"thumbcaption\\"><div class=\\"magnify\\"><a href=\\"/File:On_the_hull_of_DS9.jpg\\" class=\\"internal\\" title=\\"Enlarge\\"><img src=\\"/skins/common/images/magnify-clip.png\\" width=\\"15\\" height=\\"11\\" alt=\\"\\" /></a></div>On the hull of <a href=\\"/Deep_Space_9\\" title=\\"Deep Space 9\\">Deep Space 9</a></div></div></div>\n<div class=\\"thumb tright\\"><div class=\\"thumbinner\\" style=\\"width:182px;\\"><a href=\\"/File:DS9_hull_map.png\\" class=\\"image\\"><img alt=\\"\\" src=\\"http://hydra-media.cursecdn.com/sto.gamepedia.com/thumb/3/33/DS9_hull_map.png/180px-DS9_hull_map.png?version=076345638f554f468fd97ea7187bb038\\" width=\\"180\\" height=\\"296\\" class=\\"thumbimage\\" srcset=\\"http://hydra-media.cursecdn.com/sto.gamepedia.com/thumb/3/33/DS9_hull_map.png/270px-DS9_hull_map.png 1.5x, http://hydra-media.cursecdn.com/sto.gamepedia.com/thumb/3/33/DS9_hull_map.png/360px-DS9_hull_map.png 2x\\" /></a>  <div class=\\"thumbcaption\\"><div class=\\"magnify\\"><a href=\\"/File:DS9_hull_map.png\\" class=\\"internal\\" title=\\"Enlarge\\"><img src=\\"/skins/common/images/magnify-clip.png\\" width=\\"15\\" height=\\"11\\" alt=\\"\\" /></a></div>Map of DS9's hull during the space walk</div></div></div>\n<div class=\\"thumb tright\\"><div class=\\"thumbinner\\" style=\\"width:182px;\\"><a href=\\"/File:Bird-of-Prey_wreckage_on_DS9.png\\" class=\\"image\\"><img alt=\\"\\" src=\\"http://hydra-media.cursecdn.com/sto.gamepedia.com/thumb/3/37/Bird-of-Prey_wreckage_on_DS9.png/180px-Bird-of-Prey_wreckage_on_DS9.png?version=10281adacee929630847c2a018ef4d83\\" width=\\"180\\" height=\\"126\\" class=\\"thumbimage\\" srcset=\\"http://hydra-media.cursecdn.com/sto.gamepedia.com/thumb/3/37/Bird-of-Prey_wreckage_on_DS9.png/270px-Bird-of-Prey_wreckage_on_DS9.png 1.5x, http://hydra-media.cursecdn.com/sto.gamepedia.com/thumb/3/37/Bird-of-Prey_wreckage_on_DS9.png/360px-Bird-of-Prey_wreckage_on_DS9.png 2x\\" /></a>  <div class=\\"thumbcaption\\"><div class=\\"magnify\\"><a href=\\"/File:Bird-of-Prey_wreckage_on_DS9.png\\" class=\\"internal\\" title=\\"Enlarge\\"><img src=\\"/skins/common/images/magnify-clip.png\\" width=\\"15\\" height=\\"11\\" alt=\\"\\" /></a></div>The wreckage of a Klingon <a href=\\"/Bird-of-Prey\\" title=\\"Bird-of-Prey\\">Bird-of-Prey</a> blocks the player's path on the hull of Deep Space 9.</div></div></div>\n<ul>\n<li> Voice of the Gods\n<ul>\n<li> Go To <a href=\\"/Deep_Space_9\\" title=\\"Deep Space 9\\">Deep Space 9</a>\n</li>\n<li> Speak with the Vorta, Eraun\n</li>\n<li> Hail Deep Space 9\n</li>\n<li> Strategize with the Founder\n</li>\n<li> Activate an Environment Suit\n</li>\n<li> Exit the Airlock\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li> Black Ops\n<ul>\n<li> Traverse the Crossover\n<ul>\n<li> Activate Maintenance Safety Posts\n</li>\n<li> Use Reaction Thrusters to Jump to the Crossover\n</li>\n<li> Jump from Post to Post Along the Crossover\n</li>\n<li> Go to Sensor Maintenance Panel\n</li>\n<li> Reroute External Sensors\n</li>\n<li> Keep Moving Along the Maintenance Posts\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li> Head Around the Crashed Ship\n</li>\n<li> Jump!\n</li>\n<li> Jump Back Down to the Station\n</li>\n<li> Cross the Power Junctions\n</li>\n<li> Use the Control Junction to the Right\n</li>\n<li> Mind the Gap\n</li>\n<li> Jump to the Promenade\n</li>\n<li> Override the Security Systems\n</li>\n<li> Enter the Promenade\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li> Intruder\n<ul>\n<li> Cross the Exchange to the Promenade\n</li>\n<li> Reach the Ops Turbolift\n<ul>\n<li> Use Force Field Controls to Defenestrate Jem'Hadar (Optional)\n</li>\n<li> Trigger Trapped Environmental Controls (Optional)\n</li>\n<li> Find Useful Supplies (Optional)\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li> Confront Kar'ukan\n</li>\n<li> Beam Up and Pursue Kar'ukan\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li> Fight of Angels\n<ul>\n<li> Engage Kar'ukan's Forces\n</li>\n<li> Finish the Remaining Jem'Hadar Ships\n</li>\n<li> Beam Down to Deep Space 9\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li> Honor the Charge\n<ul>\n<li> Talk to James Kurland in DS9's Ops\n</li>\n<li> Hail the Enterprise from Ops on DS9 (Optional)\n</li>\n<li> Hail the Dominion from Ops on DS9 (Optional)\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n"}]}}}}"""))
		missions.add(new Mission(text: """
{"query":{"pages":{"4394":{"pageid":4394,"ns":0,"title":"Mission: Report to Gamma Orionis","revisions":[{"*":"<h4><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Romulan_Republic_.28Federation-aligned.29\\">Romulan Republic (Federation-aligned)</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Report_to_Gamma_Orionis&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\\" title=\\"Edit section: Romulan Republic (Federation-aligned)\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h4>\n<div class=\\"missiontext\\">\n<p>Our Starfleet allies have located a Borg presence in the Gamma Orionis Sector Block. A fleet already begun massing in the Cestus Sector in response.\n</p><p>Report immediately to Four of Ten. She is a liberated Borg who has been providing Starfleet with strategic information. Last I heard, she was stationed on the <a href=\\"/U.S.S._Victory\\" title=\\"U.S.S. Victory\\">U.S.S. Victory</a>.\n</p>\n</div>\n&lt;/div&gt;<div class=\\"rightcolumn\\"></div>\n"}]}}}}"""))
