{"query":{"pages":{"5557":{"pageid":5557,"ns":0,"title":"Mission: The Cure Applied","revisions":[{"*":"<h3><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Mission_text\\">Mission text</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_The_Cure_Applied&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\\" title=\\"Edit section: Mission text\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h3>\n<div class=\\"missiontext\\">&lt;Rank&gt;, there are increasing reports of <a href=\\"/Borg\\" title=\\"Borg\\">Borg</a> activity in the <a href=\\"/Vorn_System\\" title=\\"Vorn System\\">Vorn System</a>. \n<p>They're doing something big there, and Starfleet Command wants to know what it is. \n</p><p>Watch your back -- subspace chatter indicates that the Klingons have notice the Borg buildup in the Vorn system too. You don't want to end up fighting two enemies at once.\n</p>\nGood luck, &lt;rank&gt;.</div>\n"}]}}}}"""))
