{"query":{"pages":{"24610":{"pageid":24610,"ns":0,"title":"Mission: Khitomer Vortex","revisions":[{"*":"<h3><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Mission_Text\\">Mission Text</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Khitomer_Vortex&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\\" title=\\"Edit section: Mission Text\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h3>\n<div class=\\"missiontext\\">There are reports of Borg ships massing in the Quadra Sigma system.\n<p>A large Borg fleet is trouble we don't need. Also, levels of chroniton particles detected in the system could mean that the Borg are attempting to open a temporal anomoly.\n</p>\nI want them stopped before they can do anything that will damage the timeline.</div>\n"}]}}}}"""))
		missions.add(new Mission(text: """
{"query":{"pages":{"8913":{"pageid":8913,"ns":0,"title":"Mission: Khitomer in Stasis","revisions":[{"*":"<h3><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Mission_Text\\">Mission Text</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Khitomer_in_Stasis&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\\" title=\\"Edit section: Mission Text\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h3>\n<div class=\\"missiontext\\">There are reports of Borg ships massing in the Quadra Sigma system.\n<p>A large Borg fleet is trouble we don't need, &lt;rank&gt;. Report to the Quadra Sigma system and find out what they're doing there. If you must engage, you're authorized to do so.\n</p>\nGood luck.</div>\n"}]}}}}"""))
		missions.add(new Mission(text: """
{"query":{"pages":{"32011":{"pageid":32011,"ns":0,"title":"Mission: Into the Hive","revisions":[{"*":"<h2><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Notes\\">Notes</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Into_the_Hive&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\\" title=\\"Edit section: Notes\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Avoid the green floors as they shoot plasma that instantly kills anyone that steps on them. There is a short time before it activates where the floor is glowing. Try to run off them as it can kill your character instantly.\n</li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n<li>In the boss room, avoid the sides as a player can fall off and cannot get revived due to falling down into a big hole.\n</li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n<li>In the boss room, standing behind the pillars on each side is a good way to avoid being killed by the borg queen instantly.\n</li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n<li>In the boss fight, split your teams into 2 per side as this will flank the boss.\n</li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n<li>In the boss fight, concentrate on the medical drones as they can heal the boss.\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h3><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Known_Bugs\\">Known Bugs</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Into_the_Hive&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\\" title=\\"Edit section: Known Bugs\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h3>\n<ul>\n<li>There is a known bug on the boss room where if a player dies in the boss room, and all team members are forced to respawn outside the room, a team member can respawn inside the wall, thus breaking the mission for that person. The only possible fix for this is to teleport out of the level. Command stuck does not work, as it was tried and failed.\n</li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n<li>A bug on the boss can have the Borg Queen fall off the side of the level and get stuck. If this happens, your team will all have to commit suicide to respawn the queen. This fix was confirmed for this bug and works.\n</li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n<li>Some graphic cards on some computers have issues with showing the glowing green floor. Be advised if you are not seeing glowing floors, this could be a bug found in this mission. It is not experienced by all, but some are affected by it, depending on the graphic card types.\n</li>\n</ul>\n"}]}}}}"""))
