{"query":{"pages":{"13149":{"pageid":13149,"ns":0,"title":"Mission: Kern System Patrol","revisions":[{"*":"<h2><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Objectives\\">Objectives</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Kern_System_Patrol&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\\" title=\\"Edit section: Objectives\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul>\n<li> Secure Kern System\n<ul>\n<li> Defeat Klingon Defense Squadrons (4)\n</li>\n<li> Destroy Surveillance Satellites (5)\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h2><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Walkthrough\\">Walkthrough</span></h2>\n<dl>\n<dd><i>There is no walkthrough for this mission, yet. You can help STOWiki by <a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Kern_System_Patrol/Walkthrough&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\\" class=\\"new\\" title=\\"Mission: Kern System Patrol/Walkthrough (page does not exist)\\">writing it here</a>.</i>\n</dd>\n</dl>\n"}]}}}}"""))
		missions.add(new Mission(text: """
{"query":{"pages":{"13318":{"pageid":13318,"ns":0,"title":"Mission: Danteri System Patrol","revisions":[{"*":"<h3><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Mission_Text\\">Mission Text</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Danteri_System_Patrol&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\\" title=\\"Edit section: Mission Text\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h3>\n<div class=\\"missiontext\\">\n<p>Go to Danteri V and help handle a situation with two traders on the planet surface.\n</p><p>Deal with a situation between two brothers.\n</p>\n</div>\n"}]}}}}"""))
		missions.add(new Mission(text: """
{"query":{"pages":{"11859":{"pageid":11859,"ns":0,"title":"Mission: Seedea System Patrol","revisions":[{"*":"<h3><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Mission_Text\\">Mission Text</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Seedea_System_Patrol&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\\" title=\\"Edit section: Mission Text\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h3>\n<div class=\\"missiontext\\">\n<p><i>&lt;Rank&gt;</i>, I'm glad you're here!\n</p><p>My name is D'naen Trix. I'm the captain of the S.S. Rover.  \n</p><p>We're helping to evacuate this system, but I can't drop my shields to beam survivors onboard with those crazy lizards pointing disruptors in my face!\n</p><p>If you could back us up, we can get everyone to safety.\n</p><p>We need you to keep the Gorn busy while we beam people to our ship. Once everyone is safely aboard, I'm getting out of here. I can shake warp six out of this engine on a good day, and that should be enough.  \n</p>\n</div>\n"}]}}}}"""))
		missions.add(new Mission(text: """
{"query":{"pages":{"13319":{"pageid":13319,"ns":0,"title":"Mission: Honod System Patrol","revisions":[{"*":"<h3><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Mission_Text\\">Mission Text</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Honod_System_Patrol&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\\" title=\\"Edit section: Mission Text\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h3>\n<div class=\\"missiontext\\">\n<p>Civilian Authority: &lt;rank&gt; &lt;name&gt;, we require Starfleet's assistance.\n</p><p>Several unarmed civilian freighters have been destroyed near your coordinates. We are seeking sanctions against the people we hold responsible for these attacks, but we require evidence from the \\"scene of crime,\\" as it were.\n</p><p>Some in my government suspect Romulan involvement in the attacks, but I would like evidence gathered by a neutral party before making any accusations. Please locate one of our missing ships and determine the cause of its destruction.\n</p>\n</div>\n"}]}}}}"""))
		missions.add(new Mission(text: """
{"query":{"pages":{"13487":{"pageid":13487,"ns":0,"title":"Mission: Veyga System Patrol","revisions":[{"*":"<h3><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Mission_Text\\">Mission Text</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Veyga_System_Patrol&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\\" title=\\"Edit section: Mission Text\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h3>\n<div class=\\"missiontext\\">\n<p>As you may know, a standard Gorn battle maneuver is to use a group of fast ships to surround a ship or facility with a small minefield. The target is trapped until a larger Gorn fleet arrives.\n</p><p>Most of the time, this is a death sentence for anyone unfortunate enough to be the Gorn's prey.\n</p><p>We're getting distress calls from miners in this sector. The Gorn have moved in and dropped their minefields.\n</p><p>Eliminate the Gorn minefields from around the mining outposts, and keep the area clear until any trapped freighters can escape. \n</p><p>If you encounter the Gorn, you are authorized to defend your ship and crew, but your top priority must be saving the trapped miners.\n</p>\n</div>\n"}]}}}}"""))
		missions.add(new Mission(text: """
{"query":{"pages":{"13490":{"pageid":13490,"ns":0,"title":"Mission: Kalferi System Patrol","revisions":[{"*":"<h3><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Mission_Text\\">Mission Text</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Kalferi_System_Patrol&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\\" title=\\"Edit section: Mission Text\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h3>\n<div class=\\"missiontext\\">\n<p>Captain, the research vessel U.S.S. Bale is sending out a general distress signal. It is under attack by Nausicaan raiders.\n</p><p>Scans indicate enemy ships converging from multiple vectors. We will need to engage the Nausicaans and protect the Bale.\n</p>\n</div>\n"}]}}}}"""))
		missions.add(new Mission(text: """
{"query":{"pages":{"13497":{"pageid":13497,"ns":0,"title":"Mission: Vor System Patrol","revisions":[{"*":"<h3><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Mission_Text\\">Mission Text</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Vor_System_Patrol&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\\" title=\\"Edit section: Mission Text\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h3>\n<div class=\\"missiontext\\">\n<p><a href=\\"/Bran_Mhat\\" title=\\"Bran Mhat\\">Bran Mhat</a>: <i>&lt;Rank&gt;</i>, we are in desperate need!\n</p><p>We are conducting peaceful scientific work in this system, but the Gorn somehow have the idea that we are doing weapons research! \n</p><p>It's ridiculous! I'm a doctor, not a combat engineer!\n</p><p>They've been sending scout ships for the last hour to test our base's defenses. Long-range sensors show a Gorn fleet on the way! \n</p><p>Please, we are helpless against such firepower. You must protect us!\n</p>\n</div>\n"}]}}}}"""))
		missions.add(new Mission(text: """
{"query":{"pages":{"6126":{"pageid":6126,"ns":0,"title":"Mission: Maiewski System Patrol","revisions":[{"*":"<h3><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Mission_Text\\">Mission Text</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Maiewski_System_Patrol&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\\" title=\\"Edit section: Mission Text\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h3>\n<div class=\\"missiontext\\"><b>&lt;rank&gt;</b> <b>&lt;name&gt;</b>, we need your help!\n<p>My people use the asteroids in this area as material for our replicators. Orion Syndicate raiders have been plundering automated collection drones and taking our payloads. \n</p><p>These rocks are virtually useless to anyone but us. I don't even know why the Orions would want them, unless they're trying to force us to shut down our replicators and starve!\n</p><p>Will you patrol the belt and clear out the raiders? They'll probably be lurking near the larger asteroids.\n</p>\n</div>\n"}]}}}}"""))
		missions.add(new Mission(text: """
{"query":{"pages":{"6220":{"pageid":6220,"ns":0,"title":"Mission: Ceron System Patrol","revisions":[{"*":"<h3><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Mission_Text\\">Mission Text</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Ceron_System_Patrol&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\\" title=\\"Edit section: Mission Text\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h3>\n<div class=\\"missiontext\\">\n<p>Captain, a portion of the KDF's Fifth fleet have blockaded this system. They're hiding their ships in the asteroid belt and attacking any ship that approaches.\n</p><p>Six hours ago, they destroyed a civilian ship with more than 200 passengers aboard.\n</p><p>The colonists on the planet are scared, sir.\n</p><p>They can't flee, because the Klingons will destroy their ships. The can't stay, because the Klingons could land at any time. They need our help.\n</p><p>Our orders are to patrol this system and engage as many Klingons ships as we can find. If we can open a hole for the colonists, Starfleet will send in evacuation ships.\n</p>\n</div>\n"}]}}}}"""))
		missions.add(new Mission(text: """
{"query":{"pages":{"6221":{"pageid":6221,"ns":0,"title":"Mission: Vesper System Patrol","revisions":[{"*":"<h3><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Mission_Text\\">Mission Text</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Vesper_System_Patrol&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\\" title=\\"Edit section: Mission Text\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h3>\n<div class=\\"missiontext\\">\n<p>Captain, long range scans indicate anomalous elemental composition in some of the asteroids in this region.\n</p><p>We need a closer look at those asteroids to see if they are what the scientists at Vulcan Science Academy are theorizing they might be.\n</p><p>Nausicaans are known to use this asteroid belt as a base, but I think the scientific potential indicated by the elemental reading readings makes the risk worth taking.\n</p>\n</div>\n"}]}}}}"""))
		missions.add(new Mission(text: """
{"query":{"pages":{"6324":{"pageid":6324,"ns":0,"title":"Mission: Lilitu System Patrol","revisions":[{"*":"<h3><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Mission_Text\\">Mission Text</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Lilitu_System_Patrol&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\\" title=\\"Edit section: Mission Text\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h3>\n<div class=\\"missiontext\\">\n<p>&lt;Rank&gt;, this asteroid field is known to be a dump site for raiders and pirates.\n</p><p>We try to keep a close eye on the area. During Starfleet's last survey of the area, the U.S.S. Parsons recorded increased Orion Syndicate activity, as well as some clusters of \\"suspicious\\" debris. However, they were called away before they could conduct a full investigation.\n</p><p>We need you to scan each of the larger debris clusters. There could be clues left behind that we can match with recent crimes. We might be able to link these criminal acts to the Syndicate, or at least offer some closure to the victims and their families.\n</p><p>I must warn you, &lt;Name&gt; \u2013 the Orions won't look upon your presence here kindly. Expect resistance.\n</p>\n</div>\n"}]}}}}"""))
		missions.add(new Mission(text: """
{"query":{"pages":{"6325":{"pageid":6325,"ns":0,"title":"Mission: M'rade System Patrol","revisions":[{"*":"<h3><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Mission_Text\\">Mission Text</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_M%27rade_System_Patrol&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\\" title=\\"Edit section: Mission Text\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h3>\n<div class=\\"missiontext\\">\n<p><i>&lt;Rank&gt;</i>, we're picking up a faint emergency transponder signal from a Federation runabout, but transmissions from the Klingon base in this system are jamming local frequencies.\n</p><p>I recommend that we jam the station's communications, and then scan the debris for traces of the runabout.\n</p><p>Sensor readings indicate that the Klingons are searching for the source of the signal as well.\n</p><p>We should proceed with extreme caution.\n</p>\n</div>\n"}]}}}}"""))
		missions.add(new Mission(text: """
{"query":{"pages":{"6327":{"pageid":6327,"ns":0,"title":"Mission: Eriksson System Patrol","revisions":[{"*":"<h3><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Mission_Text\\">Mission Text</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Eriksson_System_Patrol&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\\" title=\\"Edit section: Mission Text\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h3>\n<div class=\\"missiontext\\">\n<p><i>&lt;Rank&gt;</i>, the Klingons have become much more aggressive in this area of space recently. We believe that they're using this system as a staging ground to prepare for a larger attack.\n</p><p>We can't allow them to get the upper hand, <i>&lt;Name&gt;</i>. What you do here could turn the tide of the war.\n</p><p>We've had some odd readings from the local surveillance beacons, and I want you to check it out.\n</p><p>Pay attention to brief sensor contacts \u2013 where there is a brief reading of a Klingon ship, there are likely to be more hidden ships nearby.\n</p><p>Good luck.\n</p>\n</div>\n"}]}}}}"""))
		missions.add(new Mission(text: """
{"query":{"pages":{"2235":{"pageid":2235,"ns":0,"title":"Mission: Eirhess System Patrol","revisions":[{"*":"<h3><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Mission_Text\\">Mission Text</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Eirhess_System_Patrol&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\\" title=\\"Edit section: Mission Text\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h3>\n<div class=\\"missiontext\\">\n<p>Starfleet aid shipments are being stored in this system for distribution to the surrounding planets.  Unfortunately, we're having trouble with Reman raids -- they hit the caches of supplies and help themselves to whatever they want.\n</p><p>I don't understand why they did it, Captain.  There is enough for everyone ... if everyone is willing to share.\n</p><p>Starfleet wants us to patrol this system and keep an eye out for Reman ships.\n</p><p>They like to lurk around the larger asteroids and wait for a transport ship to drop off supplies.  Then they swarm around the crates like hordes of Teneebian locusts.\n</p>\n</div>\n"}]}}}}"""))
		missions.add(new Mission(text: """
{"query":{"pages":{"2236":{"pageid":2236,"ns":0,"title":"Mission: Elvren System Patrol","revisions":[{"*":"<h3><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Mission_Text\\">Mission Text</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Elvren_System_Patrol&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\\" title=\\"Edit section: Mission Text\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h3>\n<div class=\\"missiontext\\">\n<p><a href=\\"/Science\\" title=\\"Science\\" class=\\"mw-redirect\\">science</a> <a href=\\"/Bridge_officer\\" title=\\"Bridge officer\\">bridge officer</a>: Sensors indicate unusual energy readings from the planet.  We should approach the planet and investigate.\n</p>\n</div>\n"}]}}}}"""))
		missions.add(new Mission(text: """
{"query":{"pages":{"2237":{"pageid":2237,"ns":0,"title":"Mission: Icari System Patrol","revisions":[{"*":"<h3><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Mission_Text\\">Mission Text</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Icari_System_Patrol&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\\" title=\\"Edit section: Mission Text\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h3>\n<div class=\\"missiontext\\">\n<p><b>&lt;rank&gt;</b>, we are in need of your help.\n</p><p>Planetary sensors have detected asteroids of an unknown substance in our orbit. We believe they drifted here from another system.\n</p><p>We do not have the resources required to identify or deal with the asteroids, and we are concerned that their orbit will deteriorate and they could fall to the surface. Would you please study the asteroids and determine their origin and if there is any threat to us?\n</p>\n</div>\n"}]}}}}"""))
		missions.add(new Mission(text: """
{"query":{"pages":{"8402":{"pageid":8402,"ns":0,"title":"Mission: Rhi System Patrol","revisions":[{"*":"<h3><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Mission_Text\\">Mission Text</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Rhi_System_Patrol&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\\" title=\\"Edit section: Mission Text\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h3>\n<div class=\\"missiontext\\">\n<p>Since the destruction of the <a href=\\"/Romulus\\" title=\\"Romulus\\">Romulus</a> homeworld, many of the former colony worlds have tried to go their own way.  <a href=\\"/Starfleet\\" title=\\"Starfleet\\">Starfleet</a> Command supports these attempts at independence -- someday some of these worlds might even apply to be members of the Federation.\n</p><p>Empress <a href=\\"/Sela\\" title=\\"Sela\\">Sela</a> has been sending fleets to harass these \\"breakaway\\" planets.\n</p><p>Starfleet wants the <i>&lt;ship name&gt;</i> to be a buffer between the residents of the colony in this system and the Romulan forces.  Our orders are to keep the Romulans at bay and give these people a chance to develop their own system of government.\n</p>\n</div>\n"}]}}}}"""))
		missions.add(new Mission(text: """
{"query":{"pages":{"2248":{"pageid":2248,"ns":0,"title":"Mission: Sienae System Patrol","revisions":[{"*":"<h3><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Mission_Text\\">Mission Text</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Sienae_System_Patrol&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\\" title=\\"Edit section: Mission Text\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h3>\n<div class=\\"missiontext\\">\n<p>&lt;rank&gt;, the Romulans have been meeting with Hirogen ships in this system, and Starfleet Intelligence suspects that they are seeking a formal alliance.  That could be bad for the Federation.\n</p><p>Frankly, the Romulans are desperate to revive their empire, and they're willing to ally with any race that they think can help them do that.\n</p><p>Having the Hirogen hunting in this area is bad enough.  If the Romulans get them to sign a treaty, Empress Sela will have a powerful new weapon in her arsenal.\n</p><p>The encounters with the U.S.S. Voyager had with the Hirogen prove how dangerous they can be.\n</p><p>Starfleet knows the Hirogen are using this system as one of their bases of operations.  Our orders are to engage them here and force them to find new hunting grounds.  The farther they are from Federation space, the safer we are.\n</p>\n</div>\n"}]}}}}"""))
		missions.add(new Mission(text: """
{"query":{"pages":{"2249":{"pageid":2249,"ns":0,"title":"Mission: Terrh System Patrol","revisions":[{"*":"<h3><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Mission_Text\\">Mission Text</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Terrh_System_Patrol&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\\" title=\\"Edit section: Mission Text\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h3>\n<div class=\\"missiontext\\">\n<p>Teams of independent miners have been working in this system to gather viterium, but they're being attacked by <a href=\\"/Reman\\" title=\\"Reman\\">Remans</a> who don't want any competition.\n</p><p>Our orders are to patrol this system and keep the Remans away from the miners.  They like to stay cloaked until the miners have a full payload and then pounce, so we should be wary.  Space that looks clear probably isn't.\n</p>\n</div>\n"}]}}}}"""))
		missions.add(new Mission(text: """
{"query":{"pages":{"2250":{"pageid":2250,"ns":0,"title":"Mission: Ra'kholh System Patrol","revisions":[{"*":"<h3><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Mission_Text\\">Mission Text</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_Ra%27kholh_System_Patrol&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\\" title=\\"Edit section: Mission Text\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h3>\n<div class=\\"missiontext\\">\n<p>The starbase in this system houses a holographic research facility where artificial life forms work side-by-side with Federation science teams to find ways to expand holographic technology and lift the limitations that technology puts on sentient holograms.\n</p><p>The Hirogen would love to get their hands on that research.  We can't let that happen.\n</p><p>I want you to sweep this system and engage any Hirogen targets you find.  Be careful, <b>&lt;rank&gt;</b> -- they'll try to drop out of orbit and catch you unawares.\n</p><p>If even one Hirogen gets onto the space station and gets access to the holo database, it could be a disaster.  I'm counting on you to keep everyone safe.\n</p><p>Good luck.\n</p>\n</div>\n"}]}}}}"""))
		missions.add(new Mission(text: """
{"query":{"pages":{"2266":{"pageid":2266,"ns":0,"title":"Mission: T'liss System Patrol","revisions":[{"*":"<h3><span class=\\"mw-headline\\" id=\\"Mission_Text\\">Mission Text</span><span class=\\"mw-editsection\\"><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">[</span><a href=\\"/index.php?title=Mission:_T%27liss_System_Patrol&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\\" title=\\"Edit section: Mission Text\\">edit</a><span class=\\"mw-editsection-bracket\\">]</span></span></h3>\n<div class=\\"missiontext\\">\n<p>The Romulans are becoming increasingly bold about their incursions into protected areas.  We're starting to find them in systems that they never would have entered previously.\n</p><p>That stops now.\n</p><p>I want you to sweep this system and let the Romulans know they're not welcome here.  You are authorized to use whatever means necessary to get the job done.\n</p>\n</div>\n"}]}}}}"""))
